 <office:body>
  <office:text text:use-soft-page-breaks="true">
   <office:forms form:automatic-focus="false" form:apply-design-mode="false"/>
   <text:sequence-decls>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Illustration"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Table"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Text"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Drawing"/>
   </text:sequence-decls>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">cum aliquo v-tas; amicitiæ et v-tes; propter v-tem totos dies simul eramus; nares oris v-tem secutæ sunt; in v-bus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grannförhållanden)</text:span> æquum esse et facilem, C.; solis v-ia, Ov.; silvæ v-tas, Pn.; v-ia Persidis, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i concret mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grannskapet, grannar; bygd:</text:span></text:span> proxume v-æ (<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen. part.</text:span>), Pt.; lacus Avernus in nostra v-a; homo princeps ejus v-tis; in v-tem meretriciam se conferre; cantu tibiarum tota v-tas personat, C.; v-ia laudat; quære peregrinum: v-ia rauca reclamat, Hor.; v-tem armis exornare, Sa.; v-ti dant operam, ut eum interficiant, N.; conspectum ac v-am fori fugere; sapientiam nondum habent, sed jam in ejus v-a constiterunt, Sen. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">qwarter i stad,</text:span> Su. Aug. 30.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slägtskap, frändskap</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i beskaffenhet, likhet:</text:span> aqua ad v-am lactis accedens, Pn.; virtutum v-a, v-tas, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten by:</text:span></text:span> C., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Videlicet <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Video.<text:line-break/>Viden’ = Videsne.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭdeo,</text:span> vīdi, vīsum (vissum, Pt.), 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Se:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg., i allm.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ses:</text:span></text:span> vidi egomet his duobus oculis meis; vidi Philocomasium malam sibi rem quærere; vidi illam ausculantem cum adulescentulo; oculis carebis, credo, qui plus v-ent, quam quod v-ent; vide <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se efter),</text:span> sitne istæc intus; viden (= videsne), hostes tibi adesse?; comminiscere calidum consilium cito, quæ hic sunt visa, ut visa ne sint, Pt.; statuam: non oculis cernimus ea, quæ v-emus; sæpe apertis atque integris et oculis et auribus nec v-emus neque audimus, ut facile intelligi possit animum et v-re et audire, non eas partes, quæ quasi fenestræ sunt animi, C.; v-o eum esse robustum; faciem alicujus, Ter.; non visa pro visis retulit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inberättade);</text:span> equitatu viso, Cs.; ab oppidanis flamma visa est; quum alqm v-ret minus bene vestitum, suum amiculum dedit, N.; se speculo alterum; nonne v-es, ut nudum remigio latus antennæque gemunt, Hor.; ille deûm vitam accipiet divisque v-bit permixtos heroas et ipse v-bitur illis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af dem);</text:span> nonne v-es, croceos ut Tmolus odores, India mittit ebur, Vg.?; niveus v-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att skåda</text:span> = visu), Hor.; colles exire v-entur; auditos cælestes præponere visis; nulli v-dus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af eller för ingen synlig);</text:span> miserabile visu, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Se om, besöka, träffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en person:</text:span> propediem te v-bo, C.; moenia, domum alicujus, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Se</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i drömmen:</text:span> visus Homerus adesse poēta, Enn.; in somnis, in quiete alqd v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(drömma);</text:span> se facere alqd, C.: ultro flens ipse v-bar compellare virum; in somnis ecce ante oculos mæstissimus Hector visus adesse mihi, Vg.; vidi ego te in somnis fractā, mea vita, carinā Ionio lassas ducere rore manus, Ppt. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Se, upplefwa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> deraf i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">röna, erfara;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med sinnena </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">märka:</text:span></text:span> multos dies celeberrimos lætissimosve vidit; somnum non vidit in consulatu suo, C.; - tertia dum Latio regnantem v-rit æstas; nascitur et casus abies visura marinos; mugire v-bis sub pedibus terram, Vg.; mala; v-res stridere secreta divisos aure susurros, Hor.; tempora senectæ; centum messes, Ov.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medelst förståndet se:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hafwa ögon för, hafwa blick för, förmå att se, inse, finna:</text:span></text:span> verba mihi data esse v-o, Pt.; tenvis enim natura deûm longeque remota sensibus a nostris animi vix mente v-etur, Lucr.; plus aliquid v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa högre blick, djupare insigt, begripa mera);</text:span> cupiditas veri v-ndi; membrorum situs vacans corpore quam possit harmoniam efficere, non v-o: si, quid sit hoc, non v-es, at quale sit, v-es; animus non v-et formam suam, vim certe, sagacitatem, memoriam, celeritatem v-et; vidit hoc acutissime; vidit hoc Simonides, acerrimum esse sensum v-ndi; causas rerum v.; totius vitæ cursum v-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerskådar),</text:span> C.; vidit futurum, ut Thasii dilaberentur; quid potissimum vitarent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skulle undwika),</text:span> non v-bant, N.; vidit imperator, se dolis fatigari; Metellus v-et frustra inceptum, Sa.; Germanos in Galliam venire pop. Romano periculosum esse v-bat, Cs.; v-o meliora proboque, deteriora sequor, Ov.; interdum vulgus rectum v-et, est ubi peccat; ingenium subtile v-ndis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa blick för, bedöma)</text:span> artibus, Hor. (Ep. II. 1. 242); Turnus - infractos adverso Marte Latinos defecisse v-et, Vg.; poenam putabam: munus, ut v-o, est fuga, Sen. trag.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hafwa för ögonen, till afsigt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mål:</text:span></text:span> majus aliquid v-bam, C.; gloriam; commodum, L. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillse, gifwa akt; taga i betraktande, öfwerwägande; betänka, se till,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">ut, ne</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">att icke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">om icke); sörja för, akta sig, taga sig till wara:</text:span></text:span> vide consilium, si placet, Pt. Trin. 763; vide, ne ruas, Ter.; quam id recte faciam, v-rint sapientes: certe mentiar; vide, ne <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om icke)</text:span> hoc totum sit a me; v-dum est, ne non (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om wäl)</text:span> satis sit illud; de reliquo mox v-ro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(taga i betraktande);</text:span> v-dum est, ut honeste vos esse possitis (Ep. ad Fam. XIV. 14); et hæc v-da et fugienda pecuniæ cupiditas; ne longum fiat, v-ete (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tänken efter, om det ej blir för widlyftigt),</text:span> C.; vide, ne tu pejus patriæ consulas, N.; v-amus, uter -, Hor.; v-ete, quam iniqui sint, Sa.; de me divom pater atque hominum rex v-rit (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillse, besluta),</text:span> Vg.; vidĕ, ne dolone collum compungam tibi; v-e, ne querela major accrescat domus, Phdr. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Se sig om efter; söka skaffa sig, skaffa, anskaffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> provideo): dicebat Philippus, v-dum sibi esse aliud consilium: illo senatu regere se rem publicam non posse; prandium alicui, C.; puerum jubet oleum in aulam (ollam) v-re, Gell. XVII. 8.<text:line-break/>e. me vide = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lita på mig, tro mig:</text:span></text:span> nihil est de signo quod vereare, me vide, Pt. (Trin. 808; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> Mil. 375 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lor.);</text:span> hæc fient: me v-e, Ter. Phorm. 711.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om döda subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hafwa utsigt till, ligga, wetta åt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> Pn., Luc.<text:line-break/>7. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">passivum</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utom de activum motswarande bemärkelserna) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Synas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i subjectiv mening), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tyckas, anses</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (absolut l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span>):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i personlig construction (i sw. ofta att öfwersätta med opersonliga uttryck: det synes, ser ut, förefaller, låter som om l. att -; oftare med activ construction = anse, hålla för, akta, tycka):</text:span> hæc mulier Philocomasium an non est ea? Hercle opinor: ea v-etur (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det tyckes så),</text:span> Pt.; pater mihi apud forum: uxor tibi ducendast hodie, inquit: abi domum. Id mihi visust dicere: abi cito ac suspende te, Ter.; non mihi v-bantur id accusare, quod esset accusandum; mihi v-or magnum attulisse adjumentum civibus meis; ita mihi v-or perspicere, inter omnes esse conjunctionem quandam naturæ; ea ei visa sunt pro <text:soft-page-break/>nihilo; beate vixisse v-or <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tycker mig),</text:span> quod cum Scipione vixerim; tu mihi Epicharmi sententiam sequi v-eris; sibi v-entur beati (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äro i sina ögon);</text:span> hanc induxit, quæ v-retur esse, non quæ esset, discrepantiam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skenbara, ej werkliga),</text:span> C.; hæc alio spectabant, atque v-ri volebant; hoc vere v-or posse contendere, N.; Ariovistus tantos spiritus sibi sumpserat, ut ferendus non v-retur; colloquendi Cæsari causa non visa est, Cs.; mihi rectius v-etur ingenii quam virium operā gloriam quærere, Sa.; alea parva nuces et non damnosa v-etur; felicissima matrum dicta foret Niobe, si non sibi visa fuisset; idem factura v-bar, Ov.; omnemque v-bar evasisse viam, Vg.; ego mihi videor sanus; quid tibi visa Chios <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(huru fann du),</text:span> Bullati, notaque Lesbos?, Hor.; si qua tibi obscura visa sunt, de iis rursus conferemus, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i personlig construction i officiella utlåtanden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Anses, dömas, förklaras:</text:span></text:span> P. Scævola, pont. max., pro collegio respondit, sacrum non v-ri, C.; adversus remp. fecisse v-ri, Cs.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i impersonel construction, absol. l. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc. c. inf.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Det är</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (min, din o. s. w.) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">åsigt, mening:</text:span></text:span> non mihi v-etur ad beate vivendum satis posse virtutem, C.; mihi contra ea v-etur, Sa. (Jug. 85. 1).<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i impersonel construction:</text:span> videtur, visum est <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det (synes ngn rådligt l. rätt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Behagar, täckes, synes</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">godt</text:span></text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beslutar, finner för godt:</text:span></text:span> ut v-etur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som eder behagar);</text:span> prætori visum est dimittere legionem; imitamur, quos cuique visum est (imitari), C.; dis aliter visum; res Asiæ Priamique evertere gentem immeritam visum superis, Vg.; sic visum Veneri, Hor.; s i tibi v-etur, des ei filiam nuptum, N.; nullo a nostris responso dato, ubi visum est, sub vesperum dispersi ac dissipati discedunt, Cs.; visum est delere; sic visum superis, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Visum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se nedanför i den alphabetiska ordningen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭdēlĭcet</text:span> = videre licet: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">man kan se, finna:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bibehållen betydelse af sats, åtföljdt af beroende</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc. c. inf.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Det förstås; det är tydligt, naturligt:</text:span></text:span> v., parcum fuisse illum senem, qui id dixerit, Pt.; esse v. in terris primordia rerum, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">parenthetiskt l. i adverbielt bruk: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Naturligtwis, tydligtwis:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allwarlig mening:</text:span> v. de psaltria hoc audivit: id illi nunc dolet; hic errat v., Ter.; Brundusio quæ tibi epistolæ redditæ sunt, sine mea manu, tum v. datæ, quum ego me non belle haberem (Ep. ad Att. V. 11); caste jubet lex adire ad deos, animo v., in quo sunt omnia, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ironisk mening = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kan tro, kan tänka:</text:span></text:span> homo v. timidus et modestus, C.; v. cetera vita (Catilinæ conjuratorum) eorum huic sceleri obstat; - v. Jugurthæ speculanti iter suum cognitum esset, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Videsis = vide, si vis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīsĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Synlig:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">seende, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som har synförmåga:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Seende, syn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i abstract mening:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Syn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i concret mening, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bild,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl yttre </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">företeelse,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">phantasibild, föreställning:</text:span></text:span> dormientium animi utrum per semet <text:soft-page-break/>ipsos in somniando moventur an externa et adventicia v-e pulsantur?; fluentium v-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om Epicuri</text:span> εἴδωλα) transitio; falsa doloris v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(föreställning);</text:span> inanis; cui est v. veri falsique communis, nullum potest habere judicium aut ullam veritatis notam, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīso</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ursprungl. ett desiderativum?; Zeitschr. für vergleichende Sprachforschung</text:span> I. 190):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gå att se, komma att se</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquid</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T2">alqm</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T2">ad aliquem</text:span>):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gå att se efter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">besöka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett ställe:</text:span> vise ad me intro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(titta in till mig):</text:span> jam scies; cognati ut liberi me curant: v-unt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(komma att se efter),</text:span> quid agam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(huru jag mår),</text:span> ecquid velim, Pt.; v-am, si domi est; v-o, tune an illi insaniunt; v-di causa mittere alqm, Ter.; propter Musas (Praxitelis) v-untur Thespiæ: nam alia v-di causa nulla est; domus quum a vulgo v-retur, suffragata domino, homini novo, consulatum videbatur, C.; templa deorum, Sa.; ad judicem, Varr.; regna sororis Hesionæ, Vg.; sol, possis nihil urbe Roma visere majus; omne - Proteus pecus egit altos v-re montes; v-dus ater flumine languido Cocytus; Dædaleo tutior Icaro v-am gementis litora Bospori, Hor.; aulam, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gå att se till, se om</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">besöka, helsa på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (titta till, isynn. en sjuk):</text:span> socrus nurum, Ter.; et videre et visere alqm; ad ægros, Lucr.; ad ludos venies nosque vises; puerum, C.; cubat hic in colle Quirini, hic extremo in Aventino, v-dus uterque, Hor.; sororem; ad amicam, Ov.; Agrippina morbo implicata, quum v-ret eam Cæsar (Tiberius), invidiam et preces orditur; ad Burrum (ægrotantem) v-dum venit princeps (Nero), T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beskåda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med ifwer och nyfikenhet); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bese, se, se sig om, betrakta;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofta blott i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">se:</text:span></text:span> summa fuit omnium exspectatio v-di Alcibiadis; confecta cæde multitudo v-di gratiā introiit (domum Dionis), N.; ad mercatum (non lucri, sed) v-di causā venire; quum laxati curis sumus, spectare aliquid volumus et v.; ornatus v-dus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wärd att beskåda),</text:span> C.; undique v-di (captivi Sinonis) studio Trojana juventus circumfusa ruit, Vg.; ad v-dum prodigium missi, L.; proelium, Sa.; Afraniani milites v-di causa læti ex castris procurrebant, Cs.; Capitolia v-ent pompas, Ov.; v-re gestiens, qua parte debacchentur ignes, Hor.; concipitur v-itque exortum lumina solis, Lucr. I. 5; nec dum etiam sese, quæ v-it, visere credit, Catl.; præfulgebant Cassius et Brutus eo, quod non v-bantur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīsĭto</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vissito), 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Besöka:</text:span></text:span> ægrotum alqm, C.; ægrum, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ofta se:</text:span></text:span> me interrogat, ecquem Luconem noverim: adnuo vissitasse; homo ignota facie quæ non v-tata est, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīsum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Syn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i concret mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för sinnena:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> v-is nocturnis movebantur, ut eos qui vita excessissent, vivere crederent, C.; hoc v. nulli, non ipsi effata sorori, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt, i philosophisk stil i allm.: sinlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnimmelse, föreställning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> den bild l. det intryck, som föremålet framkallar för själen:</text:span> v. impressum effictumque ab eo, unde est, quale non potest esse ex eo quod non est; omnia v-a vel falsa esse possunt vel vera <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl. skeptikernes lära),</text:span> C. Acad. II. §. 18. 27. 77 et sæpius; I. 40.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drömbild, syn:</text:span></text:span> ea se in quiete per v-um ex Africano audisse dicebat; v-a somniorum, C.; v-a referre, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīsus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Syn:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">subj.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Seende; beseende; anblick, åsyn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt, att se ngt:</text:span> v-u nocent feminæ, quæ duplices habent pupillas, C. ap. Non.; qua v. erat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ses kunde),</text:span> Sa.; aliquid subdere v-u (visui), Lucr.; diffugimus v-u exsangues, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Syn, synförmåga, synsinne</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (öga):</text:span> mortales hebetat v-us tuos nubes; omnia obire v-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ögonen),</text:span> Vg.; v-u notare, vitiare; id natura negavit v-bus humanis, Ov.; acer, Pn.; repente affertur, redire Tiberio (jam morienti) vocem ac v-us, T. Ann. VI. 50; oculorum, Qu.; hebes, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obj.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utseende, anblick, gestalt:</text:span></text:span> v-um habere insignem et illustrem, C.; augustior humano v-u, L. VIII. 9. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Syn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i objectivt concret mening; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">företeelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (det, som ngn ser l. i allm. warseblifwer):</text:span> quo repentino objecto v-u (summum) terrorem injecit exercitui Romanorum (Hannibal), N.; Nymphas venerabar agrestes, rite secundarent v-us omenque levarent, Vg.; nocturnos v-us inter se consules contulerunt, L. VIII. 6; immundo somnia v-u, Hor.; inopino territa v-u, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Circumvīso</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Se sig omkring på:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convīso</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beskåda, betrakta, besöka:</text:span></text:span> luminibus mentis res occultas; sol et luna connivent et aperto lumine rursus omnia c-unt (visunt = collustrant) clarā loca candida luce, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvĭdens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ögonskenlig, synbarlig, klar, tydlig, uppenbar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för öga l. för förstånd):</text:span> rebus perspicuis et e-bus adversari; mensura; narratio; id in homine est e-ius (diligi eos, qui procreati sunt), C.; auctor; ratio, Pn.; res quam e-sima, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvĭdenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Synbarligt, tydligt, klart:</text:span></text:span> fateri, quum tam e. poenituerit, tutum censemus, L.; nocens, Val.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvĭdentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ögonskenlighet, handgriplighet, påtaglighet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sinlig förnimmelses) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tydlighet:</text:span></text:span> nihil ipsā e-ā illustrius; perspicuitatem aut e-am nos nominemus (ἐνάργειαν) fabricemurque, si opus erit, nomina, C. Acad. pr. §. 17; plus est e. quam perspicuitas, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intervīso</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Intervisso), ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Under tiden</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">då och då</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (emellanåt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">besöka, se till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (titta till):</text:span> nunc abeamus intro. Immo i-vissam domum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(titta in till mitt);</text:span> dies totos apud portum servus unus assidet <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sitter på wakt).</text:span> Sed tamen volo i-vissi, Pt. Stich. 147. 154; minus nos i-is; urbanam expolitionem ipse crebro i-so, C. ad Qu. fr. III. II. 6.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invĭdeo</text:span>, vīdi, vīsum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afundas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngn,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet.</text:span> invideor); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hysa afund; mißunna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquid,</text:span> Acc.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui aliquid, alicui aliqua re,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efterciceronianskt; wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicujus rei</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), C.); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förtryta på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> i-ndi verbum ductum est a nimis intuendo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(liksom förse l. förgapa sig på, se snedt på)</text:span> fortunam alterius, ut est in Melanippo (fabula): Quis non florem <text:soft-page-break/>liberum (liberorum) invidit meum? Male Latine videtur, sed præclare Accius. Ut enim videre, sic invidere florem rectius quam flori. Nos consuetudine prohibemur: poēta jus suum tenuit et dixit audacius, C. (Tusc. III. §. 20; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Madv. rättelse af</text:span> nobis naturam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till</text:span> nobis naturæ vim vidisse videntur, Tusc. III. §. 3, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Tregders, Seyfferts m. fl. uppl.; jfr</text:span> Qu. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nedanför):</text:span> alicui, Pt.; i-re non cadit in sapientem; illi ætati (juventuti) non solum non i-etur, sed etiam favetur; meæ novitati (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mig för min obemärkta börds skull);</text:span> nemo, qui suæ confidit, alterius virtuti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sin nästa hans förtjenst)</text:span> i-et; tibi i-o, quod unis vestimentis tam diu lautus es; paribus et superioribus i-ri solet, C.; virtuti alicujus, Cs., Sa.; isti honori meo i-ent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mig min befordran),</text:span> Sa.; (victoriæ vestræ) neque deus neque homo quisquam i-et; non i-runt laude sua <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Mdvg)</text:span> mulieribus viri Romani, L.; nolite mihi id dare, quod multi i-ant, plures etiam concupiscant, N. (Thras. IV. 2); ego cur, acquirere pauca si possum, i-or, quum lingua Catonis et Enni sermonem patrium ditaverit?; amicum alicui; gazis Arabum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Araberne deras skatter);</text:span> usum lignorum alicui, Hor.; victibus priorum, Ov.; non bonus Eurytion prælato i-dit honore, Vg.; nos dicimus hac re i-re, non, ut omnes veteres et Cicero præcipue, hanc rem, Qu. VIII. 3. 1. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej unna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngn att få ngt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förmena, förwägra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt</text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui rem</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">re</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T2">rei</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span>), Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">ut, ne</text:span>]: Cleopatra i-ens liburnis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>) deduci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ej unnande skeppen att på dem föras)</text:span> triumpho; neque ille (hospes) sepositi ciceris nec longæ i-dit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(snålade med)</text:span> avenæ; sunt plurima, quæ i-ant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ej tillåta)</text:span> pure apparere tibi rem, Hor.; quos hora novissima junxit, componi tumulo non i-eatis eodem, Ov.; i-isse deos, patriis ut redditus oris conjugium optatum et pulcram Calydona viderem; Ascanione pater Romanas i-et arces?; mihi senectus i-et imperium; i-dit fortuna mihi, ne regna videres nostra, Vg.; sepulturā alicui, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invĭdendus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afundswärd:</text:span></text:span> C. (de Or. II. §. 228); domus i-is postibus; aula i-a, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invĭdentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afundsjuka:</text:span></text:span> i. ægritudo est ex alterius rebus secundis; - utendum est enim verbo minus usitato, quoniam i. non in eo, qui invidet, solum dicitur, sed etiam in eo, cui invidetur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afundsjuk, mißunsam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ogunstig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot ngn</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui, alicujus</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">den afundsjuke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i generisk mening); ngns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">afundsman:</text:span></text:span> suis, Pt.; i-i et malevoli dicuntur, quia facile ad istas perturbationes, non quia semper ferantur; tantum Murenæ tribuit Lucullus, quantum neque malevolus imperator neque i. tribuisset; non i-i solum, sed etiam fautores laudum mearum; hujus beneficii obtrectator, virtutis hostis et i., C.; tuis i-is -; inter i-os (versari), Sa.; quid foret Iliæ Mavortisque puer, si taciturnitas obstaret meritis i-a Romuli?; i-us alterius macrescit rebus opimis; dum loquimur, fugerit i-a ætas; cura; jam dente minus mordeor i-o, Hor.: natura, Lucr.; lingua; nox coeptis i-a nostris, Ov.; i-a fatorum series summisque negatum stare diu, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invĭdia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Owilja, ogunst, mißnöje, förargelse, hat</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som ngn hyser l. hwarför ngn är föremål; isynnerhet mot offentliga (högtstående) </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personer l. handlingar, från allmänhetens sida; impopularitet, dåligt rykte, förbittring):</text:span> metus i-æ; Cleombrotus i-am (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">opinionen)</text:span> timens temere cum Epaminonda conflixit, C.; venire, incidere in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blifwa föremål för)</text:span> i-am, C., N.; esse in i-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara föremål för);</text:span> flagrare, ardere i-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara utsatt för brinnande, häftig owilja);</text:span> i. Numantini foederis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(folkets öfwer -);</text:span> habuit Scaurus i-am, quod locupletis hominis bona sine testamento possederat; i-am colligere, subire <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ådraga sig),</text:span> sustinere; i-am parare alicui; sedare, lenire, inflammare, comprimere; in i-am adducere, vocare aliquem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ådraga ngn);</text:span> i-ā premi; quærere i-am in alqm; vita remota a procellis i-arum; malevolorum i-as prosternere, C.; id factum magnæ erat tyranno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ådrog t.)</text:span> i-æ, N.; i-am accendere; i-am conflare alicui; res est in i-a; partium i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(partihat);</text:span> i. apud plebem; i. decessit, dilapsa est; belli; ex maxima i-a in gratiam et favorem nobilitatis venit Jugurtha, Sa.; absit i. verbo (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">må det ej synas förmätet),</text:span> L. VIII. 19; Ct.; facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäcka mot)</text:span> alicui, Ov.; divisere deos et nullis defuit aris i-am factura părens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäcka owilja emot</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wisa gudarnes hårdhet, då de ej hörde hennes bön),</text:span> Luc II. 35 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.;</text:span> i-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uttryck af mißnöje)</text:span> et preces orditur, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afund</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som ngn hyser l. för hwilken ngn är föremål; jfr</text:span> invidentia), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">afundsjuka, mißunsamhet:</text:span></text:span> obtrectatio et i. lacerat plerosque; digna imitatione, non i-ā, excellentium hominum virtus, C.; i-ā laudem alicujus obterere; i-ā ducum Eumenes Antigono est deditus; minori esse i-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara utsatt för -);</text:span> vereri i-am, N.; post gloriam sequitur i.; gloriam i-ā superare; ex opulentia orta est i.; i-ā æstuare, Sa.; i-ā adductus; i. atque obtrectatio laudis alicujus, Cs.; i-ā Siculi non invenere tyranni majus tormentum, Hor.; rumpi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spricka af)</text:span> i-ā, Vg.; plus i-æ quam laudis; Invidia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personificerad (afundens dæmon),</text:span> Ov. (Met. II. 760 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.);</text:span> cedo i-æ, dummodo absolvar cinis, Phdr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invĭdiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wäcker förargelse, är föremål för owilja, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förhatlig, förarglig; mißhaglig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (impopulär):</text:span> non dubito, quin, etiam si quis i. aut multis offensus videatur, tamen absolvatis, judices; numerus; i-um nomen sapientiæ; i. apud alqm; res est i-a alicui; triumphus ad bonos i.; in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot)</text:span> alqm, C.; nobis miserum, nobis i-um est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot oß en anledning till owilja),</text:span> desertam invadi rem publicam, L.; Vitelliani militis antea i-a petulantia desiderabatur, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wäcker afund, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afundswärd:</text:span></text:span> quæ i-a sunt, laudando et efferendo etiam i-ora facere, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afundsjuk, mißunnsam:</text:span></text:span> vetustas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tiden),</text:span> Ov.; alicui, Ppt.; fortuna, Vell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invĭdiōse</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På ett sätt, som wäcker förargelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">owilja,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot gerningsmannen l. den, mot hwilken hans åtgerder l. ord äro rigtade:</text:span> dicere; meam potentiam i. criminabatur, C.; vivis i., delinquis studiose, loqueris odiose, C. (Her.); nemo pulsus i-ius aut restitutus lætius, quam Cicero, Vell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På ett sätt, som wäcker afund:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invīso</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Invisso), (vīsi), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gå att se</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> eller taga kännedom om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">besöka, bese</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">person, ställe, sak</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquem</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T2">ad aliquem</text:span>): invisses (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">komma att besöka, wistas i)</text:span> pergulam; ad filiam i-am domum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(titta hem till);</text:span> captivos meos, Pt.; res rusticas vel fructus causa vel delectationis; domum, ambulationem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bese);</text:span> puerum; quid tibi necesse fuit sacrificium, quod alienæ domi fieret, i-re?, C.; Lyciam deserit et Delum i-it Apollo; urbes, Vg.; quin præsentes i-imus nostrarum ingenia?, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invīsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> invideo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ogerna sedd, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förhatlig, förarglig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> föremål för owilja l. hat, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mißhaglig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hatad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span>): nos illis esse i-os sentio, Ter.; oratio diis i-a; quo quis callidior, eo i-ior detracta opinione probitatis; persona impura, i-a, C.; Crasso i-us Pompejus, Numidis Romani, Sa.; res, Cs.; Tyndaris, Vg.; i-æ cupressus, Hor.; alicui i-simus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invīsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Osedd, ej sedd; aldrig sedd:</text:span></text:span> morbi visi i-ique, Cato; maribus non i-a solum, sed etiam inaudita sacra, C.; res, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invīsĭtātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Osedd:</text:span></text:span> gens, L., T., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĕrinvīsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket mißhaglig:</text:span></text:span> diis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭbinvĭdeo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något afundas:</text:span></text:span> alicui, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭbinvīsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något illa ansedd, något förhatlig:</text:span></text:span> apud malevolos nomen, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervĭdeo</text:span>, vīdi, (vīsum), 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med ögonen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomskåda; beskåda:</text:span></text:span> sol omnia, Ov.; tua p-es oculis măla lippus inunctis, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skärskåda, pröfwa, taga i betraktande, undersöka:</text:span></text:span> intrandum est in rerum naturam et penitus, quid ea postulet, p-dum, C.; p-eamus, utrum finitum funditus omne constet an immensum pateat vasteque profundum, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inse, begripa:</text:span></text:span> meritorum meorum fieri accessiones, p-re te spero; oportet jam p-ri animi infirmitatem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prævĭdeo</text:span>, vīdi, vīsum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förut se:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På förhand se:</text:span></text:span> venientem p-et ictum, Vg.; p-sos in aqua timet hostia cultros, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förutse, ana, beräkna:</text:span></text:span> futura p., præsentia cernere, C.; p-sa utilitas; nec p-rant impetum hostium milites, neque, si p-issent, satis virium ad arcendum erat, T. (H. IV. 15).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvĭdeo</text:span>, vīdi, vīsum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Se framför sig; förut se:</text:span></text:span> missilia inutilia, ubi, quid petatur, p-ri nequeat, L.; excusare laborem et mercenaria vincla, - quod non p-isset eum, Hor. Ep. I. 7. 69; per imagines, quidquid a tergo fit, p-re, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol. l. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Se sig före; iakttaga försigtighet, försigtighetsmått</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">ne,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">att icke); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">träffa anstalter, sörja för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">ut, ne</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T2">de re</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui rei</text:span>): actum est de te, nisi p-es; te incautum loco demovere potuerunt, p-entem et præcaventem nunquam movebunt; a diis vitæ hominum consulitur et p-etur; in posterum; mederi incommodis hominum, p-re saluti; hæc ut quam rectissime agantur, <text:soft-page-break/>omni cura p-bo, C.; consilio contra difficultates p.; p., ne fiat, Sa.; rei frumentariæ; de re frumentaria, de frumento; hunc ne qua civitas suis finibus recipiat, a me p-sum est, Cs.; p., ne commeatibus privaretur civitas; vidit se magno fore periculo, nisi p-isset, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förutse, ana</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hafwa blick</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beräkna</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquid</text:span>): est boni consulis non solum videre, quid agatur, sed p-re, quid futurum sit; medicus morbum ingravescentem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sjukdomens framsteg)</text:span> ratione p-et; p-sa et exspectata; malum p-sum; consilia eventis ponderamus et, cui bene processerit, multum illum p-isse, cui secus, nihil sensisse dicimus; mala; futura; exitus; conjecturā aliquid; quæ consilio p-ri poterant, cavebantur, C.; verum, Sa.; animo aliquid; nec quid in quaque parte opus esset, p-ri neque imperia administrari poterant, Cs.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förse sig med), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sörja för anskaffandet af; besörja, på förhand anskaffa</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquid</text:span>): rem frumentariam; nihil, Cs.; omnia suis, Sa.; a me ita præcautum et p-sum est, C.; sit bona librorum et p-sæ frugis in annum copia; rem tibi Socraticæ poterunt ostendere chartæ verbaque p-sam rem non invita sequentur, Hor.; omnia, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvĭdens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förutseende), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beräknande; försigtig:</text:span></text:span> qui orientem tyrannidem multo ante prospexerunt, hos prudentes i. e. p-es dicere possumus, divinos nullo modo; tabulas signis amicorum obsignat, p. homo; id et ad brevitatem aptius est et ad reliquas res p-ius, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvĭdenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med klok beräkning; med försigtighet, med förstånd:</text:span></text:span> pro rei copia satis p. exornat omnia, Sa.; ratio Stoicorum p-sime constituta, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvĭdentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förutseende förmåga:</text:span></text:span> p. est, per quam futurum aliquid videtur, antequam factum est, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försigtighet; klok, försigtig beräkning; beräknande förmåga:</text:span></text:span> erat et bello strenuus et bonus consilio, quorum alterum ex p-a timorem, alterum ex audacia temeritatem afferre solet, Sa.; segni uti p-a, Vell.; declinandi p., T.; timoris tormentum memoria reducit, p. anticipat, Sen.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gudomlig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försyn:</text:span></text:span> deorum p-ā administratur mundus; anus fatidica Stoicorum πρόνοια, quam latine licet p-am dicere; materiæ fictrix et moderatrix divina p.; mens mundi p. recte appellari potest, C.; mora deorum p-ā illata, L.; p-ā regitur mundus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förutseende, som eger förmåga att förutse det tillkommande:</text:span></text:span> rerum futurarum, C.; futuri, L.; fati, Tib.; Germani in feminis inesse etiam sanctum aliquid et p-um putant, neque aut consilia eorum aspernantur aut responsa negligunt, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ser sig före, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beräknande, förståndig, omtänksam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (uti att sörja för l. förebygga ngt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skarpsinnig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som har öga för l. bär omsorg för ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">försigtig, warsam:</text:span></text:span> p. sollersque naturæ; animal p-um, plenum rationis et consilii, quem vocamus hominem; auditorum aures moderantur oratori prudenti et p-o; natura consultrix et p-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sörjer för)</text:span> utilitatum et opportunitatum omnium, C.; ego, cui timebo, p. auspex; mens p-a; Ulixes domitor Trojæ multorum p. urbes inspexit, Hor.; posteri satis memoriæ meæ tribuent, si <text:soft-page-break/>majoribus meis dignum, rerum vestrarum p-um, offensionum pro utilitate publica non pavidum credant, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med klok beräkning, omtänksamt:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvīsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förutseende; beräkning; omtanke, försigtighet:</text:span></text:span> multum potest animi p. ad minuendum dolorem; p. posteri temporis; longa animi p-e fugere aliquid; harum rerum una cautio est unaque p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sätt att förebygga);</text:span> vitiorum et incommodorum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvīso</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med beräkning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> temere): T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvīso</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Prōvisso), ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gå att </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Se ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (titta ut) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">efter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn l. ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">se till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">besöka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> p-o, quam mox vir meus redeat; morē hoc fit atque stulte meā sententiā: si quem hominem expectant, eum solent provissere, illa qui causa hercle ocius nihilo venit, Pt. Stich. 641 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.;</text:span> ego ad eos p-o; p-o, quid agat, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvīsor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förutser, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beräknande;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som bär omsorg l. omtanke för:</text:span> ingruentium, dominationum, T.; tardus utilium p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trög att sörja för),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvīsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> u, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blickande framåt, framför sig:</text:span></text:span> proelium tota nocte varium, anceps -: nihil animus aut manus, ne oculi quidem p-u juvabant, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förutseende,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> beräknande af; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">omtanke, omsorg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förebyggande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> dispositu p-uque rerum civilium peritus; periculi; p-u deûm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wisa råd),</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Imprōvĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intet anande, oförberedd:</text:span></text:span> mentes i-as occupare, C.; futuri; i-os et incantos opprimere, L.; hic aliud majus nobis objicitur et i-a pectora turbat, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ej ser l. tänker sig för, utan beräkning l. beräknande förmåga, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wårdslös, owarsam, oförsigtig, tanklös, oförståndig:</text:span></text:span> puerorum ætas i-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(menlös),</text:span> Lucr., C.; i-i et creduli senes; duces i-i et negligentes, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Imprōvĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utan att se sig för; tanklöst:</text:span></text:span> se in præceps dare, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Imprōvīsus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oförutsedd, owäntad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwarpå man ej är beredd); deraf: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwerraskande:</text:span></text:span> omnia, quæ mala putantur, sunt i-a graviora; nulla res est tam i-a, tam nova, de qua se non (philosophi) omnia, quæ dici possunt, profiteantur esse dicturos; sapienti nihil i-um, inopinatum novum accidere potest, C.; metus, Sa.; i-i aderunt; cunctisque repente i-us ait, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i adverbialt bruk:</text:span> improviso, de improviso, ex improviso: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Owäntadt; oförutsedt; utan att någon anar det:</text:span></text:span> medicum tantus i-o morbus oppressit; ex i-o nasci; de i-o incidere in alqd, C.; de i-o celeriusque omnium opinione venerat; i-o unum pagum adortus erat, Cs.; de i-o; ex i-o opprimere, Sa.; i-o facere aliquid, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvĭdeo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter se:</text:span></text:span> nunc ad <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(in till)</text:span> eram r-bo, Pt. (Truc. II. 2. 65; Aul. IV. 2. 33).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvīso</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter gå att se</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> efter, om; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bese; besöka:</text:span></text:span> quando otium tibi sit, ad nos r-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åter titta in till oß),</text:span> Pt. (Truc. II. 4. 79); r-o quid hic gerat, Ter.; r-e nos, C.; domos, L.; te, dulcis amice, r-et cum Zephyris et hirundine prima, Hor.; ipsa Paphon sublimis abit sedesque r-it laeta suis, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvīsĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ideligen besöka:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vidua, Viduertas, -duitas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Viduus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭdŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Resekoffert, kappsäck:</text:span></text:span> Pt. Rud. 545.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ĭdŭlāria, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">titel på ett förloradt skådespel af</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭduus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> dī-vĭdo, dī-vĭduus): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skild ifrån</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">re;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">saknande, beröfwad, öfwergifwen af,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utan), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ensam:</text:span></text:span> me ipse v-us pestes excipio anxias, C. poēt. (Tusc. II. §. 25): v-us pharetrā risit Apollo, Hor.; pectus v-um amoris, Ov.; v. teli, Sil.; ager v. pecudibus, solum arboribus, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utan make</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">maka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (älskare, -rinna); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ogift, ensam, ledig, öfwergifwen, enko-;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭduus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭdua</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungkarl, ogift qwinna; enkling, enka:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om frånskild hustru,</text:span> Pt. Mil. 1409; plures viri nunc sunt v-i quam mulieres; misera fuit Penelope, quæ tam diu viro v-a caruit, Pt.; v-a mulier; mulierum assentator, cognitor v-arum, C.; v-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ogifta)</text:span> cessate puellæ; v-a nox, cubile, manus, Ov.; v-am manere, L.; torus; v-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ensam)</text:span> dormire, Ppt.; crustis et pomis v-as venatur avaras, Hor.; v-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ensamma)</text:span> jacere noctes, Catl.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om träd (jfr</text:span> marito): vitem v-as ducit ad arbores, Hor., Pn.; v-a in nudo quæ vitis nascitur arvo, Catl.; virgines v-æ; cohors v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om Amazonerna),</text:span> Sen. (Med. 215).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭduertas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mißwäxt:</text:span></text:span> Cato <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i ett böneformulär).</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭduĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brist</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utblottadt tillstånd:</text:span></text:span> omnium copiarum, Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enklings-, enkostånd:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭduo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beröfwa, göra tom, blott och bar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fri</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliqua re</text:span>): urbem civibus; arva pruinis, Vg.; foliis v-antur orni, Hor.; rei (<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span>), Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blifwa enkling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">enka:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ienna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Gallien (Vienne).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Viennensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vieo,</text:span> ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> vitex, vitis, vitta): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fläta:</text:span></text:span> corollam, Enn.; v-do facere crates, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viētor</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vitor), ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Korgmakare:</text:span></text:span> Pt. Rud. 990; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bödkare,</text:span></text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> (T.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widja, spö, ris, smidig qwist,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt såsom sättqwist l. flätwerk:</text:span> corpus navis v-bus contextum, Cs.; lentum <text:soft-page-break/>convellere v. (virgultorum), Vg.; agrestes illic fruticosa legebant v-a, Ov.; dictus a v-ne collis = Viminalis, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīmĭnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bär widjor; till flätning tjenlig:</text:span> salix, Col. - collis V. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. absol.</text:span> Viminalis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en af Roms sju kullar, mellan</text:span> Quirinalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Esquilinus.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīmĭnētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widjeskog, buskar:</text:span></text:span> Viminalis dictus a Jove Vimino, quoi ibi aræ: sunt qui (dicant dictum), quod ibi v-ta fuerint, Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīmĭneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widje-, af widjor:</text:span></text:span> fascis, Pt.; tegumenta, Cs.; crates, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flätad, af flätwerk:</text:span></text:span> vagina; navigium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Viesco,</text:span> ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> vieo?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wißna:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viētus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(twåstafwigt,</text:span> Hor.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slak</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (böjlig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wissen, wißnad, skrumpen, slapp; swag, matt:</text:span></text:span> cor (hostiæ); maturitate tempestiva quasi v-um et caducum, C.; senex, Ter.; vestis, Lucr.; membra, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vigeni = Viceni, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Viginti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭgeo,</text:span> ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> vegeo, vigil; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sw. waken):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara frisk, karsk, kry, lifskraftig</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till kroppens och själens lifsfunctioner, ega sina lemmars och sinnens bruk); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara liflig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till kropp l. själ), utweckla lif, liflighet l. werksamhet; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lefwa och röras</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ej blott: hafwa lif):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor (och djur) och deras organ l. förmögenheter:</text:span> corpus dormientis jacet ut mortuum, animus vivit et v-et; animus sentit, sapit, v-et, vivit; memoriā v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa lifligt, starkt minne);</text:span> nos animo tantum v-emus, C.; a tergo Alpes urgent, vix integris vobis et v-tibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(då I woren otröttade och friske)</text:span> transitæ; corpore v-ens; vegetum ingenium in corpore senis v-bat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rörde sig),</text:span> L.; ætas v-et, valet animus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wår ålder är frisk, wårt mod är starkt),</text:span> Sa.; Fama mobilitate v-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(är lifskraftig genom sin rörlighet)</text:span> viresque acquirit eundo, Vg.; Haterius orator impetu magis quam cura v-bat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hans styrka låg mera i passionen, än i sorgfälligheten);</text:span> ætas; abscinduntur venæ: v-ens adhuc mersatur calida aquā, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om wäxter och andra naturföremål: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara frisk, lifskraftig:</text:span></text:span> reserata v-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(frigjord susar)</text:span> genitabilis aura Favoni, Lucr.; quæ stirpibus continentur, arte naturæ vivunt et v-ent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utföra sina lifsfunctioner),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. (jfr</text:span> floreo):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om döda l. abstracta subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wisa sig liflig, werksam; wara i flor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (swang), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">i bruk; göra sig gällande:</text:span></text:span> ita mos, Pt. (Curc. 299); ubi studia nostra v-issent, (si Scipio mei non indiguisset)?; dent operam, ut juvenum industria in omni re v-at; studia militaria v-ent; objurgationes v-ent in amicitia, C.; pro pudore, abstinentia, virtute audacia, largitio, avaritia v-bant, Sa.; invidia; crimina, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara lycklig, mäktig; blomstra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara i anseende, wara berömd:</text:span></text:span> ejus viva facta v-ent, Næv. ap. Gell.; multa secula sic v-uit Pythagoreorum nomen, ut nulli alii philosophi putarentur; in Academia aliquid v-uit; libri tui; laus venandi apud aliquos, C.; purpura (apud Pn.); qui paulo ante victores v-issent, perterriti pacem petiverunt, N.; magnæ v-uere Mycenæ; oppidorum fama v-et, Ov.; <text:soft-page-break/>Jove nil majus generatur ipso nec v-et quidquam simile aut secundum; donec gratus eram tibi, Persarum v-ui rege beatior, Hor.; stabat regno incolumis regumque v-bat consiliis, Vg.; auctoritate; summis honoribus, T. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> XVI. 22).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blifwa liflig, komma i liflig rörelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">werksamhet:</text:span></text:span> pedes, Catl.; copia rerum, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Friskhet, lifskraftighet, karskhet, liflighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (physisk l. andelig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kraft, raskhet:</text:span></text:span> v. juventæ, animi inest alicui, L.: v. redit membris; deest ægro, Ct.; juventas et patrius v. (aquilæ), Hor.; v. ætatis, T.; igneus est ollis (animis) v. et cælestis origo, Vg.; animi, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgōrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rask; kraftig:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervĭgeo</text:span>, ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara mycket kraftig, mäktig, ansedd:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vigesimus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Viginti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭgil,</text:span> ĭlis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> vigeo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waken, waknande; waksam:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lefwande subject och deras ögon m. m.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> prius orto sole v. calamos et scrinia posco; v-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(waksamme)</text:span> canum excubiæ, Hor.; oculi, Vg.; custos; ales <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tuppen);</text:span> gallus v-i provocat ore diem, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waksam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppmärksam:</text:span></text:span> auris, animus, St.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om döda l. abstracta subject:</text:span> cura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(waksam),</text:span> Ov.; ignis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wakande</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ständigt underhållen),</text:span> Vg.; v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wakande</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">brinnande)</text:span> lucernas perfer <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låt stå)</text:span> in lucem, Hor.; nox in castris tuta et v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(waken</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under hwilken wakas, wakt hålles),</text:span> T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgil</text:span>, ĭlis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäktare, nattwäktare, waktpost:</text:span></text:span> nocturnus, Pt.; a v-bus fanique custodibus clamor tollitur, C.; de improviso v-es signa canere, Sa. Jug. 99; portarum v-es proelia temptant, Vg.; v-es Capitolii fefellerat ascendens hostis, L.; adversus incendia excubias nocturnas v-esque commentus est Augustus, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭlia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waka, wakande, waket tillstånd, nattwak:</text:span></text:span> vigila, nisi mavis agitare varius virgis v-as, Pt.; cui non auditæ sunt Demosthenis v-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wakor; nattliga studier)?,</text:span> C.; corpus patiens inediæ, algoris, v-æ; animus impurus Catilinæ neque v-is neque quietibus sedari poterat, Sa.; opes exaggerare quærit omni v-a, Phdr.; Pn. ep. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wakt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wakande för att bewaka ngt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nattwakt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> agere v-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla wakt),</text:span> C.; fessus stationibus v-isque; cura v-arum nocturnarum; munus v-arum senatores obibant, circuitio ac cura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppsigt)</text:span> ædilium erat, L.; v-as habere per urbem, Sa.; non satis diligenter in castris agebantur v-æ, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Embete, ställning, post</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> statio): tradere alteri suam v-am; manere in v-a senatoria, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nattwäkt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (tid af 3 timmar, efter hwilken wakten ombyttes):</text:span> prima v.; tertiā exacta v-ā, C.; per v-as signa canunt, Sa.; de tertia v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under)</text:span> castris egressus, Cs. (b. Gall. I. 12. 33. 40); secundā v-ā in castris minuere ignes, N.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(natt-)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wakt, waktpost,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om de soldater (l. personer i allm.), hwilka bestrida wakthållningen:</text:span> v-as disponere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utsätta),</text:span> Cs.; v-as <text:soft-page-break/>ponere, deducere (id.); ad v-as adesse, Sa.; v-is defendere urbem, C.; v-is, custodiis, stationibus portarum se inserunt, spem offerunt, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭlium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waka:</text:span></text:span> Varr. ap. Non. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭliārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wakthus:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waka, wara waken, hålla sig waken:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> v-antem somniare, dormire; v-ans v-antem vidi, Pt.; somniat ea, quæ v-ans voluit, Ter.; ad multam noctem; de nocte, C.; oculi, Vg.; noctes v-re serenas; v-antem stertere, Lucr.; ad ipsum mane v., Hor.; janitor ad <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för)</text:span> dantes v-et, Ppt.; ad calicem v-anti stertere naso, Juv. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. uttryck:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara waksam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = wara uppmärksam, tänka sig för; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">waka, hålla wakt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = sörja för ngt:</text:span> v-la, ne somno stude, nisi quidem hic agitare mavis varius virgis vigilias, Pt.; excubabo et v-bo pro vobis; pro aliqua re v-re labore et consilio; v-la, ne causam deseras, C.; v-dum est semper, multæ insidiæ sunt bonis, Acc. ap. C.; compita servant et v-ant nostra semper in urbe Lares, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker:</text:span> curæ v-antes, C.; lumina <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lågor, fyrtorns);</text:span> dolor, amor, Ov.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomwaka;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (under nattwak) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">arbeta, förfärdiga, ombesörja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> elucubro): mihi noctes v-antur amaræ; labores; carmina, Ov.; accipe, quæ v-da viris, Vg. Georg. I. 313; frange miser calamos v-taque proelia dele, qui facis in parva sublimia carmina cella, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭlans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waken, waksam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = uppmärksam, försigtig, driftig, sträfsam:</text:span> pax dormientem gubernatorem vel obruere, v-em etiam delectare potest; nemo unquam paratior, v-ior, compositior ad judicium venit; acutus, v., paratus (Cæsar), C.; v-simus, Val.<text:line-break/>(Vĭgĭlans), <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wakande tillstånd:</text:span></text:span> satin eadem in v-ti expetunt, quæ in somnis visa memoras?, Pt. Mil. 392.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭlanter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waksamt, uppmärksamt, sorgfälligt, driftigt:</text:span></text:span> v. provinciam administrare; v. nervoseque eniti, providere; v-sime vehementissimeque vexare hostem, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭlantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förmåga att waka, waksamhet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i egentligaste mening och = uppmärksamhet, sorgfällighet, drift:</text:span> Caninius fuit mirificā v-ā, qui toto suo consulatu somnum non viderit; - vilici labor, frugalitas, v.; Cæsaris horribilis v., celeritas, diligentia, C.; esse summa v-a, Pn.; Vg. G. II. 265.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭlābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wakande:</text:span></text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭlāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waksamt, sorgfälligt:</text:span></text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭgĭlax</text:span>, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ständigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wakande, waksam:</text:span></text:span> curæ, Ov.; canis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Advĭgĭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waka, hålla sig waken wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> heus a-la, Pt.; si a-veris, - conficies, Ter.; ad ignis custodiam a-ant Vestales, C.; infanti, Tib.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvĭgĭlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wakna upp:</text:span></text:span> Pn. ep. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Träget waka ut, hålla ut, dröja wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> in ea re e-arunt curæ et cogitationes meæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waka ut, genomwaka:</text:span></text:span> noctem, Tib.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med nattwak</text:span></text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">flit och möda fullborda, uttänka:</text:span></text:span> consilia cogitationibus tuis e-ta, C.; libros, Ov., Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invĭgĭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waka i, wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara waksam:</text:span></text:span> venatui, Vg.; malis, Ov.; i-ate viri, Col.; curæ animo, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obvĭgĭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hålla sig waken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stå emot sömnen); oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">se upp:</text:span></text:span> o-to opus est, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervĭgil</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Pervĭgĭlis, Ap.), ĭlis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ständigt waken, wakande, waksam:</text:span></text:span> virgo; anguis, Ov.; canis, Sen.; nox <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genomwakad),</text:span> Js. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervĭgĭlia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nattwak:</text:span></text:span> Js.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervĭgĭlium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ständigt nattwak, wakande:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En nattlig fest</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gudstjenst):</text:span> castra Campana, ut in p-o (nocturno sacro, stato sacrificio) neglecta, L. XXIII. 35; sellisternia et p-a celebravere feminæ, quibus mariti erant, T. - P. Veneris, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">titel på en dikt från 3:dje seklet e. Chr. (jfr Lysander, Rom. literaturhist. p.</text:span> 107. 108).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervĭgĭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> natten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">igenom, genomwaka:</text:span></text:span> totam noctem, C.; in armis, L.; in multo nox est p-ta mero, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervĭgĭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom religiöst bruk, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nattfest:</text:span></text:span> in novis deis colendis nocturnas p-es Aristophanes vexat, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīginti</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> dvi-, i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stammen i</text:span> duo, bis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och slutstafwelsen i</text:span> decem), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card. Indecl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugo:</text:span></text:span> unus et v., C.; vigintī tauros, Vg.; quatuor hinc rapimur v. (et) milia rhedis, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīcēni</text:span>, ae, a, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. Num. Distrib.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugo tillsammans, tjugo på hwarje, tjugo åt gången</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">isender:</text:span></text:span> annos v-os nonnulli in disciplina (Druidum) permanent, Cs.; partes habent v-as, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīcēnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugoårs-:</text:span></text:span> lex v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att ingen fick göra lån före 20:de året),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīcēsĭmus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vicensumus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīgēsĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. Num. Ord.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugonde:</text:span></text:span> tertius et v.; altero v-o anno, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīcēsĭma</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugondeskatt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">-afgift</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utgörande 20delen af en summa l. en saks wärde):</text:span> v-a portorii, C.; v-am (peculii) solvere = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">köpa sig fri,</text:span> Petr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīcēsĭmānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till tjugonde legionen:</text:span> miles, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīcēsĭmārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som utgör tjugondedelen af ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugondedels-:</text:span></text:span> aurum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīcessis</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: (as): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugo aß:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīciens</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīcies</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugo gånger:</text:span></text:span> C.; semel atque v., T. - HS v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. ensamt</text:span> v. = 20 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ggr 100,000 sestertier = 2 millioner sestertier,</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Duŏdēvīginti</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(twå från tjugo) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aderton.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēvīginti</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett från tjugo) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nitton.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vigintivir, -viratus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vir.<text:line-break/>Vigor, -goratus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vigeo.<text:line-break/>Vila, Vilica, -lico, -licus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Villa.<text:line-break/>Vilipendo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vilis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīlis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ringa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i pris eller wärde:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som fås för billigt pris, för godt köp, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Billig, ej dyr; simpel,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som ej står i högt pris:</text:span> id v. est XX minis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">minst wärdt);</text:span> annona, Pt., Hor.; natura paucis et v-bus rebus eget; frumentum v-ius; servulus; res v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> pretiosissimæ), C.; nil hic v-e est, nisi mores mali, Pt.; poma, Vg.; aqua; cibus; vinum; ludus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skola);</text:span> v-ius argentum est auro, Hor.; v-i, v-ori <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för godt, bättre pris),</text:span> Pt., Jct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allmän och moralisk mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ringa, simpel, wärdelös, likgiltig; dålig, usel, förkastlig:</text:span></text:span> vobis v. spiritus meus esse non debet, C.; fidem, fortunas, pericula v-ia habere, Sa.; ea vitam v-em fecerant, L.; v. Europe, pater urget absens; scriptores; v-ius argentum est auro, virtutibus aurum, Hor.; v-ia miretur vulgus, mihi flavus Apollo pocula Castaliā plena ministrat aquā, Ov.; v-es neniæ, Phdr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīlĭpendo</text:span>, 3.: (pendo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Akta ringa:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Billighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = godt pris på ngt:</text:span> hæc cognita tibi magis prodessent, quam tritici v.; annonæ, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ringhet, simpelhet; ringa wärde:</text:span></text:span> nominum, Pn.; argentea vasa, non in alia v-e, quam quæ humo finguntur, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Låg uppskattning, förakt:</text:span></text:span> sui, Ct., Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">För godt pris; för lågt pris, litet:</text:span></text:span> constat; venire, Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ringa, utan aktning:</text:span></text:span> colere, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvīlesco</text:span>, lui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Börja aktas ringa; mista anseendet, föraktas, blifwa föraktad:</text:span></text:span> pericula, T.; Claudius princeps e-uit, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervīlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket billig:</text:span></text:span> annona, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvīlesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mista sitt wärde</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anseende:</text:span></text:span> virtus, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Villa</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vīla), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> vicus = vic-la? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> vicus; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Varro = vinula, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwilket hwarken betydelsen l. bildningen gör troligt: det skulle då wara</text:span> = vineola): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gård</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på landet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">landtgård, landthus:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. v. rustica = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bondgård, hemman, afwelsgård:</text:span></text:span> Varro, r. r. I. 13; Col. I. 4; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en sådan</text:span> villa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">borde enl.</text:span> Varro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bestå af twå delar, en för menniskor och en för djur</text:span> (villa fructuaria <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> rustica <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Col.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">byggde hwardera kring sitt gårdsrum</text:span> (cors, chors), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bassiner</text:span> (lacus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för boskapens wattning m. m.: -</text:span> incensæ v-æ, dispersi agrestes, L.; ager cum optima v-a; v-am in Tiburte habes, cortem in Palatio, C.; v-am præterii prudens, Ter.; imminens v-æ (meæ) pinus, Hor.; coloni v-æ, Ap.; v-arum culmina fumant, Vg.; agros vastare, v-as (Numidiæ) expugnare, Sa.; Athenis vivere hominem, non in v-a putes, Pn. ep.; petit v-am cervus, Phdr.<text:line-break/>2. v. urbana (pseudurbana; suburbana, N.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen kallad</text:span> prætorium, St. Silv. I. 3. 25; Su. Tib. 39) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förnäm Romares på stadswis inredda </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Landtgård,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">villa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blott i större dimensioner än husen i staden kunde wara, der angränsande hus inskränkte byggnadsplanen), omgifwen af parker m. m. (i stilen af gymnasia, såsom Roms nuwarande villor utanför portarne, t. ex. Villa Albani och Villa Borghese); beskrifningar på sådana villor finnas i</text:span> Pn. Ep. II. 17; V. 6; Stat. Silv., I. 3; III. 2; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr den. s. k.</text:span> Villa Suburbana M. Arrii Diomedis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på grafgatan i Pompeji (Overbeck,</text:span> II. 328 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.):</text:span> v-as ædificare, L.; Luculli v-arum magnificentiam quam multi imitati sunt!; v. rudis, C.; domus atque v-æ in urbium modum exædificatæ, Sa.; plenissima; cedes coëmptis saltibus et domo v-āque, flavus quam Tiberis lavit, Hor.; v-arum immensa spatia, T. (Ann. III. 25); v. Misenensis Tiberii; splendida, Phdr. (II. 5).<text:line-break/>3. v. publica, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stadsgården, stadshuset,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> kallades en på Marsfältet, således utom Servii Tullii mur, belägen byggnad, der census hölls, utskrifning förrättades o. s. w.,</text:span> Varr. (r. r. III. 2. 7, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwarest förnekas så wäl om den, som om</text:span> villæ urbanæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">att de woro</text:span> villæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentlig mening),</text:span> L. IV. 22.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villātĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gårds</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till gården</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. landtgården </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hörande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som uppfödes </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wid gården,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> skötes </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wid gården:</text:span></text:span> v-a pastio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppfödning, bete);</text:span> genus avium, Varr.; gallina v-is, Pn.; v-us canis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villĭcus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vīlicus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gårdsfogde, fogde, ladufogde, rättare, förwaltare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som hade närmaste ledningen af landtbruket och uppsigt öfwer det öfriga tjenstefolket: wanligen sjelf en slaf):</text:span> v. circulator ne siet; v. rem divinam facito compitalibus in compitis; crebro cum domino putet <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppgöre räkenskaper);</text:span> male agitur cum domino, quem v. docet, Cato; v-o mandata dare, C.; v-e silvarum et mihi me reddentis agelli, Hor.; v-um mercari, instituere; v. vicarius diligentiæ domini succedit; quisquis destinabitur negotio v-i, sit oportebit idem robustissimus scientissimusque, ut edoceat subjectos et ipse commode faciat, quæ præcipit, Col. (XI. 1).<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> attonitæ positus modo v. Urbi (anne aliud tunc - sub Domitiano - præfecti - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">d. w. s. än förwaltande slafwar),</text:span> Juv. V. 77; ærarii, Front.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fogdes hustru; rätterska:</text:span></text:span> officia v-æ; v. juvenis sit, non nimium puella, a vino, a superstitionibus, a somno, a viris remotissima: cura eam subeat, quid meminisse, quid prospicere debeat et c., Col.; Catl., Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villĭco</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villĭcor</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara gårdsfogde, förestå ett landtbruk:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> intr.,</text:span> C., Aus.; possessionem, Ap.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wistas på landet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (it. villeggiare):</text:span> Turp. ap. Non. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förwaltning af ett landtbruk:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subvillĭcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Underfogde</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">vicefogde:</text:span></text:span> Inscr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten landtgård:</text:span></text:span> C., Catl., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>illius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Villosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Villus.<text:line-break/>Villula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Villa. <text:line-break/>Villum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Villus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Logg; ull; ragg:</text:span></text:span> tonsis mantelia v-is, Vg.; ovium; animalia v-is vestita, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Luden, hårig, raggig:</text:span></text:span> leo, Vg.; pectora Caci; ursa, Ov.; radix; lepus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vimen, -mentum, Vimin . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vieo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vin = visne, 2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pers. sing. af</text:span> volo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med det frågande</text:span> ne: Pt., Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vinaceus, -nalis, -narius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vinca pervinca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt</text:span> (chamædaphne): Pn. XXI. 99.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vinceus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">falsk läsart i st. f.</text:span> juncea, Pt. Stich. 639.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vincibilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinco.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vincio,</text:span> vinxi, vinctum, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Linda, wira</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (omlinda, omwira), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">snöra, binda, ombinda, fästa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt; absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">binda, fängsla, fjettra, slå i bojor:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> v. nervis, compedibus; dentes auro v-ti (juncti, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Schoell),</text:span> XII Tabb. fr. 9; virgines matres student esse demissis humeris, v-to <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(snöradt)</text:span> pectore, ut gracilæ sient, Ter.; facinus est v-re civem Romanum, verberare scelus; alqm v-re et constringere, C.; catenis v-tus (ab hoste) trahebatur, Cs.; lapides laqueis v. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slå snaror omkring, fästa - wid,</text:span> Jug. 94), Sa.; nexi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skuldfångar),</text:span> v-ti solutique <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med och utan bojor),</text:span> se undique in publicum proripiunt; edixit consul, ne quis civem Romanum v-tum aut clausum teneret, L.; manūs post terga v.; virginibus Tyriis mos est - suras alte v-re cothurno, Vg.; comas vittā, Ppt.; v-tus comas oleā, Tib.; tempora coronā, floribus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wira, kransa);</text:span> v-tum ire, Hor.; catenis v-tus; lauro, vittis v-re; tela jugo v-ta est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lindad kring -),</text:span> stamen secernit arundo, Ov.; illum v-tum clauso ore in Palatium traxere, T.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i materiel mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Binda, sammansätta, -foga:</text:span></text:span> camera fornicibus v-ta, Sa. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dock:</text:span> juncta, omnes fere libri, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Gerlach);</text:span> tibia orichalco v-ta; Hebrus nivali compede v-tus, Hor.; unda v-ta gelu; nodo aliquid; cortice virgæ v-tæ, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ord: (i rhythmer) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Binda, foga:</text:span></text:span> membra orationis numeris v-re; antiqui verba eligebant, neque eas aut v-bant aut explebant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utfyllde dem till hela, rundade perioder),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i militärisk mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Befästa, innesluta:</text:span></text:span> præsidiis loca, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Binda, lägga band</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngns sinne l. handlingar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fängsla, fjettra:</text:span></text:span> vi Veneris v-tus, Ppt.; omnia, quæ dilapsa jam fluxerunt, severis legibus v-da sunt; religione v-tus et constrictus; mălis v-tum (victum?) studium scribendi, C.; somno v-ta jacebat; inimica v-ximus ora, Ov.; gratā compede (amicæ) v-tus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vinclum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinculum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vinctus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om tal) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bunden; rhythmisk:</text:span></text:span> C., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vinctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vinctūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vinctus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bindning, förband:</text:span></text:span> Cæl., Pn., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vincŭlum</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vinclum</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(poet.),</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Band, snöre, boja, fjettra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> solvite v-a jugis, cado; vincla de pede detrahere, Tib.; corpora constricta v-is, C.; v-a epistolæ laxare, N.; ipse viro primus manicas et arta levari vincla jubet Priamus; stuppea v-a collo (equi) intendunt, Vg.; v-a adhibere alicui; juncea, Ov.; v-a abrumpere alicui, Hor.; vincla tormentorum abscindere; indere alicui, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bojor och band, fängelse:</text:span></text:span> v-is mandare, in v-a abripi, conjici, C., N., Cs.; ex v-is emitti, effugere, N.; in v-is habere alqm; in v-a ducere, Sa.; in v-is publicis decessit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dog),</text:span> interiit, N.; in v-a ducere alqm, L.; ex v-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bojor)</text:span> causam dicere, Cs.; morte, damno, v-is coërcere alqm, C.; esse in v-is, Pn.; vinclis et carcere frenat, Vg.; pugnam aut v-a elapsi, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Band,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som hindrar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fjettra, boja,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. förbinder, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">föreningsband,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. befästar:</text:span> v. amoris, juris, affinitatis; magnum v. est, quod semper iisdem studiis usi sumus; tecum sum reipublicæ v-o conjunctus; v. religionis; nulla te v-a impediunt certæ disciplinæ; v-a temporum te cum illis conjunxerunt; v-a numerorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rhythmens, versens),</text:span> C.; Junoni, cui vincla jugalia curæ, Vg.; v. fidei <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(band på -);</text:span> v-a fugæ, L.; excusare laborem et mercenaria vincla, quod mane domum venisset, Hor.; conjugii; amoris, Tib.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Circumvincio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rundtomkring linda:</text:span></text:span> quasi juncis murteta, item ego vos virgis c-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lägga om),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convinctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbindelse, förbindelsepartikel,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">conjunction:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvincio</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Binda fast, fastbinda, ombinda:</text:span></text:span> Dircam ad taurum d-xere Zethus et Calais; servum, Pt.; propter dolorem artuum d-tus fasciis et multis medicamentis delibutus, C.; opercula plumbo d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fästa),</text:span> L.; tempora lauro, Tib.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Binda, fängsla, lägga band på, slå i band, binda händerna på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hålla i tygel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till stadga:</text:span></text:span> se mero, Pt.; filium conjugio et consuetudine liberali, Ter.; civitates regum dominatione d.; Pompejus omnes gentes tribus triumphis d-rat; Italiam omnibus vinculis d-tam et constrictam tenere; civitates legibus et jure d-tæ; mentem hominis fati necessitate d.; urbem præsidiis, C.; somno, Lucr.; d-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fängslad)</text:span> amore, Vg.; Numa religionibus et divino jure populum d-xit, T. A. III. 26.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fängsla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns uppmärksamhet:</text:span> animos eorum, qui audiebant, d-bat voluptate, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ord: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Binda, foga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till period, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">runda:</text:span></text:span> verba comprehensione d., C. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbinda, förena:</text:span></text:span> se cum aliquo societate; societatem inter aliquos; sanguinis conjunctio d-it homines benevolentia et caritate, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fästa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid sig (winna); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn sig</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">sibi</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förbunden:</text:span></text:span> Cæsar adversarios clementiæ specie; viros primos beneficio in perpetuum tibi tuisque d-isti; summā observantiā et officio sibi alqm; largitione tribus d-tas habere, C.; hunc consuetudine sua sibi adeo d-xit, ut nemo esset perpetuo carior, N.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förpligta, förbinda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> hunc Pompejus omni cautione, foedere, exsecratione d-rat, nihil in tribunatu contrarie se facturum; jure jurando d-tus; foederibus cum hoste d-itur fides (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">man förpligtar sig till),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sakliga object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fästa, tillknyta, befästa:</text:span></text:span> hominum inter homines societatem, C. de Off. I. 22. <text:line-break/>h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inweckla sig i:</text:span></text:span> malā cupiditate <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(olycklig lidelse),</text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvinctus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbunden, tillgifwen, innerligt fästad wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span>): animæ quales non candidiores terra tulit neque quis (quibus) mihi sit d-ior alter, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvincio</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omlinda, -wira, -binda, kransa, kröna:</text:span></text:span> caput <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till hufwudet)</text:span> e-tus foliis; Mnestheus e-tus olivā, Vg.; vittā e-tæ crines, Ov.; Tiridaten insigni regio; caput diademate, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Binda:</text:span></text:span> (Ixion) celeri rotæ e-tus, Sen.; binis quadrigis e-tus in diversa nitentibus, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prævinctus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framtill) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fjettrad, bunden, fängslad:</text:span></text:span> laqueo; voluptatibus, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvincio</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bakbinda:</text:span></text:span> juvenis manus post terga r-tus, Vg.; r-ta est (Andromede), Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppbinda, uppfästa:</text:span></text:span> ancoras catenis, Cs.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.</text:span> = vincio: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Binda, omwira</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt; absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fästa, binda, fastgöra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> stipites ab infimo r-ti; trabes introrsus r-tæ, Cs.; Apollo Delon e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid)</text:span> Mycono Gyaroque r-xit; templum velleribus niveis et festa fronde r-tum, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> mentem amore, Catl.; urbes legibus, Cd.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> recludo, religo) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lösa:</text:span></text:span> alqm, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vinco,</text:span> vīci, victum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Segra, winna; besegra, öfwerwinna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Segra, winna, få öfwerhanden, winna priset, wara öfwerlägsen (få rätt, få sin wilja fram; så som man will):</text:span></text:span> argumentis vicit; vicisti, v-it tua comoedia, Pt.; viceris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(haf det så, det må wara så),</text:span> Ter.; v. judicio, sponsione <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i rättegång, wad),</text:span> C.; v-ite <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gören, låten det wara, som I wiljen),</text:span> Cs.; ea sententia vicit, Cs., L.; si v-ent duumviri, provocante reo, caput obnubito, lex ap. L.; factione respectuque rerum privatarum vicit (in senatu) Appius, L.; vicit fortuna reip.; ea pars in senatu vicit; dicendo, Sa.; v-re Cæcilius gravitate, Terentius arte (dicitur); deprendi miserum est: Fabio vel judice v-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winna, få rätt),</text:span> Hor.; vicimus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wi hafwa wunnit spelet);</text:span> loquendo, Ov.; v-et amor patriæ laudumque arrecta cupido, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i krig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Segra, winna seger, gå af med segren, blifwa segrare:</text:span></text:span> mente agitavit bellum cum Romanis renovare, donicum aut v-issent <text:soft-page-break/>aut v-ti manus dedissent, N.; v. per aliquos; actum erit de republica, uter v-rit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Cæsar eller Pompejus),</text:span> C.; jus esse belli (dixit), ut, qui v-issent, iis, quos v-issent, quemadmodum vellent, imperarent, Cs.; uno plus Etruscorum cecidisse in acie: v-re bello Romanum; v-re noluit exercitus; v-re scis, Hannibal: victoriā uti nescis; in bello Punico secundo propius periculum fuerunt, qui v-runt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(de som blifwit segrare</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">segrarne),</text:span> L. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> I. 48); in acie v.; virtute v., Cs.: manu, Ov.; urbis virtutisque parens sic v-re suevit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wande sig),</text:span> Ppt.; nisi v-itis, pagani, quæ vos alia castra excipient?; bello Othonis et Vitellii id solum scires, deteriorem fore, qui v-isset, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med innehållsaccusativus: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. causam; sponsionem, C.; sicut fortis equus, spatio qui sæpe supremo vicit Olympia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wunnit priset i Olympia),</text:span> nunc senio confectus quiescit, Enn.; v. judicium, C.; hoc v-ite <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillkämpen eder l. gören om intet detta)</text:span> et prohibete nefas, Vg.; v-re erant omnes dignæ, judexque querebar, non omnes causam v-re posse suam, Ov.; bellum v., Vell. II. 55.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bewisa, styrka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt l. att ngt så förhåller sig (med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span>): v-e, virum bonum fuisse Oppianicum, C.; profecto id ita esse, argumentis v-am, Pt.; verbis alqd, Vg. (G. III. 289); ratio hoc v-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">ut</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc. c. inf.</text:span>), Hor. Sat. I. 3. 115; II. 3. 225.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med objectsaccusativus:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: med sakl. och personl. object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Besegra, öfwerwinna, öfwerwäldiga, blifwa herre öfwer, få öfwerhand öfwer, få makt med, slå; kufwa, twinga; beweka:</text:span></text:span> leviter quamvis crebro quod tunditur ictu, v-itur in longo spatio tamen atque labascit; portenta si non v-ta forent, quid tandem viva nocerent?; succidere omnia horrisono v-ta sopore, Lucr.; v-unt illud conducibile gratiæ; v-am animum meum (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låta mitt sinne bewekas),</text:span> ne te dolo fecisse existimem, Pt.; labascit, victust, uno verbo, quam cito!, Ter.; difficultates v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besegra),</text:span> Cs.; peccavi, fateor: v-or (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jag erkänner mig besegrad);</text:span> v-i a voluptate, C.; aliquem beneficiis v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winna);</text:span> gloriā invidiam; injuriam; pravum consilium; divitias; beneficiis v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winna);</text:span> naturam ipsam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> c.), Sa.; v-ti irā bona regia vetuere reddi; somno v-tus; terrore vicit obstinatam pudicitiam, L.; navem vicit hiems; labor omnia v-it improbus; noctem funalia v-unt; v-i nescia pectora; v-tus animi; ramum v. et convellere, Vg.; omnia conando docilis sollertia v-it, Man.; prece v-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bewekt);</text:span> furore v-i: vocibus; fastidia coena; tubas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerrösta),</text:span> Hor.; dolor eum; ocelli v-ti (somno); v-ta jacet pietas; per preces, Ov.; cibum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smälta),</text:span> Pn.; inopiā veri et consensu adulantium v-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förledd)</text:span> Galba sellā levatur, T.; donis v-itur omnis amor; verbis v-ta patefit janua, Tib.; famem, Luc.; v-e obsequendo potius immitem virum; v-am sævos ante leones tigresque truces, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i krig: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Besegra, öfwerwinna, winna seger öfwer -, (slå):</text:span></text:span> victores v-tis hostibus legiones reveniunt domum; vicimus vi feroces, Pt.; hostes vicit et subegit, C.; armis alqm; Galliam bello; jus gentium est, ut v-tis victor ad arbitrium imperitet, Cs.; hostes omnes Agesilaus gravi proelio vicit; v-tus est Xerxes magis consilio Themistoclis, quam armis Græciæ, N.; vicimus perfidos hospites, imbelles hostes; abire Romani ut victores, Etrusci pro v-tis; væ v-tis!, L.; hostem, Ov.; una salus v-tis nullam sperare salutem; insidiis <text:soft-page-break/>v-re alqm; v-isti et v-tum tendere palmas Troes viderunt, Vg.; aleā v-i; non virtute, sed proditione v-i; Arminius proeliis ambiguus, bello non v-tus; minor apud v-tos animus, T.; victrix causa diis placuit, sed v-ta Catoni, Luc.; sociis florentibus et modo v-tis, Juv. - <text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerträffa, öfwergå, wara för mer, högre än</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn i ngt hänseende</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliqua re</text:span>): nox noctem longitudine; alqm veriverbio, Pt.: alqm gloriā, ætate, officio, eloquentiā; alicujus exspectationem; ratio v-it hæc omnia (de Nat. Deor. II.: 18), C.; v-bat omnes cura, diligentia, calliditate et celeritate ingenii, N.; naturam studio, Cs.; carminibus alqm, Vg.; mollitia alqm; præcepta, qualia v-ant Pythagoran Anytique reum doctumque Platona, Hor.; matrem filia; Nestora eloquio; acta patris fortibus actis, Ov.; non me Chaoniæ v-ant in amore columbæ dicere (ɔ: me melius dicant), quos juvenes quæque puella domet, Ppt.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utstå, stå ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en tid, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">genomlefwa; genomfara, -sträfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en rymd:</text:span> vivendo, durando multa secla; æra jactu, Vg.; v-unt æquora navitæ, Hor.; v-da est (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sträfwa upp för)</text:span> alta semita, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Segrare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i krig, täfling, rättegång, företag i allm.; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">segerwinnare, -herre;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen såsom attribut = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">segrande, segerrik, som wunnit</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> v-es victis hostibus legiones reveniunt domum, Pt.; bellorum hostiumque v.; multa v-i eorum arbitrio, per quos vicit, facienda sunt; galli victi silere solent, canere (alacritate quadam et quasi lætitia ad canendum excitari) v-es, C.; v. exercitus, C., Sa., Cs., N., L.; stipendium v-es victis imponere consuerunt; pejus v-bus Sequanis, quam victis Hæduis accidit; v-bus nihil impeditum, victis nihil tutum; v-em discedere, Cs.; pro v-bus agere; animus v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(herre öfwer)</text:span> lubidinis et divitiarum, Sa.; trium bellorum; multis invicem casibus v-es victique, L.; v-em Olympiæ citari, N.; septem ingentia v. fundit humi cervorum corpora; victis redit in præcordia virtus, v-esque cadunt Danai, Vg.; v. pugil; explicuit sua v. arma; v. propositi; v. victo discessit ab hoste; scribēris fortis et hostium v., Hor.; magna intonsis gloria v-or avis, Tib.; currus v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(triumphwagn),</text:span> Ov.; mansit Augusto v-e imperium; v-es implacabili odio victos consectabantur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victōria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Seger</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i krig, twist, täfling m. m.:</text:span> nos exæquat v. cælo, Lucr.; obtinere, referre, reportare, consequi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winna)</text:span> v-am; partā v-ā conservandi sunt, qui non crudeles in bello fuerunt; dare v-am; nihil v-ā dulcius; excidit e manibus; adolescentia Pompeji non offensionibus belli, sed v-is est erudita; externa v.; nocentissima; v. oritur, nascitur ex re, constat re, C.; secunda, N.; civilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwer medborgare),</text:span> Sa., N.; v-am adipisci, Cs.; pugnare pro v-a; v. luctuosa, læta, cruenta, incruenta, varia; v. est in manibus; v-am jam partam eripere alicui; v-æ temperare (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sätta gräns för segrens fullföljande);</text:span> cupido v-æ; v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(politisk seger)</text:span> uti ex lubidine; v-am in plebem crudeliter exercuit nobilitas, Sa.; pessimi exempli v. (Patrum); concedere alicui v-am; v. certaminis, L.; (non) habet v. laudem; tantus amor laudum, tantæ est v. curæ; hic v. vertitur, Vg.: horæ momento venit aut mors aut v. læta; velox, Hor.; ardua; regni, Ov.; litium, Pn.; v. evenit alicui; celerandæ v-æ intentus; magna v. neque cruenta nobis; inquietare v-am, turbare pacem; necessitas in loco, spes in virtute, salus ex v-a; vim, sanitatem, copias, omnia in v-<text:soft-page-break/>a habuere, T. - v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personificerad: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Victoria,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> segrens gudinna:</text:span> in tragoediis vidi Neptunum, Virtutem, V-am, Pt.; templum V-æ; insistebat in manu Cereris simulacrum V-æ, C.; L.; inter utrosque volat dubiis V. pennis, Ov.; rara jugo V. sedit (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hästen sällan wunnit pris),</text:span> Juv. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victōriālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Seger-:</text:span></text:span> dies, Treb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victōriātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med Victorias bild prydt mynt:</text:span> C. Font. 5; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Pn. XXXIII. 3 = 2 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sestertier.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victōriŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten bild af segergudinnan, liten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Victoria:</text:span></text:span> v-as aureas, quæ simulacrorum manibus sustinebantur, tollebat Dionysius, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victōriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Segerrik:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victrīcia</text:span>, (ium), <text:span text:style-name="T2">n. pl. A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Segrande, segerrik:</text:span></text:span> arma, Vg.; fulmina, Ov.; signa, Luc.; bella, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f. A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Segrande, segerrik, seger bådande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förkunnande; segrarinna:</text:span></text:span> legiones v-es; manus in cæde civium sæpe v.; oraculum datum erat, v-es Athenas fore; literæ v-es Cassii in senatu recitatæ; mater v. filiæ, non libidinis, C.; v. libido, L.; Sen. Oct. 299; v-es catervæ; præmia v-is hederæ; naturam expelles furcā, tamen usque recurret et mala perrumpet furtim fastidia v., Hor.; v. redit illa, Vg.: v. Roma; v. inimica, triumpha!; v-e dextra; manus; ratis, Ov.; v-es moræ Fabii, Ppt.; v. causa diis placuit, sed victa Catoni; in sua v-i conversus viscera dextra, Luc.; tu v. (in judicio) provincia ploras, Juv.; framea, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vincĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Möjlig att winna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwerwinna:</text:span></text:span> causa, Ter.; terra, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convinco</text:span>, vīci, victum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personligt object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerbewisa</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">rei, de re, in re</text:span>): aliquam de re, Pt.; c-i criminibus nefariis, multis testibus; hæc duo levitatis et infirmitatis plerosque c-unt; judicio c-tus; negligentiæ; in aliquo scelere c-i, C.; facinoris, Sa.; veris, L.; scelere, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakligt object:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bewisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt på ngn, (ofördelaktigt) om ngn:</text:span> eum ratio c-it ne liberum quidem esse; peccata argumentis; causa c-ta et damnata (pro Cl. 7), C.; iis aut fortunam defuisse aut avaritiam esse c-tam, Cs.; furor c-tus, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bewisa falskheten, orimligheten af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wederlägga:</text:span></text:span> quid negotii est ista poētarum et pictorum portenta c-re?; peccata Epicuri; oratio c-i non potest, C.; non possunt alios alii c-re sensus, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvinco</text:span>, vīci, victum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fullkomligt besegra, öfwerwinna; nedslå, krossa, i grund slå:</text:span></text:span> consilia doctorum fortuna, Pt.; iis, quos vi deviceris, consulendum est; Poenos bello, classe; urbs d-ta, C.; bonum publicum privatā gratiā d., Sa.; virtute militum hostium exercitus d.; classis d-ta est; multorum obtrectatio unius devicit virtutem, N.; d-tis Sabinis, L.; Galliam, Aquitaniam, gentes, Cs.; d-ta urbe, Vg.; acrem militiam paras non ante d-tis Sabæis, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med seger sluta:</text:span></text:span> d-ta bella, Vg. Aen. X. 370.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvinco</text:span>, vīci, victum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Med seger komma ifrån), sträfwa öfwer, igenom; genombryta; öfwerstå, utstå:</text:span></text:span> amnis molem; arbor nemus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(höjer sig öfwer);</text:span> dolorem, Sen.; morbum, Col.; Charybdin remis; fretum, æquora, Ov.; luridaque e-tos effugit umbra rogos, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerwinna; beweka:</text:span></text:span> Aeduos (bello); donis alqm; ad miserationem e-tus, T.; platanus e-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(undantränger)</text:span> ulmos, Hor.; lacrimis, Sen.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomdrifwa, åstadkomma:</text:span></text:span> e-unt, ut sibi literæ ad Tarquinios darentur, L. II. 4.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invictus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oöfwerwunnen:</text:span></text:span> morior i., N.; cestibus, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oöfwerwinnelig, okuflig; ointaglig; omöjlig att besegra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">eröfra, kufwa; obeweklig:</text:span></text:span> a labore i-um se præstitit; Hannibal; imperator i-simus; civis; defensio, C.; Romani i-i ab hostibus, imperatores gentium; adversus divitias animus (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omutlig),</text:span> Sa.; i-i Germani, Cs.; Juppiter; Cæsar; sit Medea ferox i-aque; vindemiator i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(styf = som ej gifwer efter i ordwexling),</text:span> Hor.; gens; eripe me his, i-e (Aenea), mălis, Vg.; corpus i-um a vulnere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(osårbar),</text:span> Ov.; arx i-sima, T.; ignibus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invincĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oöfwerwinnelig:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervinco</text:span>, vīci, victum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Segrande tränga igenom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fram; winna, genomdrifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt</text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">att</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">ut, ne</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sin wilje, mening</text:span>]: ergo vivida vis animi pervicit; hoc difficile est p-re dictis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bewisa),</text:span> Lucr.; restitit ac pervicit Cato, C.; hoc est tibi p-dum (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kämpa dig till),</text:span> Catl. 76. 11; non potuit p-re, ut de agris dividendis plebi referrent consules ad senatum; ipsa virtus pervicit, ne in ullo genere hominum inhonorata esset, L.; Bardanes pervicit, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fullkomligt besegra, öfwerwinna:</text:span></text:span> subdolā perfidiā p-i, Pt.; rationibus alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwertyga),</text:span> L.; sonum p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerrösta),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvinco</text:span>, vīci, victum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Besegra, nedslå, förswaga, kufwa:</text:span></text:span> vires, Lucr.; catervæ hostium r-tæ, Hor.; conjuratio coepta, adulta, r-ta, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerbewisa; wederlägga:</text:span></text:span> judicio alqm, C.; crimina rebus r-ta, L.; alqm in culpa, Gell., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvictio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederläggning:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vinct . . ., Vinculum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vincio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>indĕlĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Vindĕlĭci, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">vindelicisk, Vindelicier, (illyriskt?) folkslag wid Donau:</text:span> Augusta V-orum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Augsburg i Schwaben.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vindem . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vindex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: (vis, dico?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förswarare:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i juridisk mening = den, som förswarar ngn från att föras i fängelse:</text:span> v. ab eo (dicitur), quod vindicat, quominus is, qui prensus est ab aliquo, teneatur, Fs. 376 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">M.;</text:span> assiduo v. assiduus esto: <text:soft-page-break/>proletario jam civi quis volet, v. esto, XII. Tabb. Gell. (XVI. 10; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Schoell,</text:span> XII. Tabb. p. 116. 117); æris alieni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för skuld),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förswarare, beskyddare, hämnare, -rinna:</text:span></text:span> tabella (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den slutna omröstningen)</text:span> v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wärn)</text:span> libertatis, C., L.; periculi, L.; nec deus intersit, nisi dignus v-e nodus inciderit (in fabula), Hor.; v. ultorque parentis, Ov.; forsitan v. deus exsistet aliquis lætus et veniet dies, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnare, bestraffare, -rinna:</text:span></text:span> rerum capitalium, Sa.; v. cupiditatum, conjurationis, C.; poena, Catl.; fraudis; magnæ linguæ, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindĭcia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindĭciæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inför rätt gjordt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rättsanspråk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">besittningstagande af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en sak l. person:</text:span> de qua re disceptatur in re præsenti, sive ager sive quid aliud est, cum adversario simul manu prendere et in ea re sollennibus verbis vindicare, id est v-a, Gell. XX. 10.— <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om parterna sades:</text:span> v-as ferre rei, v-is petere aliquid, C. Mil. XXVII. 74; postulare v-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besittningsutslag),</text:span> L. III. 44.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om prætorn, domstolens ordförande, hette det:</text:span> v-as decernere, dicere, dare = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tilldöma besittning; gifwa, fälla besittningsutslag:</text:span></text:span> secundum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till förmon för)</text:span> libertatem, secundum servitutem, in servitutem a libertate; cedere v-is, L. III. 47. 57.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnd, straff:</text:span></text:span> scelerum v-æ, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindĭco</text:span>, 1.: (vindicit, XII. Tabb. ap. Gell. XX. 1. 45): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i juridisk mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra anspråk gällande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på sak l. person; ställa sig såsom ngns förswarare</text:span> (vindex) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och derigenom befria honom från att föras i häkte, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">försätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en person </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">i frihet, befria:</text:span></text:span> in jus ducito. Ni judicatum facit aut quis endo eum jure vindicit, vincito aut nervo aut compedibus, XII Tabb. l. c.; cum adversario simul (rem) manu prendere et in ea re sollennibus verbis v-re, Gell. XX. 10 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> vindiciæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> vindex); v-atur Virginia spondentibus propinquis; in libertatem v. alqm, L.; agere lege et v-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bild),</text:span> C. de Or. I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cap.</text:span> 10.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allmännare mening:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra anspråk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillegna sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquid sibi, ad se</text:span>): quod est oratoris pro - prium, apte, distincte, ornate dicere, si id mihi assumo, videor id meo jure quodam modo v-re; non nobis solum nati sumus ortumque nostri partem patria v-at, partem amici; Chii Homerum suum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom sin)</text:span> v-ant, C.; libertatem, Cs.; jure suo nonnulla ab imperatore miles, plurima vero fortuna v-at, N.; partem gloriæ ad se v., L.; urbem (ɔ: Athenas) Neptunus; v-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(återfordra åt Io</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">återgifwa)</text:span> antiquam faciem vultusque ferinos detrahat (Juppiter), Ov. Met. II. 523.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försätta i frihet; befria, wärja, frisäga, hålla fri, frälsa, rädda, förfäkta, förswara, hämna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= skaffa ngn hämnd): -</text:span> civem ab ignotissimo Phryge v-etis; turpitudo personæ ejus, in quem liberius invehimur, v-bit nos; ætas me a verberibus v-at; alqm in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i)</text:span> libertatem v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(försätta);</text:span> alqm ab impetu, a labore; a miseriis morte v-ri; laudem alicujus ab oblivione hominum, C.; Galliam in libertatem; naves a periculo, Cs.; plebem, Græciam in libertatem, Sa., N.; mortem alicujus v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hämna),</text:span> Sa.; armis alqm, Vg.; a crimine alqm; <text:soft-page-break/>ad saxa revinctam Hesionen v., Ov.; se a, de re, Sen., Pn.; flebunt Germanicum etiam ignoti, v-bitis vos, si me potius, quam fortunam meam fovebatis, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnas, taga hämnd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngn l. för ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">straffa, bestraffa, stäfja, förhindra, afwärja</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquem, in aliquem</text:span>): non modo in socios, sed etiam in cives militesque nostros sæpe est severe vehementerque v-tum; Tib. Gracchi conatus perditos v-vit Scipio; maleficia acerrime: aliquid graviter, supplicio; dolum legibus: scelus in alqm; peccatum in aliquo, C.; in alqm, Sa., Cs.; manu v., Sa.; serpentem, Ov.; in mea sortitā v-et ossa pilā (Aeacus), Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Laga anspråk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt:</text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnande, hämnd, förswar:</text:span></text:span> v. est, per quam vis et injuria et omnino, quod obfuturum est, defendendo aut ulciscendo propulsatur, C. (de Inv. II. 53).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindicta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Högtidlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inför prætor skeende </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">befrielse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frigifning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en slaf, enligt</text:span> Schol. ad Ps. V. 88 = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frihetsstaf,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en staf</text:span> (virga; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eljest kallad</text:span> festuca), qua manumittendi a prætore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se nedanför)</text:span> in capite pulsantur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Becker, Röm. Alterth.</text:span> II. 1. 66 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.):</text:span> auctor v-æ jam venit ipse tuæ (i. e. patronus tuus), Ov. Fast. VI. 676; si neque censu neque v-a neque testamento liber factus est, liber non est, C. Top. 2. §. 10 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(härtill Boethius:</text:span> v. est virgula, quam lictor manumittendi servi capiti imponens servum in libertatem vindicabat, dicens quædam verba sollennia, atque ideo illa virgula v. vocabatur); ille (servus, qui conjurationem contra libertatem factam ad consules detulit, L. II. 4) primum dicitur v-ā liberatus. Quidam v-æ quoque nomen tractum ab eo putant: Vindicio ipsi nomen fuisse, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnd, förswar:</text:span></text:span> legis; libertatis, L.; legis, Vell.; ira procedit ad v-am sui, Val.; professa perdunt odia v-æ locum, Sen.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnd, straff:</text:span></text:span> facilis v. est mihi, sed inquinari nolo ignavo sanguine, Phdr.; venire v-æ properum; modo tardari metu, modo cupidine v-æ inardescere, T.; capitale exemplum v-æ, Pn.; at v. bonum vita jucundius ipsa, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>indonissa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Belgien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vine . . ., Vinibua <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>īnĭcius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Vīnĭciānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vinifer, -nipollens, -nitor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>inius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn</text:span> (Cons. cum Galba Imp. 69 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">e. Chr.).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vinnŭlus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smekande, söt:</text:span></text:span> oratio, Pt.; v. dicitur molliter se gerens et minime quid viriliter faciens, Paul. Diac. 377. 7; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Isid. = mollis et flexibilis, a vinno = cincinnus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vinolent . . ., Vinosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīnum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Win</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i betydelsen winer, winsorter,</text:span> Varr. IX. 66. 67, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och i allm. poet.):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. (om drycken):</text:span> meri v-i hirnea; flos veteris v-i naribus meis <text:soft-page-break/>objectus est: v-o conspergere fores; cedo cantionem pro veteri v-o novam, Pt.; v. novum, vetus; fugiens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skämdt);</text:span> non omne v. vetustate coacescit; v. fert ætatem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(håller sig);</text:span> nimia vetustas v-i; v. vetustate evanescens; v. lene, meracius, C.; v-o obrutus, N.; v. adventitium, Sa.; v-o incaluit, T.; v. generosum et lene; v-a liques et spatio brevi spem longam reseces; v-i fons; laudes v-i; exsiccat culullis v-a Syra reparata merce, Hor.; indulgere v-o; v-a cadis onerarat Acestes; v-o sepultus, Vg.; proximi Rheno Germani et v. mercantur, T.; v. ex napis, Pn.; forte, Col.; purum; calidum; gravis v-o; nimii v-i homo; v-a mera; v-a dant animos; bibere, libare, fundere, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winstock, drufwa:</text:span></text:span> pendens, Cato; serere v., Varr.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drickande, dryckeslag; dryckenskap:</text:span></text:span> persuasit nox, amor, v., adolescentia; in v-o immodestus, Ter.; ad v. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i dryckeslag),</text:span> C.; per v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= i dryckeslag l. i drucket tillstånd),</text:span> Pt., C.; nec regna v-i sortiere talis nec tenerum Lycidam mirabere; libera v-a referre; inter v-a fugam Cinaræ mærere protervæ; quis post v-a gravem militiam crepat?, Hor.; v-a diem celebrent: non festa luce madere est pudor, Tib.; in v-um pronus, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Villum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Litet win</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (rus):</text:span> edormiscam hoc villi, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnācea</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drufwans hylsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (l. skinn):</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnāceum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnāceus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winbärskärne, drufkärne:</text:span></text:span> acini v-o, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">winets, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Win-:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnālia</text:span>, (ōrum, Mcb.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winfest,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fest för winskörden i April och Augusti:</text:span> Varr. l. l. VI. 56; Ov. Fast. IV. 863.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Win-,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som är för win, har afseende på win:</text:span> cella, Pt.; lacus, Cato; vas, C.; saccus, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winhandlare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winkärl, -fat:</text:span></text:span> vesculum v., Pt. Trin. 888 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Fl.;</text:span> invertunt Allifanis v-a tota, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindēmia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (demo?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winbergning, winskörd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i abstract och collectiv mening:</text:span> uber, Varr.; mitis, Vg.; exigua; gracilis; modicas colligere v-as, Pn.; facere v-as, Col.; vendere v-as, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skörd:</text:span></text:span> mellis; olearum; turis, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindēmiālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindēmiārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till winbergning hörande:</text:span> vas, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindēmio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hålla winskörd; plocka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (drufwor):</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindēmiātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winbergare, wingårdsman:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindēmĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: id.: Sen. ludus.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vindēmiŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten winskörd; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skörd, inkomst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> C. Att. I. 10. 4.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winland, winberg, wingård:</text:span></text:span> C., Vg., Hor.; ut v-a egomet cædam mea, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ordspråk = hugga på l. critisera sig sjelf, tala förklenande om sig sjelf,</text:span> Hor. Ep. II. 1. 220.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Win-:</text:span></text:span> latex, Sol. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnea</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winplantering, winträd</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">löfsal</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af winrankor med deras stödjeträ, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wingård, winberg:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> instituere v-am; segetibus et v-is et pratis res rusticæ lætæ sunt, C.; curvis purgatur v. rastris, Catl.; largo pubescit v. fetu; seras posuit v frondes; rastros patietur humus, v. falcem, Vg.; verberatæ grandine v-æ, Hor.; fame coacta volpes alta in v-a uvam appetebat summis saliens viribus, Phdr.; fodere, palare v-am, Col.; v. floret, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stormtak, -hus,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som anwändes till skydd wid belägringar (i form af en winplantering l. löfsal af winstockar med de stänger och twärträ, kring hwilka de slingra och stödja sig; jfr</text:span> jugatio, Veg.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Marquardt</text:span> III. 2. 476): v-am pluteosque agere ad alqm, Pt. Mil. 266; v-is aliisque operibus urbem oppugnare; locus procul muro satis æquus v-is agendis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framköra, framrulla),</text:span> L.; v-is ac testudinibus constitutis propius urbem accessit, N.; v-is expugnare; v-as incendere, Sa.; v-as agere, Cs., Sa.; v-is partem castrorum obtegere; v-æ contextæ viminibus, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīneālis</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīneārius</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīneātĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winlands-, wingårds-:</text:span></text:span> terra v-lis; collis c-ius, Col.; falx v-ca, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnĭbua</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Windrinkerska:</text:span></text:span> Lucil. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winbärande:</text:span></text:span> vitis, Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnĭpollens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som råder för winet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winets herre</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> armipotens): Liber, Pt. Curc. 114.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wingårdsman:</text:span></text:span> (vitis), C.; maturæ v. uvæ, Vg.; Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnĭtōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wingårds-:</text:span></text:span> falx, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnŏlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drucken, rusig:</text:span></text:span> v. compressit mulierculam, Ter.; in violentiam v-orum incidere; furor; v-um inter sobrios bacchari; hæc vobis videntur consilia siccorum, an v-orum somnia?, C.; v-i interfecti sunt ab hostibus, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begifwen på dryckenskap</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fylleri; drinkare, supare:</text:span></text:span> Thraces homines v-i rebusque venereis dediti, N.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dränkt i win, rusgifwande:</text:span></text:span> medicamentis v-is curari, C. (in Pis. 6). <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnŏlentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dryckenskap, fylleri:</text:span></text:span> ligurritio, v., cupedia; furiosa v., C</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Älskare af win; drinkare, begifwen på dryckenskap; utswäfwande i dryckom:</text:span></text:span> lena v-sima, Pt.; laudibus arguitur vini v-us Homerus, Hor.; senex; ætas; convivium, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. sapor v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stark winsmak),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invīnius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nykter:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vio, Viocurus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Via.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Viŏla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Viol:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Violblomma:</text:span></text:span> quid tum, si fuscus Amyntas? et nigræ v-æ sunt et vaccinia nigra; pallentes v-æ, Vg.; lana Tarentino v-as imitata veneno, Hor.; alba; lutea, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Violfärg, violett färg:</text:span></text:span> tinctus v-ā, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Violfärgad, violett:</text:span></text:span> purpura, N. ap. Pn.; flos; color, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Violplantering; blomstersäng, -rabatt:</text:span></text:span> irriguumque bibant v-a fontem, Vg.; v-a et myrtus - spargent olivetis odorem, Hor. II. 15. 5.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som färgar violgrått:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Viol . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Vis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīpĕra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Huggorm:</text:span></text:span> venenata, C.; atra, Hor.; sub præsepibus mala tactu v. delituit, Vg.; si fallo, v. nostris sibilet in tumulis et super ossa cubet, Ppt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. om en hätsk (giftig) menniska:</text:span> v-am nutricare sub ala (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sin egen barm),</text:span> Petr.; tandem, v., sibilare desisti, Fl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīpĕreus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīpĕrīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Huggorm-, orm-:</text:span></text:span> morsus v-nus, C.; sanguis v-nus, Hor.; fel, fauces, monstrum v-eum, Ov.; v-a anima <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(andedrägt),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ipsānius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn</text:span> (M. Vipsanius Agrippa).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭr,</text:span> viri, (<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen. pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ofta</text:span> virum), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Man:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (= fullwuxen person af mankön, mots.</text:span> femina, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">synonymt, men ej identiskt med</text:span> mas), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">karl;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> stundom med swagare eftertryck om förut omtalad person</text:span> = ille: utrum tu masne an femina es, qui illum patrem voces? Vir sum equidem. Quære, v., porro patrem. Virile secus ego nunquam habui; ea pudica est necdum cubat cum v-is; v-i principes; vide, ut extimuit mulier, postquam ted aspexit. - V-i quoque armati id faciunt; procede, bone v., lepidum mancupium meum. Bonus v. nunquam fui, Pt.; hoc male habuit v-um; v-um me natam vellem, Ter.; ea sacra v-i oculis aspici fas non est; v consularis; v. bonus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> bonus, justus, honestus, sapiens); summi in nostra civitate v-i, C.; hunc unum plurimæ gentes consentiunt populi primarium fuisse v-um, Inscr. ap. C.; = ille, Sa. Cat. 25, Jug. 9; v. fortis et magnanimus; causa efficiens magnos v-os, C.; pugnatum est ab hostibus ita, ut a fortibus v-is in extrema spe salutis, Cs.; v. cetera egregius, L.; nulla v-o juranti femina credat, Catl.; tandem desine matrem tempestiva sequi v-o; dissimulant et nube cava speculantur amicti, quæ fortuna v-is, classem quo litore linquant; arma, v-i, ferte arma, Vg.; turpes v-i (eunuchi), Hor.; femina virque, Tib., Ov.; non alius feminis, quam v-is, habitus, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt i fråga om krig: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Man,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofta i mots. till hästar; fotknekt i mots. till ryttare:</text:span> magnanimi v-i, freti virtute et viribus; dispertiti v-i, dispertiti ordines; cadunt volnere v-i virûm, Pt.; cum his equis v-isque, ut ajunt, pugnandum est, C.; v. v-um legit; equites v-ique, L.; hæret pede pes densusque v-o v.; obvius adversoque occurrit seque v-o v. contulit; audetque v-is concurrere virgo, Vg.; mors et fugacem persequitur v-um; heu, heu quantus equis, quantus adest v-is sudor!, Hor.; fulgentes armis v-isque campi, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Man</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i mots. till gosse:</text:span> pueroque v-oque, Ov. (Met. XIII. 397; IX. 417); v., non puer, Pn.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i prægnant mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Man, karl</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = man med kraft </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(hjelte)</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i physisk och moralisk mening), mod, character:</text:span> vos etenim juvenes animum geritis muliebrem, illa virago v-i, Enn. ap. C.; eu noster, <text:soft-page-break/>laudo: tandem perdoluit: v. es, Ter.; quod viriliter animoque magno fit, id dignum v-o et decorum videtur: quod contra, id, ut turpe, sic indecorum; Marius rusticanus v., sed plane v.; v-um videri negant Peripatetici, qui irasci nesciat, C.; virorum more; vestrum est, si viri esse vultis, Sa.; tota in alterum Tarquinium versa (Tullia) eum mirari, eum v-um dicere, spernere sororem, quod v-um nacta cessaret muliebri audacia, L.; arma v-umque <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hjelte)</text:span> cano, qui -, Vg.; si quid in Flacco v-i est -, non patietur, Hor.; si v. es, i, dictas exige dotis opes, Ov.; feminis lugere honestum est, v-is meminisse; mollitiam corporis objectante accusatore prorupit reus: interroga -: v-um me esse fatebuntur, T.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Man; äkta man; make:</text:span></text:span> advenientem me solebas antidhac appellare itidem, ut pudicæ suos v-os, quæ sunt, solent; ego præter alios meum v-um fui rata siccum, frugi, continentem, amantem uxoris maxume; da mihi, vir, Calendis qui meam matrem munerem, Pt.; omnibus uxoribus v-is esse advorsas æque studium est, similis pertinacia; qui scis id, mi v.?, Ter. Hecyr. II. 1. 5. 38; v-i quantas pecunias ab uxoribus dotis nomine acceperunt, tantas ex suis bonis cum dotibus communicant, Cs.; mulier genere atque forma, præterea v-o, liberis satis fortunata fuit, Sa.; Tanaquil excelsa et alta sperare complexa v-um jubet; secretis v-i alieni assuefacta sermonibus nullis verborum contumeliis parcere de v-o ad fratrem, de sorore ad (illius) v-um, L.; v. meus, Ov.; v. gregis (caper); v-o jungere filiam; Creūsa defuit et comites natumque v-umque fefellit, Vg.; sævo nupta v-o, Hor.; puella quum par connubium maturo tempore adepta est, cara v-o magis et minus est invisa parenti, Catl.; subscribam: salvo grata puella v-o, Ppt. (V. 3. 72); imperat v-o (uxor), Juv.; v-um et parentem retinuit Julia, Luc. <text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mots. till gud l. halfgud (heros):</text:span> quem v-um aut heroa lyra vel acri tibia sumis celebrare, Clio, quem deum?, Hor.<text:line-break/>7. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mannen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = manlig kraft l. manlige födslodelar:</text:span> membra sine v-o, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Qwinna,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> enl.</text:span> Fs. p. 261 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Muell.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Manhaftig:</text:span></text:span> Varr. ap. Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrīlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Manlig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= som tillhör l. utmärker l. är för man i motsats till qwinna: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">För män; mans, männers, karla-:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> v-e secus (liberos) ego nunquam habui, Pt.; balneæ, Cato; Clodius ea sacra, quæ viri oculis ne imprudentis quidem aspici fas est, non solum aspectu v-i, sed flagitio stuproque violavit, C.; calcei v-es, Varr.; v-em sexum non reliquit, N.; v. stirps <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afkomma)</text:span> ex matrimonio fuit, L.; v. pars <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= manlig könsdel),</text:span> Lucr.; v. cultus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(drägt och wapen),</text:span> Hor.; proles, Vg.; contactus; manus; coetus v-es fugere; stirps; vox, Ov.; duos v-is sexus simul enixa est, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i gramm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Masculin:</text:span></text:span> vocabulum, nomen, Varr., Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Manlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som tillhör man i motsats till gosse, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">manna-, mans:</text:span></text:span> toga v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som</text:span> sumebatur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid 17:de året, då</text:span> prætexta ponebatur), C.; v. ætas (A. P. 166); - ne forte seniles mandentur juveni partes pueroque v-es; vestis, Hor.; puer curam gerens v-em, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Manlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som anstår män (wanligen i god, någon gång i sämre </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mening); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">manhaftig, karlawulen:</text:span></text:span> v. animus, C., Sa., Hor., Ov.; oratio; dolor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(harm),</text:span> C.; ingenium; audacia, Sa.; ecquid in antiquam virtutem animosque v-es et pater Aeneas et avunculus excitat Hector?, Vg.; vultus, Hor., Ov.; Agrippina æqui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jemnlikhet)</text:span> impatiens, dominandi avida, v-bus curis feminarum vitia exuerat, T.; compositio verborum, Qu.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Personlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som tillhör en enskild l. wid en delning kommer på hans lott, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">enskild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i sw. oftast icke att öfwersätta annorlunda, än med ett eftertryckligt betonadt pron. possessivum: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">min, din</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.):</text:span> plus etiam quam pro v-i parte obligatus; est aliqua mea pars v., C.; juvabit rerum gestarum memoriæ principis terrarum. populi pro v-i parte <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för min del, efter min förmåga)</text:span> et me ipsum consuluisse, L.; actoris partes chorus officiumque v-e defendat, Hor.; pro v-i portione, T., Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrīlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Manlighet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">manlig förmåga, manlige könsdelar:</text:span> (homo) ademptæ v-is, T.; excisa, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mannaålder:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Manligt wäsende:</text:span></text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrīlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Manligt; med mannamod; som det anstår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">höfwes en man; som en man:</text:span></text:span> facere; ægrotare, C.; sedit, qui timuit, ne non succederet: esto. Quid? qui pervenit fecitque v.?, Hor.; ferre aliquid, Ov.; v-ius dicere sententiam, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrĭpŏtens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraftig:</text:span></text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Manbar:</text:span></text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrītim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Man för man; man mot man; hwarje serskildt; hwar för sig; ur hand i hand:</text:span></text:span> præda v. divisa, Cato; agrum v. dividere, C.; milites v. legerat, N.; pecus v. distribuere, Cs.; commonefacere v. (milites) beneficii sui, Sa.; si tam novitas Græcis invisa fuisset, quam nobis, quid nunc esset vetus aut quid haberet, quod legeret tereretque v. publicus usus?, Hor.; nondum aperta conjuratione, at v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hos hwarje enskild)</text:span> promptis studiis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Giftaslysten, -sjuk, älskogssjuk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om qwinnor):</text:span> non bibosa, non mammosa, non v-a, non loquax, ap. Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virtus</text:span>, ūtis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mandom, mannamod; tapperhet;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tappra handlingar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bragder; hjeltebedrifter:</text:span></text:span> v. ex viro appellata est: viri autem maxime propria est fortitudo; rei militaris; bellandi; præstare v-e, C.; per v-em (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ärans bana; hjeltedöden)</text:span> mori; v-i militum confidere; pristina v.; v-e certare cum strenuo, Sa.; Helvetii reliquos Gallos v-e præcedunt, Cs.; tam bellatorem Mars se haut ausit dicere neque æquiperare suas v-es ad tuas; v-e et forma et factis invictissimus, Pt.; v-e militum copias hostium devicit; desperare de v-e alicujus, N.; v-esque virosque -; dolus an v., quis in hoste requirat?, Vg.; reges ex nobilitate, duces ex v-e sumunt (Germani), T.; spectata per labores; temeraria; hic v-is honos, Ov.; stimulos dedit æmula v., Luc.; tunc est probanda, si locum v. habet, Sen. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allmännare betydelse:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personers:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraft,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stor) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förmåga, duglighet, dugtighet, skicklighet, förtjenst, företräde, talent:</text:span></text:span> cape sis v-em animo et corde expellas desidiam tuo, Pt.; confestim notæ (Cimonis) v-is (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">statsmannaskicklighet)</text:span> consecutum est desiderium; in Græcorum v-bus exponendis mores eorum secuti sumus; ut eluxit v-bus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(talenter),</text:span> sic vitiis obrutus est, N.; ex v-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förtjenst, duglighet)</text:span> coepit nobilitas; ad v-em accendi; v. hebescit, Sa.; in novo populo omnis ex v-e nobilitas, L.; aditus ad illum summum ordinem civium industriæ ac v-i patebat; oratoris vis v-que; v. dicendi; animi v-es non voluntarias <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se</text:span> 2) vincunt v-es voluntariæ, quas quidem proprie v-es appellamus, C.; diserti v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(talaretalent)</text:span> Messalæ, Hor.; multa viri v. animo multusque recursat gentis honos; gratior est pulcro veniens in corpore v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förtjensten);</text:span> eos ardens evexit ad æthera v.; conscia v., Vg.; haud facile emergunt, quorum v-bus obstat res angusta domi, Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i moralisk mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dygd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (såsom en persons hela wäsen), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sedlighet</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">syn.</text:span> honestas), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ädel character; dygd,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">dygder:</text:span></text:span> v. (est) quærendæ rei finem scire modumque, Lucil.; animus ubi v-is via grassatur, abunde potens pollensque est, Sa.; non sunt audiendi, qui v-em duram et ferream quandam esse volunt; v. et conjungit et conservat amicitias; alii se ad philosophiam, alii ad jus civile applicant - ipsarumque v-um in alia alius mavult excellere: v-bus ornatum esse; omnis v. nos ad se allicit facitque, ut eos diligamus, in quibus ipsa inesse videatur; hæ leniores v-es (benevolentia, æquitas et c.); v. solum in sapiente perfecta est; v-is laus omnis in actione consistit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om de 4 hufwuddygderna,</text:span> de Off. I. 5), C.; v-is rigidæ satelles; v. est medium vitiorum et utrinque reductum; v. repulsæ nescia sordidæ intaminatis fulget honoribus; v. recludens immeritis mori cælum negata temptat iter via, Hor.; ad v-em revocare; negavit id suæ v-i (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">character)</text:span> convenire, N.; tua me v. tamen et sperata voluptas suavis amicitiæ quemvis sufferre laborem suadet et inducit noctes vigilare serenas, Lucr.; quo fata trahunt, v. secura sequetur; expulsæ terris v-is jam sola fides (Cato), Luc.; Nero v-em ipsam exscindere concupivit interfecto Thrasea Paeto, T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos personer och saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraft; god egenskap,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (dygd), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">godhet, förtjenst:</text:span></text:span> mercis; deûm v-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tack ware gud; gud ske lof)</text:span> habemus, et qui (quo) nosmet utamur et aliis qui comi tati simus benevolentibus; v-e formæ (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det är din skönhets förtjenst)</text:span> id evenit, te ut deceat, quidquid habeas, Pt.; equi; corporis v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kroppsligt företräde),</text:span> C.; hæc est v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förtjensten hos, nyttan l. wärdet af)</text:span> memoriæ rerum gestarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(historien),</text:span> Sa.; ordinis hæc v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förtjenst)</text:span> erit aut ego fallor, ut jam nunc dicat jam nunc debentia dici; v-e carentia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det kraftlösa, matta, dåliga i en dikt),</text:span> Hor.; navis, L.; v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(krafter, egenskaper)</text:span> herbarum; manūs v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(styrka);</text:span> nec adhuc v. in frondibus ulla, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bĭvĭra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som haft twå männer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> univira): Varr. ap. Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Centumvir</text:span>, ĭri, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">-vĭri</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hundramän</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en domstol af egentl. 105 medlemmar (3 ur hwar och en af de 35 tribus), af hwilken allahanda civilmål handlades:</text:span> inter Claudios et Marcellos (de testamento) judicarunt c-i, C. (de Or. I. 176. 180); nullius magni oratoris liber apud c-os dictus legitur, T. Dial. c. 38; <text:soft-page-break/>Pn. Ep. IV. 24; Qu. IV. 2. 5.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Centumvĭrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hundramännens;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som förekommer, förhandlas af l. inför</text:span> centumviri: id in judicio c-i certatum accepimus, C.; causæ c-es nunc primum obtinent locum, olim splendore aliorum judiciorum obruebantur, T. (Dial. c. 38).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕcemvir</text:span>, ĭri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">-vĭri</text:span>, ōrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ûm, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tiomän,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Decemvirer,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett collegium af 10 män:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. decemviri legibus scribundis (bis quinque viri, Hor.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett år 450 f. Chr.</text:span> (303 a. U. C.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillsatt collegium för utarbetande af en romersk lag</text:span> (legibus de imperio consulari scribendis, L. III. 1), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de år 303, 304 af folket stadfästade</text:span> XII tabulæ: L. III. 50 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.:</text:span> d-os, qui XII tabulas perscripserunt, necesse est fuisse prudentes; d-i maxima auctoritate sine provocatione creati sunt, qui et summum imperium haberent et leges scriberent: summa legum æquitate prudentiāque conscripserunt X tabulas - duæ tabulæ iniquæ tertio anno additæ sunt (de Rep. II. §. 61 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. decemviri litibus judicandis, C. Or. §. 156; Varro l. l. IX. 85.<text:line-break/>c. decemviri sacris faciundis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett collegium, som hade sig uppdraget att förwara och förklara de sibyllinska böckerna och efter deras bud anställa fester åt Apollo m. m.:</text:span> L. VI. 37 et sæp.<text:line-break/>d. d-ri agris dividundis, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕcemvĭrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Decemvirernes:</text:span></text:span> invidia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot</text:span> d.); tertius annus d., C.: d. potestas non ultra biennium valuit, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕcemvĭrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Decemvirat,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tiomannacollegium:</text:span></text:span> C., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Duōvir</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Duumvir</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Duōvĭri</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Duumvĭri</text:span>, ōrum (ûm), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett collegium l. en commission af twå män, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Duumvirer:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">domare i brottmål, omtalade från Roms äldsta tider:</text:span> d-i perduellionem judicent; d-os facit, creat rex, L. I. 26; d-i perduellionis, C.<text:line-break/>b. duumviri sacrorum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwilka förwarade de sibyllinska böckerna (sednare</text:span> decemviri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> quindecimviri): libri per d-os sacrorum aditi, L. III. 10.<text:line-break/>c. duumviros navales classis ornandæ reficiendæque causa populus jussit, L. (A. U. 443).<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i municipierna woro</text:span> duoviri juri dicundo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de högste embetsmännen (jfr</text:span> quattuorviri): C. Leg. Agr. II. §. 93; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Marquardt,</text:span> III. 1. 351 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Duumvĭrālis</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">person, som eger duumvirs rang:</text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Duumvĭrālĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Duumvĭrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Duumvirs</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">embete:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvĭro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snöpa:</text:span></text:span> Varro, Catl. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvĭrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: pilorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(borttagande),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quattuorvĭri</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett collegium af fyra män, i municipierna af twå</text:span> duumviri (ɔ: consules, prætores) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och twå ædiler (jfr</text:span> duumvir): q-os fecerant municipes, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quattuorvĭrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Quattuorvirs</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">embete:</text:span></text:span> C. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quindĕcimvir</text:span>, ĭri, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">-vĭri</text:span>, ōrum (ûm), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medlem af ett collegium af </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">femton män</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> decemviri c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> duumviri b.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwilka </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förwarade och tolkade</text:span> (adibant) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de sibyllinska böckerna: jfr</text:span> C. de Legg. II. §. 20; quindecim Diana preces virorum audiat, Hor.; q-vir, T. VI. 12.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quindĕcimvĭrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Femtonmanna-:</text:span></text:span> q-i sacerdotio præditus, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quindĕcimvĭrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Femtonmans embete:</text:span></text:span> Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quinquĕvir</text:span>, ĭri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medlem af ett </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">femmannacollegium:</text:span></text:span> C., Hor., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quinquĕvĭrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Quinquevirs</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">embete:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Septemvir</text:span>, ĭri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medlem af ett </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sjumannacollegium:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för anställande af</text:span> epulum Jovis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> tresviri): Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för anläggande af en coloni:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Septemvĭrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Septemvirers:</text:span></text:span> auctoritas, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.:</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Septemvĭrālis</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">man af septemvirs rang l. ställning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Septemviral:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Septemvĭrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Septemvirs</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">embete:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sēvir</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sexvir</text:span>, ĭri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medlem af ett </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sexmannacollegium:</text:span></text:span> Petr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sēvĭrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sēvĭrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sevirs</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wärdighet:</text:span></text:span> Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tresvĭri</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> triumvir): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tremän,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> collegium af tre män:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en polismyndighet:</text:span> quid faciam, si nunc t. me in carcerem compegerint?, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. t. epulones <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för anställande af</text:span> epulum Jovis: C. de Or. III. §. 73.<text:line-break/>c. coloniæ deducendæ: L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Triumvir</text:span>, ĭri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">-vĭri</text:span>, ōrum (ûm), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Triumvir,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> medlem af ett collegium af tre män, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">triumvirer,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. t-i coloniæ deducendæ, Sa., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för anläggande af en coloni, fördelning af jord o. s. w.:</text:span> t-i Romani ad agrum (Placentinum) venerant assignandum; t-i agrarii, t-i agrum metantes, L.<text:line-break/>b. t-i capitales, nocturni, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">polismyndigheter:</text:span> C., L. <text:line-break/>c. t-i auro, argento, ære (æri) flando, feriundo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> t-i monetales: C., Jct.<text:line-break/>d. t-i reipublicæ (constituendæ), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för statsskickets ordnande, titel, hwilken Antonius, Octavianus och Lepidus tillade sig, då de med wapenmakt delade romerska riket sig emellan:</text:span> M. Antonius triumvir reipublicæ, N.; t. r. c., L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Triumvĭrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Triumvirs, -virers, -virernes:</text:span></text:span> Hor., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Triumvĭrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Triumvirat, triumvirs</text:span></text:span> (a. d.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wärdighet:</text:span> C., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīgintīvir</text:span>, ĭri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">-vĭri</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjuguman,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> medlem af ett collegium af tjugu män:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för åkerfördelning:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en underordnad communalbefattning:</text:span> Tiberius postulavit, ut Nero filius Germanici munere capessendi vigintiviratus solveretur et quinquennio maturius, quam per leges (liceret), quæsturam peteret, T. Ann. III. 29. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīgintīvĭrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Vigintivirs</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">befattning:</text:span></text:span> C., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnĭvĭra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som blott haft </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">en</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> man:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭrāgo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(archaistiskt och om kraftiga, karlawulna jungfrur) och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Virgo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beslägtadt med</text:span> vireo?):<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mö, ungmö, jungfru;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom apposition: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">jungfrulig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. om qwinnor och djur:</text:span> ancilla v-ago; v. grandis; venibis tu hodie, virgo; v. atque mulier nulla est, quin sit mala, quæ præter sapiet, quam placet parentibus, Pt. (Pers. 336; 365-6); vos etenim juvenes animum geritis muliebrem, illa virago viri, Enn. ap. C.; Paluda (Pallas) virago, id. ap. Varr. l. l. VII. 37; v. Vestalis; adulta; v. filia, C.; v. nubilis propter paupertatem collocari <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blifwa gift)</text:span> non poterat; nata est Attico neptis ex Agrippa, cui filiam v-em collocarat, N.; o quam te memorem, v.?; audet - viris concurrere v., Vg.; Dianam teneræ dicite v-es, intonsum pueri dicite Apollinem; montium custos nemorumque v. (Diana); v-es sanctæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om Vestalerna),</text:span> Hor.; v. dea (Diana); v-em vi superare, rapere; v. bellica (Pallas), Ov.; Veneri donatæ a v-e puppæ, Ps. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absolut om en Vestal:</text:span> iret v. et sacra capesseret, T. (XI. 34); equa, Pn.; porca, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jungfrulig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ren, skär;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> obrukad, ouppodlad:</text:span> (oratio casta, verecunda, v. incorrupta quodam modo, C.); terra, Pn.; charta, Mt.; v-es rosæ, Pervig. Ven.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ung qwinna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: om Pasiphae, Minos’ drottning,</text:span> Vg.; nuper v-es nuptæ, Hor. <text:line-break/>III. Aqua Virgo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. blott</text:span> Virgo = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wattenledning i Rom (slutpunkt: Fontana di Trevi):</text:span> V-e lotus, Mt. XIV. 163.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgĭnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jungfrurs, jungfru-:</text:span></text:span> feles v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jungfrutjuf),</text:span> Pt.; ploratus; vestitus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jungfrulig:</text:span></text:span> modestia, poēt. ap. C.; Venus alia v-i flore prædita, Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgĭnāle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: partes muliebres: Phædr. IV. 15. 12 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Muell.).</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgĭnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jungfru-:</text:span></text:span> feles (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tjuf),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgĭneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jungfru-, jungfrurs, mörs;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som är för </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">jungfrur:</text:span></text:span> comptus, Lucr.; urnæ (Danaidum); gymnasium, Ppt.; sagittæ (Dianæ), Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jungfrulig:</text:span></text:span> pudor; vultus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>irgĭnisvendōnĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: (vendo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jungfrusäljare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> föregifwet persiskt namn hos</text:span> Pt. Pers. 702.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgĭnĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jungfrudom, mödom, jungfrustånd:</text:span></text:span> v-em violare, C.; Vestales Numa v-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jungfrulöfte)</text:span> aliisque cæremoniis venerabiles ac sanctas fecit, L.; v-em rapere, Ov.; v-is honos, Vg.; præflorata; nova nupta interfectæ v-is, Ap.; illibata, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virguncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungmö; liten flicka:</text:span></text:span> Sen., Ct., Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvirgĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försätta ur jungfruståndet:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Viratus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vir.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>irbius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mythiskt personnamn:</text:span> Vg. VII. 262; Ov. F. VI. 756.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>irdŏmărus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gallisk furste:</text:span> Ppt. V. 10.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Virectum = Viretum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vireo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭreo,</text:span> ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stå grön; grönska:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> oculi, Pt.; arbores; vites, C.; viscum fronde v-et novā; nemus; <text:soft-page-break/>mons; stagna v-ent musco, Vg.; flamma Aetuæ; cultor v-entis agelli, Hor.; pectora felle v-ent, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grönska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara ung, wara frisk, wara kraftig, blomstrande:</text:span></text:span> Camillus senex v-bat integris sensibus, L.; v-ent genua; v-ens Chia (puella); v-enti canities abest, Hor.; flos virtutis v-ens, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭreo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en fågel (grönfink):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭresco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Börja blifwa grön; grönska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. och oeg. men.:</text:span> gramina, Vg.; copia rerum, Lucr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> vis).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrētum</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Vĭrectum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grönt fält, grön äng:</text:span></text:span> per amoena v-a, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrĭdis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grön, grönskande:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. till färgen:</text:span> ripa; collis; vestitus, C.; zmaragdi, Lucr.; lapillus; colubra, Hor.: pallor; gramen, Vg.; color; gemma, Pn.; v-es undæ, poēt. ap. Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frisk, rå:</text:span></text:span> lignum, C.; caseus, Col.; v-i non cocta fidelia limo, Ps.; sucus, Pall.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frisk, kry, ungdomlig:</text:span></text:span> cruda deo (Charoni) v-isque senecta; juventa, Vg.; leo, St.; et v. et postea senex, Sen.; senectus, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrĭde</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grön färg;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gröna ställen, gröna träd, ängar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.:</text:span> Pn., Sen. - viridia = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blomsterrabatter</text:span></text:span> (= xystus): Phdr. II. 5. 14.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrĭdārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trädgård, trädgårdsanläggning:</text:span></text:span> C., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grönt:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrĭdĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grönhet, grön färg:</text:span></text:span> laureæ, C.; maris, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grönska, brodd:</text:span></text:span> herbescens; pratorum, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Friskhet, ungdomlighet:</text:span></text:span> senectus quamvis non sit molesta, tamen aufert eam v-em, in qua etiamnunc erat Scipio, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrĭdo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara grön:</text:span></text:span> color, Lucr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">isynnerhet i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. præs.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭrĭdans</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grön, grönskande:</text:span></text:span> laurus; v-te toro consederat herbæ, Vg.; lux, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Färga grön:</text:span></text:span> vada v-antur ab herbis, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭror</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grön färg; grönska:</text:span></text:span> novus, Vop.; pratorum, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvĭresco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wißna, blekna:</text:span></text:span> Varr. ap. Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intervĭreo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grönska (glänsa grön) emellan:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervĭrĭdis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikt grönskande; klart grön:</text:span></text:span> campus, Mela; color, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prævĭrĭdis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Starkt grön:</text:span></text:span> Frontin. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prævĭrĭdans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungdomlig:</text:span></text:span> ap. Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvĭresco</text:span>, rui, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grönska på nytt, blifwa åter grön:</text:span></text:span> silva, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blifwa ung, ungdomlig, stark på nytt:</text:span></text:span> ad bellum; vires reip.; ille, C.; senectus non r-it, Col.; partes reip., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subvĭrĭdis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något grön:</text:span></text:span> folia, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vīresco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vis.<text:line-break/>Vĭresco, Viretum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vireo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Virga,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäl af</text:span> vireo):<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Qwist; späd gren:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> māla hærent in v-a sua, Varr.; simili frondescit v. metallo, Vg.; quatitur tepido fraxina v. noto; vinctæ cortice v-æ, Ov.; turis, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spö, ris</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till att slå l. piska ngn med, serskildt om lictorernes </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">spön</text:span></text:span> (fasces): v-is cædere alqm, C.; vigila, nisi quidem hic agitare mavis varius v-is vigilias, Pt.; v-as securesque omnibus minitari; tergum laceratum v-is, L.; metuens v-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(riset)</text:span> jam grandis Achilles cantabat patriis in montibus; frangis sociorum in sanguine v-as (lictorum), Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spö, snärt:</text:span></text:span> mihi commotā jam dudum mulio v-ā innuit. Ergo vale, Juv.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ympqwist:</text:span></text:span> fissa cortice v-am inserit, Ov.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Limspö, -stång:</text:span></text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Staf;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt om Mercurii staf, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">trollstaf:</text:span></text:span> tum v-am capit: hac animas ille evocat Orco pallentes, alias sub tristia Tartara mittit, dat somnos adimitque et lumina morte resignat, Vg.; v-am potenti somniferam sumpsisse manu, Ov.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strimma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på himmelen; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rand</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en klädning:</text:span> Sen., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spögubbe:</text:span></text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af qwistar </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flätad:</text:span></text:span> calathiscus, Catl.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Randig, strimmig:</text:span></text:span> sagulum, Vg.; tigris, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Småskog:</text:span></text:span> C. de Legg. II. §. 21.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgeus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ris-; af ris, qwistar:</text:span></text:span> scopæ, Cato; pabulum; supellex, Vg.; sæpes, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgĭdēmia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Risskörd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> comiskt bildadt ord</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett kok stryk:</text:span> ulmea v., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten qwist, litet spö:</text:span></text:span> quasi v-ā divinā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trollspö)</text:span> suppeditantur alicui omnia; v-ā circumscribere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(draga en krets omkring)</text:span> alqm, C.; Thrasybulo a populo honoris causa data est corona facta duabus v-is oleaginis, N.; v. censoria (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">critiskt streck),</text:span> Qu. I. 4. 3.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strimmig, randig:</text:span></text:span> concha, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgultus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Risbewuxen:</text:span></text:span> vallis, Sa. ap. Serv. Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Virgultum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Buskar, busksnår, ris, kratt:</text:span></text:span> frondes et v-a, C.; locis circa densa obsita v-a obscuris, L. I. 14; cornea v-a; in ignem frondem ac v-a facesque conjiciunt, Vg.; v-is abditus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>irgĭlius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ergĭlius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn, berömdt genom skalden</text:span> P. Virgilius Maro, † 18 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">f. Chr.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Virgĭliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Virgĭn . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Virago.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>irgīnius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ergīnius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Virgīnia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn</text:span> (L. III. 44).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Virgo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Virago.<text:line-break/>Virgul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Virga. <text:line-break/>Virguncula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Virago.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭriæ,</text:span> ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Armband:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭriātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prydd med armband:</text:span> Lucil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭriŏlæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ĭriāthus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lusitanisk</text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">från westre delen af spanska halfön) hjelte i 2:dra seklet f. Chr.:</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Virid . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vireo.<text:line-break/>Viril . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vir. <text:line-break/>Viriolæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Viriæ.<text:line-break/>Viripotens, Viritim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vir.<text:line-break/>Viror <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vireo.<text:line-break/>Vīrosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Virus. <text:line-break/>Vĭrosus, Virtus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vir.<text:line-break/>Virulentus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Virus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīrus</text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> viri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> viro, Lucr. II. 474. 853; VI. 805 (inc. l.)], <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slem, saft:</text:span></text:span> ciceris, Col.; cochlearum, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skarp</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skarpt smakande l. luktande </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wätska;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen abstr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skarp, frän stank</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">smak:</text:span></text:span> odores perdit olivum v-o suo; tetri primordia v-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i hafswatten),</text:span> Lucr.; ponti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sälta),</text:span> Man.; alarum; mustelæ; vini, Pn.; palus eructat v-us, Col.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gift:</text:span></text:span> serpentis, C. poēt.; mălum, Vg.; Sen. Med. 700. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gift; stank; snusk:</text:span></text:span> quærit alqm, apud quem evomat v. acerbitatis suæ, C.; Græcia - artes intulit agresti Latio: sic horridus ille defluxit numerus Saturnius et grave v. munditiæ pepulere, Hor.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">animalisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säd:</text:span></text:span> Vg.; verrinum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slemmig:</text:span></text:span> piscis, Col. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stinkande; frän:</text:span></text:span> castorea, Vg.; caro, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīrŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Giftig:</text:span></text:span> serpens, Gell.; Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīs,</text:span> vim, vi (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> vīres, vīrium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (vis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen. sing.,</text:span> Varr. VIII. 2. 7; vīs, <text:span text:style-name="T2">nom., acc. pl.,</text:span> Lucr. III. 265; II. 586): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraft, styrka; makt; wåld:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraft:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">physisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraft, styrka;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kropps-)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">krafter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hos menniskor l. djur), absolut och i förening med</text:span> corporis: vine corporis an virtute animi res militaris magis procedat, (quæsitum est), Sa.; minus habeo v-um, quam vestrum utervis; non sunt in senectute v-es, ne desiderantur quidem; linguæ solutio, vocis sonus, latera, v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ledig tunga, god organ, friska lungor, physisk styrka);</text:span> vir maximis v-bus; quidquid agas, decet agere pro v-bus, C.; urorum, Cs.; magna contorsit equum vi, ap. Qu.; eos v-bus editior cædebat, ut in grege <text:soft-page-break/>taurus; v. consili expers mole ruit sua, vim temperatam di quoque provehunt in majus: iidem odere v-es omne nefas animo moventes, Hor. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> 4); instat vi patriā Pyrrhus, Vg.; jam Tiberium corpus, jam v-es, nondum dissimulatio deserebat, T.; v. materna (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">att föda),</text:span> Luc. II. 338.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraft</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos naturliga ting i allm., i abstractare l. concret mening, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förmåga; förmögenhet:</text:span></text:span> rerum vis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">nom. pl.</text:span>) et potestates; constant quæque, donec v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(yttre kraft)</text:span> obiit, quæ res diverberet ictu, Lucr.; odora canum v.; utraque v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wärmens och köldens),</text:span> Vg.; neglecta solent incendia sumere v-es, Hor.; gemina v. (venti et æstus); v-es resumere, absumere; sine v-bus herbæ; v. fontis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(werkan);</text:span> v. nocendi; v. contraria vino; alias aliasque flumina v-es concipiunt, Ov.; fida canum v., Lucr.; canes amica v. pastoribus, Hor.; v. literæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uttal),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">andlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraft, förmåga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skicklighet o. s. w.):</text:span> summa dicendi v.; omnis v. dicendi ratioque in mentibus vel sedandis vel excitandis expromenda est; v. ingenii, eloquentiæ, C.; ergo vivida v. animi pervicit, Lucr.; tarda senectus debilitat v-es animi mutatque vigorem, Vg.; doctrina sed vim promovet insitam rectique cultus pectora roborant, Hor.; tu satis ad dandas Romana in carmina v-es, Luc.; v. inveniendi, respondendi, Qu. <text:line-break/>4.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en saks </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäsende:</text:span></text:span> omnis nostra v. in animo et corpore sita est, Sa.; eloquentiæ v. et natura; v. amicitiæ; omne, quod sumitur in oratione aut ad probandum aut ad refellendum, aut sua vi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(deß eget wäsende)</text:span> et natura sumitur aut assumitur foris, C.; non de appellatione rei, sed de vi quæritur, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett begrepps </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omfång:</text:span></text:span> in IV partes vim honesti divisimus, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett ords </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Betydelse:</text:span></text:span> v. verbi, C. Tusc. I. §. 5; v. et proprietas verborum, Qu.<text:line-break/>II.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Makt, förmåga:</text:span></text:span> deorum vi regitur mundus; v. magistratus, C.; vim præfecturæ intendit Sejanus, T.; plebis, Sa.; vim Cæsaris assumere, Qu.; vi superûm sævæ memorem Junonis ob iram, Vg.; acrior v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(makt)</text:span> rapit alqm; non hæc mihi v. aut tibi talium res est aut animus deliciarum egens, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Makt, krafter, styrka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofta till krigiska företag); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förmögenhet</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">syn.</text:span> facultates, opes, copiæ): prævalentis populi v-es se ipsæ conficiunt; nec validiores opibus ullæ inter se civitates contulerunt arma neque his ipsis tantum unquam v-um aut roboris fuit, L.; gloria quem supra v-es (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillgångar)</text:span> et vestit et ungit -, Hor.; v-es = copiæ, milites, Cs. b. C. III. 57. I. 35; amicas v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förbundna trupper)</text:span> assumere; alicujus præconsumere v-es, Ov.; ne patriæ validas in viscera vertite v-es, Vg.; certatum totis concussi v-bus orbis in commune nefas, Luc.; v-es Italæ, Hor.; ultra v-es nitor corporis, Juv.<text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mängd, myckenhet, massa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sällan</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span>): exemplorum; infinita v. innumerabilium atomorum; auri, C.; hostium v. maxima, N.; ingens v. frumenti, jumentorum, telorum, pulveris, aquæ, levis armaturæ, Cs.; utrium; serpentium, Sa.; sanguinis alti v. sibi fecit iter, Luc.; bitumineæ, aquæ, Aetnæ v-es, Ov.; hederæ, Hor. <text:line-break/>IV. <text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraft; inflytande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">betydelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">ad, in rem</text:span>): <text:soft-page-break/>maxima est v. fortunæ ad utramque partem (et ad bene res gerendas et ad male -); natura ad dicendum vim affert maximam; quum tanta v. justitiæ sit, ut ea etiam latronum opes firmet atque augeat, quantam ejus vim inter leges et judicia in constituta rep. fore putamus?, C.; vim maximam habere ad <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utöfwa på; bidraga till)</text:span> aliquid, Cs., Qu.<text:line-break/>V. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraft</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kraftansträngning, häftighet, wåldsamhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i kroppslig l. andelig mening); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">force, passion, eftertryck, eld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i framställning:</text:span> morbi, C., N., frigoris; veneni; multæ et reconditæ literæ erant in eo oratore, v. non erat, C.; v. major; v. fluminis, tempestatis, Cs.; tanta v. avaritiæ irrupit, Sa.; non ea v. animi, non tanta superbia victis, Vg.; flammæ, N.; maxima vi certare; majore vi urgere; summa vi contendere, Sa., Cs.; mali; vaporis; nimiæ v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kraftansträngningar),</text:span> Ov.; verborum acer spiritus et v.; v. insani leonis, Hor.; in eo (oratore) plus vis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span>) est, quam sanguinis, T. Dial. 26; venti; languescit v. omnis (dicendi); rebus vim addit oratio, Qu. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåld;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i krig: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anfall, storm:</text:span></text:span> vicimus vi feroces, Pt.; vi et armis oppressa res publica, C.; vim facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bruka),</text:span> suscipere, C., Cs.; vi, per vim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med wåld, på wåldsam wäg),</text:span> C., Cs., Sa., Hor.; solida v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rent wåld),</text:span> Enn., C.; v. civilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en skenbar strid wid egendomstwist),</text:span> Gell.; hoc est vim afferre; cogere alqm vi; vim afferre, inferre, offerre, adhibere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillfoga)</text:span> alicui, C., N.; vi cogere, Cs., C., L.; vi et metu virgarum adductus, C.; vi subigere; vim parare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rusta sig till att bruka wåld, storma),</text:span> Sa., Vg.; vi cepit, expugnavit urbem, L., Cs.; vim sustinere, Cs., N.; per vim temptare iter; ad vim descendere, Cs.; imperium non erat vi consecutus, sed suorum voluntate, N.; fit via vi, rumpunt aditus; auro vi potitur, Vg.; de vi et injuria queri, Qu.; me occidistis, ait, cui sic prærepta voluptas et demptus per vim mentis gratissimus error, Hor.; vim ferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillfoga)</text:span> alicui, pati <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lida);</text:span> vim minis addit; insidiæque et v. et amor sceleratus habendi, Ov.; non erat ad apertam vim par, L.; leges vi, ambitu, pecunia turbabantur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlens</text:span>, tis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(poet.) och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåldsam, wild, häftig, stormande, obändig:</text:span></text:span> homo v-ior, Ter.; homo v. et furens; vehemens et v.; v-simæ tempestates; impetus; non opes v-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wåldsmakt, tyrannisk makt)</text:span> et populo Rom. minime ferendam potentiam, sed caritatem civium et gloriam concupiscere; - ut vere dicitur, parva esse ad beate vivendum momenta corporis commodorum, sic nimis v-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wildt</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerdrifwet)</text:span> est nulla dicere (T usc. V. 24), C.; v-a ingenia Tarquinii Superbi et Tulliæ; tyrannus, L.; Notus v. me vexit aquā; v-ior Eurus, amnis; v-a pectora Turni, Vg.; v-ens Aufidus; - Lucania bellum incuteret v-a, Hor.; ferus ac v-ens, Ps.; v-a vada Phasidis, Sen.; v-ior cetero mari Oceanus et truculentiā cæli præstat Germania, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåldsamt, med wåld, med häftighet, obändigt, ostyrigt:</text:span></text:span> tolerare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(otåligt),</text:span> Ter.; fremere v-ius, Juv.; quæstio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ransakningen)</text:span> exercita v. et ex libidine plebis, Sa.; retortis litore Etrusco v. undis, Hor.: ludos dirimere, L.; gerere aliquid, Pn.; persequi, Col.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåldsamhet, wild häftighet, wåld, wildhet, raseri; hårdhet:</text:span></text:span> effrenata; inimicorum, C.; leonum, Lucr.; feneratorum; fortunæ, Sa.; accenso gliscit v. Turno; non flectitur v.; exarsit v. Turni, Vg.; v. vultus, Ov.; clades omnibus, quæ urbi per v-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(raseri)</text:span> ignium acciderunt, gravior atque atrocior; prorupta per immensum ædificia, ut continuæ v-æ (ignis) campus et velut vacuum cælum occurreret, T.; v. et convicia Virginii, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwa wåld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">orätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förnärmelse:</text:span></text:span> quod v-tum est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den orätt, som begåtts),</text:span> magnis beneficiis compensandum est, C.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med concreta object:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåldsamt behandla, mißhandla, såra, skada; förolämpa, förnärma:</text:span></text:span> voce alqm, C.; fines <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(härja, ofreda),</text:span> Cs.; cedentes v-ri vetuit; Plato a tyranno crudeliter v-tus est; Atticus nihil indulsit amicis ad Antonium v-dum, N.; corpus vulnere; agros ferro, Vg.; misso thyrso; ictu baculi; nemus securi, Ov.; ferro alqm, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära hand, lägga hand på, förgripa sig på, wåldföra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en person l. sak, som borde wara skyddad l. helig; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kränka, skända, oskära, wanhelga:</text:span></text:span> parentem; sacra stupro; corpus sanctum manu, C.; hospitem, Cs.; legatum; sacra; fanum, N.; deum; vivos et exstinctos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ohelga</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bringa förbannelse öfwer),</text:span> Ov. Met. X. 485.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bloda, rödfärga:</text:span></text:span> ebur ostro, Vg. Aen. XII. 67.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med abstracta object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förgripa sig på, skända, kränka; bryta, bryta emot:</text:span></text:span> virginitatem; existimationem; famam probris; jura; amicitiam, C.; hospitium; foedus, L.; inducias, Cs.; clementiam (supplici debitam), N.; tellus prius ima dehiscat ante, pudor, quam te violo, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sårbar:</text:span></text:span> telis, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som får kränkas, kränkbar:</text:span></text:span> haud v-e numen, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kränkning, wanhelgande:</text:span></text:span> templi, L.; fidei, Vell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viŏlātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som förgriper sig på, kränkare, wanhelgare:</text:span></text:span> juris gentium, L.; foederis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēviŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tilltwinga sig:</text:span></text:span> Ppt. I. 7. 16.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inviŏlābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Okränkbar, fridlyst, helig:</text:span></text:span> Lucr., Sil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inviŏlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Okränkt, oskadd, oförkränkt:</text:span></text:span> corpus; aliquid integrum et i-um, C.; fides, Sa.; ut i-us in navem escenderet (legatus), effecit, N.; corpora vestra, conjugum ac liberorum vestrorum servat i-a Hannibal, si inermes - a Sagunto velitis exire, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Okränkbar, fridlyst, helig:</text:span></text:span> tribunus; templum, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inviŏlāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oförkränkt, heligt:</text:span></text:span> vos deos verentes memoriam nostri pie i-teque servabitis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīresco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stärkas:</text:span></text:span> increscunt animi, vīrescit volnere virtus, poēt. ap. Gell. XVIII. 11. 4.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Viscatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Viscum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>iscellīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen i</text:span> gens Cassia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Viscer . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Viscus.<text:line-break/>Viscidus, Viscor, Viscosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Viscum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Viscum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viscus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> (Pt.): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Viscum,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mistel, mistelten</text:span></text:span> (V. album, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Linn.), en parasitwäxt, som lefwer på större träd:</text:span> v. suam sedem non habet, in aliena vivit, in quercu, robore; altitudo non excedit cubitalem: mas fertilis, femina sterilis; Druides nil habent v-o sacratius, Pn. (XVI. 92 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.);</text:span> quale solet brumali frigore v-um fronde virere nova, quod non sua seminat arbor, et croceo fetu teretes circumdare truncos: talis erat species auri frondentis opaca ilice, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lim, fågellim</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af wäxten</text:span> viscum: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> v. pennis avium tactu ligandis, oleo subactum, confit ex acinis et cet., Pn. (XVI. 94; XXIV. 6); bestiolæ in sordibus avium tanquam in v-o inhærescunt, C.; captare feras et fallere v-o, Vg. (G. I. 139; IV. 41). <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> viscus merus est meretricum benevolentia, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viscor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blifwa klibbig:</text:span></text:span> Juv. VI. 463.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viscātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Limbestruken, lim-:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> virga; alæ, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> beneficia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwarmed man lockar l. fångar);</text:span> munera, Sen., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viscĭdus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viscōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klibbig:</text:span></text:span> Pall.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Viscus,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viscĕra</text:span>, ĕrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. de mjuke delarne af djurkroppen</text:span> (quidquid sub corio est, Serv.); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så wäl </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kött,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">inelfwor:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> <text:line-break/>1 eg.:</text:span> ex v-bus v-us; cadavera jam rancenti viscere, Lucr.; tunica inhærescit v-bus, poēt. C.; boum v-bus vesci; omne bonum in v-bus medullisque (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">köttet, sinligheten)</text:span> condere, C.; tergora diripiunt costis et v-a nudant; raptabat - viri mendacis v-a Tullus per silvam, Vg.; culter aperit percussi v-a tauri; de putri v-e nasci, Ov.; telum penetrat in v-a, Ct.; te v-bus meis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mitt lif)</text:span> plus amo; v. et farra, Su.; Tityus v-e pascit aves, Tib.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någons eget </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kött</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">barn, slägt</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blod), folk:</text:span></text:span> dolor armavit contra sua v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(barn)</text:span> matrem, Ov.; ne patriæ validas in v-a vertite vires, Vg.; Sen. Agam. 27; - populumque potentem in sua victrici conversum v-a dextrā, Luc. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Det inre, innersta,</text:span></text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hjertat, kärnan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en sak:</text:span> montis, Vg.; non tantum segetes alimentaque debita dives poscebatur humus, sed itum est in v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inre, inelfwor)</text:span> terræ, effodiuntur opes -, Ov. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> in parentis v-a intravit suæ deterior ætas, Sen. Oct. 418); - venæ et v-a reip.; id malum inhæret in v-bus reip.; principia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inledningarne)</text:span> non extrinsecus, sed ex ipsis v-bus causarum sumenda sunt, C.; imis hæret imago (defuncti mariti) v-bus, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viscĕrātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bitwis:</text:span></text:span> Enn. ap. Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Viscĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Köttutdelning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt folket (af sökande till embeten o. d.):</text:span> epulis et v-bus et gladiatorum muneribus, ludorum venationumque apparatu pecunias profundere, C.; populo v. data a M. Flavio in funere matris - honoris etiam causa ei fuit, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēviscĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blotta köttet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">inelfworna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sarga, sönderslita, flå:</text:span></text:span> e-tus saxa spargens tabo, sanie et sanguine atro; testudo e-ta, ap. C. (Tusc. I. 107; de Div. II. 133); Enn.; Pac.; accipiter columbam pedibus e-at uncis, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förslösa:</text:span></text:span> opes, Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Visibilis, Visio (onis) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Video.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīsio,</text:span> 4. = pēdo: Lucil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Visito, Viso <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Video.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>istŭla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">floden Weichsel.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Visum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Video.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ĭsurgis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">floden Weser i nordwestra Tyskland.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Visus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Video.<text:line-break/>Vita <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vivo. <text:line-break/>Vitabilis, -tabundus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vito.<text:line-break/>Vital . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vita, Vivo.<text:line-break/>Vitatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vito.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ĭtellia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Italien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Vĭtellensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ĭtellius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Vĭtelliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vitellus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vitulus.<text:line-break/>Viteus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vitis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vītex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en buskwäxt</text:span> (v. agnus castus): Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vitiarium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vitis.<text:line-break/>Vitiat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vitio, Vitium.<text:line-break/>Vitic . . ., Vitifer, Vitigenus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vitis.<text:line-break/>Vitilena <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vitium.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vitilīgo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fläck på kroppen; utslag:</text:span></text:span> tollere albas, Pn.; foeda, Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vitilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vieo.<text:line-break/>Vitilitigator, -litigo, Vitio, Vitios . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vitium.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vītis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winträd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. del deraf, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">winstock, winranka, winlöf:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> v-is sacræ inventor, Enn.; v-es lætificæ, poēt. ap. C.; v-ium satus, ortus, incrementa, religatio, propagatio, C.; v-es autumno fundi videmus, Lucr.; lenta; lætis v-bus intexere ulmum; almæ v-es; prævalidæ multoque Baccho (vino) fluentes v-es, Vg.; sub arta v-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(löfwerk, lusthus af winträd)</text:span> bibere, Hor.; rode, caper, v-em!; v-e <text:soft-page-break/>caput tegere, Ov.; ut vidua in nudo v. quæ nascitur arvo nunquam se extollit, nunquam mitem educat uvam, at si forte eadem est ulmo conjuncta marito, multi illam agricolæ, multi accoluere juvenci, sic virgo, dum intacta manet, dum inculta senescit et cet., Catl. (LXII. 50 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.).</text:span> —— <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winstock</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom attribut för centurionen, som med sådant werktyg afstraffade soldater:</text:span> v-e regere centum, Ov.; centurio, fractā v-e in tergo militis, alteram clara voce et rursus aliam poscebat, T.; dare v-em (i. e. centurionatum, ordinem) alicui, Sp.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ranka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> eller namn på wäxter, som likna winträdet, såsom</text:span> vites albæ, Ov. Met. XIII. 800.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīteus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Win-,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som är af winträd:</text:span> coliculus, Varr.; pocula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med win uti),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītiārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Plantskola</text:span></text:span> (seminarium) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">för winträd:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītĭcŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wingårdsman:</text:span></text:span> Sil. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītĭcŏmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med winlöf i håret:</text:span></text:span> Lyæus, Avien.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītĭcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten winstock</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">winranka:</text:span></text:span> C., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winbärande:</text:span></text:span> regio; collis, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītĭgĕnus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītĭgĕneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af winträd, win-:</text:span></text:span> liquor; latices, Lucr.; surculus, Cato; lignum, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītĭsător</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: (sero, sēvi): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winplanterare, wingårdsman:</text:span></text:span> o Dionyse pater, optume v., Semela genite, Acc. fr. 241 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ribb.;</text:span> Sabinus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭtium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fel; lyte; last:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">objectivt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fel, lyte, skada, brist, swaghet, dålig egenskap, olägenhet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (beskaffenhet hos en sak, hwarigenom den förlorar sitt wärde l. ej kan uppfylla sitt ändamål):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> corporis v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lyte);</text:span> mercis, Pt.; in amore hæc insunt v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(olägenheter),</text:span> Ter.; v. est, quum partes corporis inter se dissident; ædes fecerunt v.; venditorem ejus rei, quam vendat, v-a dicere oportet; nihil est in tecto aut in parietibus v-i; v. peregrinitatis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">att wara främling),</text:span> C.; aquæ capiunt v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skämmas);</text:span> mentis, Ov.; naturæ; res v. facit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tager skada),</text:span> Cs.; turpe (corporis); v-o mutatur uva, Hor.; āeris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(osundhet),</text:span> Vg.; sonat v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(klingar sprucket)</text:span> fidelia, Ps. III. 21; oris et linguæ, Qu.; pusillum, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om qwinnor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skam</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förlust af ära; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kränkning:</text:span></text:span> v. afferre, addere, offerre alicui = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skända:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ter.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fel, skuld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = en saks skadliga inflytande, inwerkan:</text:span> tempestatis v-o factum est, Cs.; fortunæ v-o decoxit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spelade bankrutt),</text:span> non suo; valetudinis v-o furere, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i subjectiv mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fel, felsteg, brist, swaghet, skuld; last</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i uttrycken: räkna l. lägga ngn ngt till last:</text:span> v. dicere alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(säga ngt på ngn, tala illa om ngn),</text:span> Pt.; detractis omnibus v-is orator et omni laude cumulatus; adest fere nemo, quin acrius et acutius v-a in dicente, quam recta videat; nosce v-a tua; v-o dare, vertere alicui aliquid, C.; v-a ducum; quod v-o adversariorum multi victi concidissent, commiseratus est fortunam Græciæ Agesilaus, N.; imperatorum, Sa.; omnibus hoc v. cantoribus atque poētis, ut -; v-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skuld)</text:span> parentum rara juventus; tuo <text:soft-page-break/>v-o rerumne labores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lider),</text:span> nil referre putas?; in v-um ducit culpæ fuga, si caret arte; decipit exemplar v-is imitabile; v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(felsteg)</text:span> belli, Hor.; animi v. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">brist på mod),</text:span> Ov.; dulcibus abundat v-is, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fel,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> begånget mot lagliga former, serskildt med afseende på auspicier, som blifwit orätt tydda l. lemnade utan afseende:</text:span> v-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot laga l. häfdwunnen form)</text:span> creati consules; v-o captum tabernaculum; comitiorum solum v. est fulmen, C., L.; v-o navigare, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mißbruk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i offentliga förhållanden:</text:span> v-a corrigere, Sa. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i moralisk, personlig mening (såsom egenskap l. enskild yttring): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fel, last, synd, odygd;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (olater); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">dålig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">klanderwärd egenskap; dålig sida; utswäfning;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sedligt förderf, sedeförderf, osedlighet:</text:span></text:span> omni virtuti v. contrarium est; animi elatio, si vacat justitiā, in v-o est; confidentia in v-o ponitur; qui non defendit injuriam, tam in v-o est, quam si parentes aut patriam deserat; domesticis v-is se inquinare; pudet me istorum philosophorum, qui ullum judicium vitari, nisi v-o ipso vitato, putant; eos, qui singulis v-is excellunt, - propter cruciatus aliquos dicimus miseros esse, an propter vim turpitudinemque v-orum?, C.; inter tanta v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sedeförderf)</text:span> imbecilla ætas corrupta tenebatur; ambitionis v. propius virtutem est; v-a sua callide occultare, Sa.; Pausanias ut virtutibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(talanger)</text:span> eluxit, sic v-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(laster)</text:span> obrutus est; v-a juventutis; nihil fuit Alcibiade excellentius vel in v-is vel in virtutibus, N.; nec v-a nostra nec remedia pati possumus, L.; virtus est v. fugere et sapientia primă stultitiā caruisse; pinguis v-is; hesterna v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utswäfningar);</text:span> labi in v-um; amicorum v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swagheter); -</text:span> neve te nostris v-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förderf)</text:span> iniquum ocior aura tollat; vigilansne ploro turpe commissum an v-is carentem ludit imago?, Hor.; flagrat v-o; alimenta v-orum, Ov.; insectari v-a, Qu.; Tiberius virtutes non sectabatur, v-a (ministrorum) oderat; Galba magis extra v-a, quam cum virtutibus; apud Germanos nemo v-a ridet neque corrumpere et corrumpi seculum vocatur; Germani haud minus facile v-is, quam armis vincentur, T.; omne animi v. tanto conspectius in se crimen habet, quanto major, qui peccat, habetur, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtĭlēna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (lena): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skändlig kopplerska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (comiskt ord):</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtĭlītĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skamligt lasta, förtala:</text:span></text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtĭlītĭgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lastare:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtio</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i physisk mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämma, förderfwa, förpesta:</text:span></text:span> aper v-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skämdt wildswinskött);</text:span> mel v-tum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förgiftad);</text:span> vinum lino v-tum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som fått en bismak af -),</text:span> Hor.; res dentibus ævi v-ta; ignis polum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förbränner);</text:span> Hypanis salibus v-atur amaris; plumbum, semina v-re; aura odoribus v-ta; corpus curis v-tum, Ov.; oleum v-atur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skämmes),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skända, kränka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mö):</text:span> virginem, Ter., Ov., T., Qu.; venter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(moderlif)</text:span> v-tus, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om andra object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förderfwa, förfalska:</text:span></text:span> diem tribuni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(göra felaktig, tillägga den fel = göra den omöjlig för offentliga förhandlingar genom anmälande af olyckliga auspicier eller blott af afsigten att</text:span> servare de cælo), C. Att. IV. 9; v-ta significatio verbi, C.; senatus consulta; memoria rerum v-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förfalskad),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtiātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skändande:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtiātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skändare:</text:span></text:span> feminæ, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prævĭtio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I förwäg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skämma) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förgifta:</text:span></text:span> fontes, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämd, förderfwad, skadad, med lyte behäftad; sjuk:</text:span></text:span> non ego vitam tuam empsim v-a nuce, Pt.; ilex, Vg.; ovis, Col.; puer; corpus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sjuk),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i subj. mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Felaktig, bristfällig, oriktig, orätt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> opus; ipsa ad ornandum præcepta quæ dantur, ejusmodi sunt, ut ea quamvis v-simus orator explicare possit; v-um est rhetoricam vituperare propter rhetorum vituperandam vitam; tabella (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den slutna omröstningen)</text:span> v-um occultat suffragium, C.; fuit hoc v. Lucilius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(häri bestod hans fel),</text:span> Hor.; (Augustus) cacozelos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(purister)</text:span> et antiquarios ut diverso genere v-os sprevit, Sa.; v-um et corruptum dicendi genus; v. ordo, oratio, verbum, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oriktig, formwidrig, mot auspicier stridande:</text:span></text:span> quæ augur injusta, nefasta, v-a, dira defixerit, infesta irritaque sunto, C. de Legg. II. 21; consul, collega <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot auspicier wald),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lastbar, syndig, osedlig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> moraliskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">dålig, usel:</text:span></text:span> vel v. vel sine vitio vel probus vel improbus, Pt.; tenenda sunt sua cuique, non v-a, sed tamen sua; vita, C.; ætas parentum pejor avis tulit nos nequiores mox daturos progeniem v-orem; scandit æratas v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sjukliga, usla)</text:span> naves cura; libido, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtiōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illa, sjukligt:</text:span></text:span> habet se membrum, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Felaktigt, orätt, falskt:</text:span></text:span> concludere; legem ferre, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtiōsĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Felaktighet, bristfullhet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> moralisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bristfällighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uselhet:</text:span></text:span> malitia certi cujusdam vitii nomen est, v-tas omnium, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtŭpĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Finna fel hos, klandra, tadla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl i allm. som i förhatlig men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lasta, nedsätta:</text:span></text:span> an mavis v-rier falso, quam vero extolli?, Pt.; consilium alicujus; improbus notari ac v-ri sine vitiorum cognitione satis insignite et aspere non potest; omnia, quæ cum vitiis conjuncta sunt, v-da; vitiosum est v-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nedsätta)</text:span> rhetoricam propter rhetorum v-dam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(klander wärda)</text:span> vitam; graviter aliquid, C.; cælum v-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ordspråk</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se fläckar i solen),</text:span> Phdr.; turpia, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtŭpĕrābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klanderwärd, tadelwärd:</text:span></text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtŭpĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klander, tadel; lastande, nedsättande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> vitupero): v-em subire, suscipere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ådraga sig);</text:span> cadere, venire, adduci in v-em (id.); res est alicui v-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ådrager honom klander);</text:span> v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(anledningar till klander)</text:span> vitare, effugere, C.; v-e carere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gå fri från),</text:span> Su.; severa; ridicula; liber continet v-em; v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(critiker)</text:span> scribere, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtŭpĕrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klandrare, tadlare, lastare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som nedsätter ngt:</text:span> philosophiæ v-bus responsum est in Hortensio; invidi v-es, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtŭpĕro</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lastare:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīto,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undwika, sky, fly, akta sig för, söka undgå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">undkomma,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl i rummet, som i allmännare mening: constr. med</text:span> <text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> Pt. (Petr.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>: domi se contineant, v-ent infortunio; huic verbo, Pt.; aspectum, oculos alicujus; frigus; duo vitia v-da sunt; suspiciones; adversarium; v., ne-, C.; tela <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(undwika);</text:span> proditionem, Sa.; suspiciones quoque v-bat criminum, N.; tela; locum; proelium; fugā mortem; periculum, Cs.; quid quisque v-et, nunquam homini satis cautum est; balnea v-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skyr);</text:span> v-vi culpam, non laudem merui; v-da est improba Siren desidia; hastam; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.</text:span>: privatas is quærat opes et tangere v-et, scripta Palatinus quæcunque recepit Apollo, Hor.; insidias, Ct.; ursum; jaculum; poculum; imbrem, Ov.; comitantes; v., ne irritentur animi; civitas (Romana sub Tiberio) se tegens adversum proximos: congressus, colloquia, notæ ignotæque aures v-ri: etiam muta atque inanima, tectum et parietes circumspectabantur (Ann. IV. 69), T.; v-dum est, ne maligni videamur, Qu.; hunc coccina læna v-ri jubet et comitum longissimus ordo, Juv. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Möjlig att undwika:</text:span></text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undwikande, angelägen att undwika,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> construeradt såsom particip. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.:</text:span> classem, castra hostium, Sa., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undwikande, skyende:</text:span></text:span> doloris; fori, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvīto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undwika, fly, sky:</text:span></text:span> fluctus, Pt.; letum, Lucr.; procellam; dolorem, C.; aliquid magno d-as animi capitisque dolore, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvītātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undwikande:</text:span></text:span> legionum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indēvītātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oundwiklig:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvīto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undfly, söka undwika, undgå:</text:span></text:span> dolorem; causas offensionum, C.; casum; mălum; imperium, Cs. (Ht.); tempestatem e-re imperatores utile arbitrati sunt; utilissimum ratus Alcibiades impendentem e-re tempestatem, N.; fraxinum (ɔ: hastam), Ov.; meta fervidis e-ata rotis, Hor.; asperitatem orationis; vitia; verba liberiora, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvītābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undwiklig, möjlig att undgå:</text:span></text:span> telum, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvītātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undwikande:</text:span></text:span> malorum, C. (Her.), Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnēvītābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oundwiklig:</text:span></text:span> fatum, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vitor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vietor, Vieo.<text:line-break/>Vitrarius, Vitreus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vitrum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭtrĭcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Styffader:</text:span></text:span> C., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭtrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glas:</text:span></text:span> C.; o fons Bandusiæ splendidior v-o; perlucidior v-o, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt, hwarmed färgades blått: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wejde</text:span></text:span> (Isătis tinctoria): Britanni se v-o inficiunt, quod cæruleum efficit colorem, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtrārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glasblåsare, glasfabrikant:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtreus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glas-;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som är </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">af glas:</text:span></text:span> vasa, Col.; hostis, latro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(piece i</text:span> ludus latrunculorum), Ov., Mt.; v-o bibit Priapo, Juv. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtrea</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glassaker, konstwerk af glas, glaskärl:</text:span></text:span> St., Mt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Marquardt,</text:span> V. 2. 337).<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glaslik, glasblå, skimrande:</text:span></text:span> ceratis ope Dædalea nititur pennis v-o daturus nomina ponto, Hor.; v-æ undæ, Ov., Vg.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skimrande, förledande, tjusande:</text:span></text:span> fama (Sat. II. 3. 222); Circe <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tjusande, med bitanke på hennes egenskap af hafsgudinna och solens dotter),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ĭtrūvius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn:</text:span> M. Vitruvius Polio, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">författare till ett arbete i architectur från den äldre kejsaretiden.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vitta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beslägtadt med</text:span> vieo? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om utseendet se Rich):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hufwudbindel, band,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som bars</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. af friborna qwinnor i allm., i motsats till</text:span> libertinæ (meretrices): matronarum modo v-as habeat assimuletque se tuam esse uxorem, Pt. (Mil. 719 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ritschl. jfr Lorenz</text:span> Mil. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Einl. 27, Excurs. zur</text:span> Mostell. 215-17); ubi jam facibus cessit prætexta maritis vinxit et acceptas altera v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dubbla enl. Marq.</text:span> V. 2. 44 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Anm.)</text:span> comas, jungor, Paule, tuo sic discessura cubili, Ppt.; crinales; non v. ligatos impedit - crines nec stola longa pedes, Tib., Ov.; supplice <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> b) v-ā decoræ matres, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af prester, vestaler och andra prestinnor, af skyddsökande m. m.; äfwen af jungfruliga gudinnor:</text:span> v-as temeravit sacerdos, Ov.; virgineas ausi divæ (Palladis) contingere v-as; sacerdos v-is redimitus, Vg.; albenti velatus tempora v-ā, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Band</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> omkring de</text:span> infulæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af ull), hwilka offerdjur l. menniskor, som skulle offras, buro l. som lindades kring altaren o. s. w.:</text:span> mihi sacra parari et salsæ fruges et circum tempora v-æ; cinge hæc altaria v-ā, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vittātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bindelprydd; omlindad med band</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bindlar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> vitta): capilli (matronæ), Ov.; sacerdos, Luc., Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ĭtŭla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">triumphens gudinna:</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭtŭlor,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> vitulus?): 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jubla, triumphera; bringa tackoffer:</text:span></text:span> v. victoriā, Enn. ap. Fest.; in sacris, Varr. ap. Mcb.; Jovi - bonas copias commodanti lubens v-or atque dis cunctis merito, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vĭtŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kalf, ungstut; qwiga, ung ko:</text:span></text:span> Varr., C.; tener, Hor.; v-os tueri; facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(offra)</text:span> v-ā pro frugibus; hæc v. bis venit ad mulctram, binos alit ubere fetus, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Unge</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af andra djur:</text:span> equi, Vg.; balænæ; elephanti, Pn. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjökalf:</text:span></text:span> (strepitus) eripiet somnum Druso v-isque marinis, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtellus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten kalf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (såsom smekord):</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gula, ägg-gula:</text:span></text:span> v-o ovi aurum significabatur, C. de Div. II. §. 134; Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtŭlīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kalf-, af kalf:</text:span></text:span> caruncula; assum, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vĭtŭlīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> (caro): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kalfkött:</text:span></text:span> Pt., N. Ages. VIII. 4.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vituper . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vitium.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīverra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett rofdjur, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skunk:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Viv . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Vivo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vīvo,</text:span> vixi, victum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara wid lif, uppehålla lifwet, lefwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så l. så länge:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. i eg. men.:</text:span> mei memineris, dum vitam v-es; quot hic ipse annos v-et, quojus filii tam diu vivont?; erit, ubi te ulciscar, si v-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så sannt jag lefwer);</text:span> bene hercle est uxorem tibi valere et v-re; - v-it victuraque est, immortalis est, Pt.; nemo tam senex est, quin se annum putet v-re; res ad v-dum necessariæ; Panætius vixit XXX annos, postquam illa scripserat; v. et spirare; satis diu vel naturæ vixisti vel gloriæ, patriæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för ditt land)</text:span> certe parum, Cæsar; vitis, C.; vixit ad extremam ætatem, N.; v-it adhuc; in breve tempus; nunc tertia v-itur ætas, Ov.; v-re regem (vulneratum), nuntiatum est, L.; plurimas v-di causas habebat, Pn.; invidia erga v-entem, T.; victura (= vivacia) rosaria Pæsti, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i önskningar:</text:span> ita v-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så sannt jag will lefwa l. må jag så wißt få lefwa),</text:span> C.: male v-e ac vale, Pt. (Trin. 997); v-e valeque <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lef och må wäl),</text:span> Hor.; v-ite <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lefwen, faren wäl)</text:span> silvæ, Vg.; ne v-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(må jag ej lefwa, jag will dö, om -),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i prægnant mening; lefwa i sann, rätt mening:</text:span> eo (in cælum) quum venerimus, tum denique v-emus, C.; is mihi demum v-re et frui animā videtur, qui honesto aliquo negotio intentus est, Sa.; v-amus, mea Lesbia, atque amemus, Catl.; hic v-o et regno, Hor.; propter vitam v-di perdere causas, Juv. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa i minnet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om döda ting: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara, bestå:</text:span></text:span> ignis, Pt.; mea semper v-et gloria, C. ap. Gell.; v-re si non spiritu, at virtutis laude; ejus mihi v-it auctoritas, C.; v-it sub pectore volnus, Vg.; v-et extento Proculejus ævo notus in fratres animi paterni; nulla valere diu nec v-ere carmina possunt, quæ scribentur aquæ potoribus, Hor.; v-et Mæonides, Tenedos dum stabit et Ide; gloria, Ov.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> uppehålla sig l. uppehållas, nära sig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">af, på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> suco suo; de suo; qui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwaraf)</text:span> v-amus, nihil est, Pt.; alienā misericordiā, C.; lacte et carne v-unt pellibusque sunt vestiti, Cs.; suco; v-itur ex rapto, non hospes ab hospite tutus, non socer a genero, Ov.; alienā v-re quadrā, Juv.; v-it siliquis et pane secundo, herbis et urtica, Hor.; sanguine v-imus vigemusque, L.; gramine, Ter.<text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en tid (oftare</text:span> esse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">än</text:span> vivere); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wistas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stadigt) på ett ställe:</text:span> dictus popularibus olim, qui tum v-bant homines ævumque agitabant, flos delibatus populi Suadæque medulla, Enn.; v-runt in agris contenti re sua familiari, C.; solos felices v-entes clamat in urbe; jam Athenis, jam Romæ v-re vellet, Hor.; in antris, in stagno, Ov.<text:line-break/>IV. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om konstwerk: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa; hafwa lif:</text:span></text:span> Phidiacum v-bat ebur, Juv. VIII. 103. <text:line-break/>V. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillsammans </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sammanlefwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om man och qwinna):</text:span> v-es mecum, basilico accipiere victu, Pt.; emeritis stipendiis - cupiditatum secum esse et secum, ut dicitur, v-re; beate videor vixisse, quod cum Scipione vixerim; Panætius vixit cum Scipione, C.; mulier, quæ cum eo v-re consueverat; cum eo a condiscipulatu v-rat conjunctissime, N.; cum aliquo, Hor., Ov.; cum improbis, Pt.; vixit cum conjuge novem annis sine jurgio, sine offensa, Pn. ep. <text:line-break/>VI. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> föra sitt lif så l. så, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">föra ett - lefnadssätt:</text:span></text:span> edepol proinde ut bene v-itur, diu v-itur; lepidus v-is (ɔ: es); moribus antiquis, Pt.; <text:soft-page-break/>vitam honeste v.; ex more alicujus, Ter.; in luxuria; in pecunia tenui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i små wilkor);</text:span> in diem, in horam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för dagen, för timman),</text:span> C.; sibi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för sig),</text:span> C., Sen.; bene <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dygdigt)</text:span> et beate; quiete et libere; instituto alicujus; ex natura; naturæ convenienter; parce; sobrie; magnifice; animose; hominum vitæ amice; in laude, cum gloria <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med ära, med utmärkelse);</text:span> in literis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i wittra sysselsättningar);</text:span> fortunate beateque; capessentibus remp. adhibenda est tranquillitas animi, si sunt cum gravitate constantiaque victuri, C.; si non mecum ætatem egisset, stulta v-ret <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sakna lefnadswett),</text:span> Pt.; molliter; eo more; bonis moribus, Sa.; non vixit male, qui moriens natusque fefellit; non illuc v-itur isto, quo tu rere, modo; v-itur parvo bene; quocirca v-ite fortes fortiaque adversis opponite pectora rebus; v-e memor, quam sis ævi brevis; rectius v-es, Licini, neque altum semper urgendo -; recte v-is, si curas esse, quod audis; recte, sapienter, intra naturæ fines, Hor.; innocue v-ite: numen adest; v-e pius; cælebs; sine conjuge, innuba per silvas v-bat, Ov.; non mea mutata est ætas, sine crimine tota est: viximus insignes inter utramque facem, Ppt.; liberius; laute; pro dignitate; privatum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom enskild person),</text:span> N.; negligentius, Pn.; Curios simulant et Bacchanalia v-unt; v-e bidentis amans et culti villicus horti, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> v-bat volup; suco suo cochleæ; mirumst te lolio v-re, tam vili tritico; ficis v-amus aridis, Pt.; bene, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victus</text:span>, us (victi, Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefnadssätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i hwad till föda, kläder, boning hörer), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lefnadswanor:</text:span></text:span> persecutus est Aristoteles animantium omnium ortus, v-us, figuras, C. (de Fin. V. §. 10); una domus erat, idem v-us (Scipionis et Lælii) isque communis; in omni vita v-uque excultus, C.; filium (vitiis corruptum) a pristino v-u deducere; parsimonia v-us; liberalis, splendidus non minus in vita <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(offentligt uppträdande),</text:span> quam in v-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lefnadswanor),</text:span> N.; non conferendum esse Gallicum cum Germanorum agro neque hanc consuetudinem v-us cum illa comparandam, Cs.; rēgio v-u ætatem agere, Sa.; asper v-u venatus; facilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beqwäm)</text:span> v-u gens, Vg.; quali v-u sapiens utetur?, Hor.; parcus in v-u, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifwets uppehälle</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och hwad dertill hörer; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kost, föda, näring, spis; mat och dryck;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">födoämnen, rätter, mat:</text:span></text:span> domi lepide lepidis v-bus accipere alqm; asper est v. meus, Pt.; parare ea, quæ suppeditent et ad cultum et ad v-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lifwets wård och uppehälle, jfr</text:span> cultus); non sibi soli, sed conjugi, liberis ceterisque; qui esset cultus aut v., nisi tam multæ nobis artes ministrarent?; multi divitias despiciunt, quos parvo contentos tenuis v. cultusque delectat, C.; quotidianum v-um (captivi Eumenis) amoveri jussit; nihil attigit nisi arma et ea, quæ ad v-um pertinebant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(födoämnen),</text:span> N.; tum v-u revocant vires; infelix, Vg.; tenuis; mundus; foedus; penuria v-us, Hor.; inops; v-bus invidere alicujus, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Umgänge, samlif:</text:span></text:span> v. inter hospites comis, T. (Germ. 21 d. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Victuālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till lifwets nödtorft, till födan hörande:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīta</text:span>, ae (vitāī, Lucr.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lif:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (= tillwaro i lefwande tillstånd):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> deos oro, ut uxor v-æ tuæ superstes suppetat; æquum fuit deos <text:soft-page-break/>paravisse, uno exemplo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wilkor)</text:span> ne omnes v-am viverent; hæc (= hæ) res me v-æ, soror, saturant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(göra mig mätt på -),</text:span> Pt.; v-am tueri; me fuerat æquius, ut prius introieram, sic prius exire de v-a; v-am sustentare, amittere; v-am eripere, adimere, auferre alicui: v-ā privari; v-am ponere, finire; v-ā frui; pro patria dare, profundere v-am; v-ā, e v-ā cedere, excedere, decedere, abire; esse in v-a, C.; v. mancipio nulli datur, omnibus usui, Lucr.; vergobretus v-æ necisque potestatem in suos habet, Cs.; ante judicii diem finem sibi v-æ fecit, L.; v-æ finis, exitus; v-am petere, Sa.; hic unde v-am sumeret (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rädda)</text:span> anxius, pacem duello miscuit, Hor.; his lacrimis v-am damus et miserescimus ultro, Vg.; tædia v-æ; v-ā frui; v-am odisse; v-am relinquere; v. relinquit alqm, Ov.; v-am alicujus poscere, T.; redituræ (non) parcere v-æ, Luc.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tilltal:</text:span> mea v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. blott</text:span> vita (ζωὴ καὶ ψυχή, Juv.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till l. om en älskad person:</text:span> mea v., Pt., C.; vidi te in somnis fracta, mea v., carina; quid juvat ornato procedere, v-a, capillo?, Ppt.<text:line-break/>3. = victus: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifsuppehälle:</text:span></text:span> v-am sibi repperit, Pt. St. 462.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lif</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lifstid, lefnad, lefnadstid</text:span></text:span> (ætas): v. longinqua, Pt.; di boni, quid est in hominis v-a diu?; v. longa, brevis; v-am producere longius; v-am degere; homo quod rationis est particeps, totius v-æ cursum videt; artes in omni v-a cultæ mirificos efferunt fructus; si v. suppetit, -, C.; Cato perpetuā v-ā a Scipione dissensit, N.; v-am silentio transire; agitare; transigere; exigere; in obscuro agere, Sa.; v-æ summa brevis spem nos vetat inchoare longam, Hor.; v-am in tenebris luctuque trahebam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framsläpade);</text:span> ducere (id.), Vg.; v. longa; brevis v-æ spatium, Ov.; si v. suppeditet, principatum Trajani senectuti seposui; XXXVII annos v-æ explevit, T.; v. brevis et angusta; longissima, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lif, lifwet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med afseende på deß beskaffenhet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lefnadsförhållanden, lifwets förhållanden, öden,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl med afseende på och för den enskilda menniskan, som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">menniskolifwet, menskliga lifwet, detta lifwet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> denna werlden i allmänhet:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> v. misera, Sa.; v-am inopem coluit, Ter.; v. privata; honorata; beata; suavis; amara; nos ea, quæ sunt in usu v-aque communi, non ea, quæ finguntur aut optantur, spectare debemus; virtutem ex consuetudine v-æ sermonisque nostri interpretemur; iis rebus, quæ tractantur in v-a, modum et ordinem adhibere; acerba multa et varia in hominum v-a fortunaque versantur; imprimis constituendum est, quos nos et quales esse velimus et in quo genere v-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(yrke);</text:span> in perpetuitate v-æ sibi constare; serpit per omnium v-as amicitia; quemadmodum in omni v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(alla lefnadsförhållanden)</text:span> rectissime præcipitur, ut perturbationes fugiamus, - sic ejusmodi motibus debet oratio vacare, C.; Pausanias vir magnus, sed varius in omni genere v-æ, N.; genus hoc inter v-æ versamur, ubi acris invidia atque vigent ubi crimina; fortunata v.; v-æ color; v-æ labores mollire mero; nihil sine magno labore v. dedit homini; respicere exemplar v-æ morumque jubebo doctum imitatorem et vivas hinc ducere voces; simul et jucunda et idonea dicere v-æ, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifwet, det werkliga lifwet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i motsats till theorien, scenen o. s. w.:</text:span> ergo histrio hoc videbit in scena, sapiens non videbit in v-a?, C.<text:line-break/>IV. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lif, samlif, umgänge, umgängessätt:</text:span></text:span> societas v-æ; v-æ communitas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(samhällslifwet);</text:span> v. victusque communis; ambitio <text:soft-page-break/>major, v. tristior; v-ā et sermone horridus, C.; sic v. erat: facile omnes perferre et pati: cum quibus erat quomque una, eis se dedere, eorum studiis obsequi, Ter.<text:line-break/>V. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lif, lefnadssätt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i afseende på sedliga, folkliga, sociala, personliga åtskilnader; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wandel:</text:span></text:span> v. inhonesta, turpis, Sa.; Atticus philosophorum præceptis ad v-am agendam utebatur, N.; libertas vitæ (Germanorum); v. omnis Germanorum in venationibus et in studiis rei militaris consistit, Cs.; pars philosophiæ de v-a et moribus (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moralen);</text:span> v. rustica; sapiens; v-am instituere, agere, C.; ad illa mihi pro se quisque intendat animum, quæ v., qui mores fuerint, L.; hanc olim v-am veteres coluere Sabini; Minos (mortuorum) v-as et crimina discit, Vg.; cælebs v.; integer v-æ scelerisque purus, Hor.; v-æ mollitia; antiqua <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gammaldags);</text:span> v. inculpata, Ov.; ea v. est tua, in qua nihil præteritum excusandum habeas; v. per virtutem acta, T.; v. urbana, Qu.<text:line-break/>VI. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lif</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom föremål för beskrifning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lefnadshistoria, lefnadsteckning:</text:span></text:span> in hoc libro exponemus de v-a excellentium imperatorum; uno volumine v-am excellentium virorum complurium concludere, N.<text:line-break/>VII. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lif</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">själ,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> skild från kroppen; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ande, skugga:</text:span></text:span> v-aque cum gemitu fugit indignata sub umbras; v. per auras concessit mæsta ad manes corpusque reliquit; tenues sine corpore v-æ (<text:span text:style-name="T2">nom. plur.</text:span>), Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifwets, lifs-;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som tillhör lifwet:</text:span> v. calor, vis, ævum; multaque vivendo v-a vincere sæcla (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af lifstid),</text:span> Lucr., C.; halitus, Pn.; viæ v-es, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifwet uppehållande, lifs-:</text:span></text:span> haud, credo, invisus cælestibus auras v-es carpis, Vg.: sanguis, Pn.<text:line-break/>3. vita v. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Werkligt lif,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som är wärdt att l. kan kallas att lefwa (jfr</text:span> innuptæ nuptiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ett olycksamt bröllop,</text:span> C.): quî potest esse vita v., ut ait Ennius, quæ non in amici mutua benevolentia conquiescat?, C. (de Am.).<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som blir wid lif, som kan lefwa, som har kraft att</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utsigt till att lefwa:</text:span></text:span> ero tibi v., Pt.; ut sit v., metuo; mancipium frugi quod sit satis, hoc est, ut v-e putes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så att du ej behöfwer frukta för mitt lif, enligt föreställningen:</text:span> optima quæque fere manibus rapiuntur avaris), Hor. Sat. II. 7. 3; fetus, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītālia</text:span>, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifsorgan, kroppens ädlaste delar:</text:span></text:span> Luc., Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likswepning:</text:span></text:span> Petr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītālĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifskraft:</text:span></text:span> portio v-is est in sanguine, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vītālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På ett lefwande sätt; såsom en lefwande warelse:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvīto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aflifwa, döda:</text:span></text:span> hæc omnia vidi inflammari, Priamo vi vitam evitari, Enn. ap. C. Tusc.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Vahl.</text:span> Enn. Trag. 123 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är bestämd </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">för lefwande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> warelser:</text:span> navis, Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Djurgård</text:span></text:span> (locus sæptus, in quo feræ vivæ pascuntur, Gell.); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fiskdam; bur:</text:span></text:span> v-a suum silvestrium; cochlearum, Pn.; (piscium), Juv. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på skämt:</text:span> pomis et crustis viduas venantur avaras excipiuntque senes, quos in v-a mittant, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med lif begåfwad; lefwande, liflig:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvax</text:span>, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Långlifwad, som lefwer länge,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> seglifwad (mots.</text:span> brevis, brevis ævi):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor och djur:</text:span> heres; mater, Hor.; cervus, Vg.; Sibylla; pater; ănus, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om wäxter och sakliga subject öfwerhufwud: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Långlifwad;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som står länge, håller sig, består länge</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">oförwißnelig, oförgänglig, waraktig:</text:span></text:span> oliva <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(länge grönskande),</text:span> Vg.; apium (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som står grönt sent ut på wintren);</text:span> mortalia facta peribunt: nedum sermonis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(språkets)</text:span> stet honos et gratia v., Hor.; gramen; cæspes; virtus, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liflig, lifskraftig:</text:span></text:span> sulfur; gramen; fecunda semina rerum v-i nutrita sŏlo, Ov.; verba, Luc.; cursus, Gell.; discipulus, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvācĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Seg lifskraft, långt lif; uthållighet, waraktighet:</text:span></text:span> angustis terminis v. ipsa concluditur, Pn. ep. III. 7. 13; lenta, Pn., Qu.; nervosa, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvesco</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvisco</text:span>, vixi, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Få lif; börja lefwa:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blifwa liflig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kraftig:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liflig, lifskraftig, kraftig:</text:span></text:span> evanuit v-um Cæsonis ingenium; exactæ ætatis Camillus erat, sed vegetum ingenium in v-o pectore vigebat, L.; v-a vis animi pervicit; v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lifskraftig)</text:span> tellus tuto res teneras effert in luminis oras, Lucr.; bello v-a virtus; v-a dextra, Vg.; impetus, Hor.; senectus; odium, T.; corpus; animus, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwande, full af lif:</text:span></text:span> signa, Ppt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvĭde</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifligt:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som är wid lif, har lif; mots. död):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor och djur och deras lemmar m. m.:</text:span> v-a cutis; v-um vivere; pater venibit multo potius, quam te me v-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medan jag lefwer)</text:span> unquam sinam egere aut mendicare, Pt.; nemo me lacrimis decoret nec funera fletu faxit. Cur? volito v-us per ora virûm, Enn.; v. vidensque pereo, Ter.; v. et videns cum victu ac vestitu suo publicatus est; v-o videntique funus indicitur; Paulus principis civis personam facile dicendo tuebatur, et vero etiam tum Catone v-o; v-a vox; is orator, v-is ejus æqualibus, par optimis numerabatur, C.; quem quisque v. pugnando locum ceperat, eum, amissa anima, corpore tegebat; ferociam animi, quam habuerat v., in voltu retinens mortuus; persuadet, ut Jugurtham maxime v-um, sin id parum procedat, mortuum sibi traderent, Sa.; v-um capere, in suam potestatem redigere alqm; utroque v-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medan båda woro i lifwet),</text:span> Cs.; v-us tradidit regnum filio; ea, quæ v-o se acciderunt, futura prædixit, N.; laudationem tam æquis auribus mortui (Appii) audivit, quam v-i accusationem audierat (populus), L.; hujus v. eram, mortuus hujus ero, Ppt.; (infera) regna invia v-is; quæ gratia currum (curruum) armorumque fuit v-is - eadem sequitur tellure repostos, Vg.; v-a adhuc membra, viscera; sanguis; caro; pascitur in v-is livor, post fata quiescit. Tunc suus e merito quemque tuetur honos, Ov.; <text:soft-page-break/>Lamiæ puerum v-um extrahit alvo; unus v-orum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ensam af alle nu lefwande),</text:span> Hor.; sentit v-us eam, quæ mortuis præstari solet, venerationem, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om wäxter och andra naturföremål:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwande, frisk:</text:span></text:span> cæspes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grön),</text:span> Hor.; quin ante v-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rinnande)</text:span> perfunderis flumine?, L.; se flumine v-o abluere; plantaria <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> viviradix), Vg.; radix; arundo; virga etiamnunc v-a; fons; neu tu Vestam aliud, quam v-am intellige flammam, Ov.; gurges, Qu.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Naturlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ej bearbetad):</text:span> v-o sedilia saxo; antra pumice v-o, Vg., Ov.<text:line-break/>c <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om konstwerk: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (uttrycksfull; som tyckes lefwa):</text:span> v-os ducent e marmore vultus, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i mots. till det, som blott har sin tillwaro i minnet:</text:span> (Amor) paulatim abolere Sichæum incipit - et v-o prævertere amore jam pridem resides animos, Vg.<text:line-break/>e. cujus facta v-a vigent, Næv. ap. Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liflig, känslig:</text:span></text:span> scio, quam sit tibi v. et ingenuus animus, Pn. ep. VIII. 6. 17.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det lefwande af en kropp, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Friska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (röda) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">köttet; köttet:</text:span></text:span> ad v-um resecare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skära upp till - = nagelfara med en sak):</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kapital:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifwande:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vīvĭrādix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sättqwist med rot:</text:span></text:span> C. (de Sen. XV. 12); alii malleolo, alii v-e conseri vineam melius existimant; semina consortio v-um liberata facilius convalescunt, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convīvo</text:span>, (vixi, victum), 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa tillsammans med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span>): Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spisa, hålla gästabud tillsammans:</text:span></text:span> cum aliquo, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convictio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samlif, umgänge:</text:span></text:span> jucundissima, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convictor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Umgängesbroder, -wän; bordskamrat:</text:span></text:span> domestici; utor familiaribus et quotidianis c-bus, quos Cratippus adduxit, C. ep.; Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convictus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samlif,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> enskildt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">umgänge:</text:span></text:span> detrahere aliquid alteri contra naturam est: tollit enim c-um humanum et societatem, C.; M. Brutus Atticum non solum consilii principem habuit, sed etiam in c-u, N.; longi c-us, Ov.; facilis, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gästabud, måltidslag, gille</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kalas):</text:span> luxuria c-us, Vell.; tracto in longum c-u; c-bus et hospitiis non alia gens effusius indulget (quam Germani), T.; in c-bus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convīva</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bordsgäst, gästabudskamrat, gäst:</text:span></text:span> hilarissimus; commodus, Pt.; hilaris et bene acceptus; alicujus consessores, c-æ, contubernales; est in Originibus Catonis, solitos esse in epulis canere c-as ad tibiam de clarorum hominum virtutibus (Tusc. I. 2; Brut. 19); apud Atticum non minus animo, quam ventre c-æ delectabantur, N.; occidit et Pelopis genitor c. deorum; raro, qui - exacto contentus tempore vita cedat uti c. satur, reperire queamus, Hor.; ut vitæ plenus c. recede, Lucr.; c-æ meæ, Pompon. ap. Non.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convīvālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gästabuds-,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som förekommer, uppföres wid gästabud:</text:span> oblectamenta, L., vestis, Sen.; ludus, Ct.; fabulæ c-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(-snack),</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convīvium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gästabud, gille, gladt lag:</text:span></text:span> nunquam per vinum ex me exoritur discidium in c-o; me c-i tæsumst, Pt.; bene majores nostri accubitionem epularem amicorum, quia vitæ conjunctionem haberet, c. nominarunt; tempestivis c-is delector; turpe est in re severa c-i dicta inferre; c. publicum; c-i moderati et honesti non est saltatio; c. opipare apparatum, C.; c. celebrare, concelebrare, C., T.; nemo in c-o Attici aliud acroama audivit, quam anagnosten; in c-o accubare; ducere, adhibere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medhafwa, medföra)</text:span> in c-um, N.; magis in decoris armis, quam in c-is lubidinem habere; sordidum me et incultis moribus ajunt, quia parum scite c. adorno, Sa.; nos c-a, nos proelia virginum - cantamus; nimis arta premunt olidæ c-a capræ, Hor.; curare mutua inter se c-a; c-a læta frequentant, Vg.; c-a agitare, Pt., Ov.; proceres ineunt c-a regis; in vicem ineunt c-a; inque repentinos c-a versa tumultus assimulare freto possis, quod sæva quietum ventorum rabies motis exasperat undis, Ov.; sus animal ad c-a natum, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convīvor</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Convivo, Enn.), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fira gästabud</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gladt lag:</text:span></text:span> solitus est non modo in publico, sed de publico c-ri, C.; crebro, Ter., Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convīvātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som anställer gästabud; wärd:</text:span></text:span> scitus, L.; c-is uti ducis ingenium res adversæ nudare solent, celare secundæ, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervīvo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa alltjemnt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ända till:</text:span></text:span> ad summam ætatem, Pt. Capt. 742.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvīvo</text:span>, vixi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fortfara att lefwa, förblifwa i lifwet:</text:span></text:span> spe sustentatam p-isse reor, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvīvo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa åter:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvīvisco</text:span>, vixi, victum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Komma till lif igen, få lif på nytt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> apes, Varr.; galli cantum audivit, avum (qui natione Gallus erat) r-isse putat; quum sol illuxisset, r-isse sibi videbantur, C.; anima moribunda, Ov.; pennæ r-unt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäxa ut igen),</text:span> Pn.; secuere membra non r-turi senis (natæ Peliæ), Sen. trag.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bilder:</text:span> respublica r-at atque recreetur; a metu; causa Pompejanorum jugulata; civitates legibus suis et judiciis usæ r-xerunt; senatus ad auctoritatis pristinæ spem r-it, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕdĭvīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som lefwer upp igen, kommer i bruk på nytt:</text:span> lapis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gammal sten till ny byggnad),</text:span> C.; gens; bella, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Irrĕdĭvīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oersättlig, oupprättlig:</text:span></text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭpervīvo</text:span>, vixi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerlefwa:</text:span></text:span> alicui, Js.; gloriæ suæ Virginius, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vix,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knappt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med swårighet, med nöd; näppeligen:</text:span></text:span> v. ægro cum corde meo me somnus reliquit; advenio Acherunte v. via alta atque ardua, Enn.; v. reprimor, quin te manere jubeam; v. ægreque; quadrigas si nunc inscendas Jovis, v. poteris effugere infortunium, Pt.; v. possum; v. <text:soft-page-break/>aut ne v. quidem apparent; v. teneor, quin accurram, C.; iter angustum et difficile, v. qua singuli carri ducerentur, Cs.; v. instantes sustinebant clades; v. ad quietas stationes viribus sufficiebant, L.; v. durare carinæ possunt imperiosius æquor, Hor.; v. semel admittit, quum sæpe negavit, Ppt.; v. quicquam firmare ausim; v. duobus ictibus caput amputavit, T.; Corbulo v. ferret tot vasa ingentia, tot res impositas capiti, Juv.; v. ego lecticam subsequor: ille feret, Mt.; v. ipsa tantum; v. adhuc credo malum, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med afseende på mått, tal, tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knappt, knappast, nätt och jemnt:</text:span></text:span> hic sunt v. tres minæ, Ter.; v. singulis ætatibus singuli tolerabiles oratores inveniuntur; quam diu in oratorum enumeratione versamur, quum tamen spisse atque v. - ad Antonium Crassumque pervenimus; v. tandem legi literas; vixdum legeram, quum ille venit, C.; v. agmen novissimum extra munitiones processerat, quum Galli - committere proelium non dubitant, Cs.; v. ea fatus eram, tremere omnia visa repente, Vg.; vixdum perfunctum eum bello atrocior domi seditio excepit, L.; quarta v. demum exponimur hora, Hor.; vixdum finierat Maternus, quum Vipstanus cubiculum ejus intravit; vixdum ingressus Illyricum Tiberius properis matris literis accitur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vixdum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vix 2.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vixet = vixisset <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> Vivo: Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ulcer . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ulcus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ulcisco</text:span> (Enn.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ulciscor,</text:span> ultus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.,</text:span> L.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämna, hämnas:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämna, -nas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn (sig l. annan) = skaffa hämnd, upprättelse:</text:span> patrem (Agamemnona) materno sanguine u-rem, Enn. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Vahl.</text:span> Trag. 184); quid tam necessarium, quam tenere semper arma, quibus possis - te u-i lacessitus?; dolorem suum, Cs. (Afr.); triumphavere ob iras graviter ultas, L.; sanguinem nostrum, Sa.; subit ira cadentem u-i patriam et sceleratas sumere poenas, Vg.; mente vesana feror partes in omnes, unde me u-i queam, Sen. tr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnas på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquem, aliquid</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicujus scelus</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ngn för hans brott):</text:span> inimicos, Pt.; alqm pro re, pro scelere, Ter., Cs.; alqm aliqua re; mortem alicujus; injurias, injuriis; odi hominem et odero: utinam u-i possem! sed illum u-entur mores sui, C.; si quam injuriam acceperat, oblivisci quam u-i maluit; injurias patriæ, N.; proscripti Regis Rupili pus atque venenum hybrida quo pacto sit Persius ultus, opinor omnibus - notum - esse, Hor.; Alphesiboea suos ulta est pro conjuge fratres, Ppt.; privatas injurias, Cs.; sævitiam centurionum, T.; - suas quoque injurias ultum irent, L.; quidquid sine sanguine civium ulcisci nequitur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att inf.</text:span> ulcisci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">här är passiv, behöfwer wäl ej antagas),</text:span> impune sit, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnd; straff:</text:span></text:span> concupiscere, Sen.; petere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uttaga)</text:span> ab aliquo; ara u-is; u-i mactari, T.; voluptas u-is, Qu.; prima hæc est u., quod se judice nemo nocens absolvitur, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af l. för ngn, ngt (med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så wäl af den, på hwilken hämnd utkräfwes, som af den, åt hwilken hämnd l. upprättelse förwärfwas):</text:span> conjurationis investigator et u.; u. injuriarum, C.; matronæ Brutum ut parentem luxerunt, quod tam <text:soft-page-break/>acer u. violatæ pudicitiæ fuisset; invocati u-es parentum dii, L.; exoriare aliquis nostris ex ossibus u., Vg.; patiens (Augustus) vocari Cæsaris u., Hor. [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Mars med tillnamnet</text:span> Ultor (Cæsaris u.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hade ett af Augustus uppfördt tempel å</text:span> Forum Augusti, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af hwilket ännu några colonner återstå</text:span>]; victor Asiæ, u. Europæ (Agamemnon), Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnarinna, hämnande:</text:span></text:span> u. afflictæ civitatis, C.; luctus et u-es posuere cubilia curæ, Vg.; pia soror, impia mater, u. (Meleagri) Althæa, Sen. trag.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnultus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ohämnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som ej fått hämnd l. upprättelse):</text:span> faxo haud i-um prandium comederis, Pt.; vitam, ne i. esset, ad incertissimam spem reservavit, C.; nos, nisi damnose bibimus, moriemur i-i; preces i-æ, Hor.; nunquam hodie moriemur i-i, Vg.; non impune feremus, quæque inhonoratæ, non et dicemur i-æ; i-os flere dolores, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ostraffad:</text:span></text:span> cur eum i-um esse sinitis?; injuriæ impunitæ et i-æ, C.; i-um aliquid auferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(få l. hafwa gjort ngt ostraffadt),</text:span> Ter.; i-us ut tu riseris Cotyttia!; si cui videor non justus, i-o dicere, quod sentit, permitto, Hor.; i-us (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oskadd)</text:span> hostem subeuntem prohibuit, Ct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnulte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ostraffadt:</text:span></text:span> Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ulcus,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Warsår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bulnad, sår:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> u-is æstus, Acc.; stultus incurata pudor malus u-a celat, Hor.; ferro rescindere summum u-is os, Vg.; u. serpit; u-a aperire, fovere, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bilder:</text:span> u. tangere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trampa ngn på bölden, beröra någons swaga sida),</text:span> Ter.; quidquid horum attigeris, u. est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swårighet);</text:span> tu in hoc u-e tanquam unguis exsistis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">upprifwer, förwärrar det onda),</text:span> C.; u. (ɔ: amoris), Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ulcĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Såra:</text:span></text:span> serpentis morsu u-tus, C. poēt.; lumbos mulæ onere, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ulcĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sårnad:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Exulcĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Komma att bulna; göra sårig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">upprifwa sår:</text:span></text:span> pulmonem, Ce.; pulex aurem, Varr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sinne, själssmärtor o. d.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprifwa, såra, förbittra:</text:span></text:span> ea, quæ sanare nequeunt, e-ant; animum alicui, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Exulcĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bulnad, -nande:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Exulcĕrātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förorsakar sår, håller sår öppet:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Exulcĕrātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: vis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕdulcĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ånyo komma att bulna; upprifwa:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ulcĕrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sårig; full af bulnader:</text:span></text:span> facies Tiberii, T.; arbor, Pn.; - jecur (amantis), Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ulcuscŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Litet sår:</text:span></text:span> oris, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">U</text:span>lia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Hispanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Uliginosus, -ligo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Uveo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ŭ</text:span>lixes, is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ĕi (<text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span> -em, Hor.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mindre riktigt:</text:span> Ulysses): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. konung på Ithaca, gr. Odysseus.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ŭlixēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Ullus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ulmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alm</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofta omtalad såsom anwänd till stöd för winrankor l. till ris att piska ngn med):</text:span> u-orum Acheruns <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(almars graf</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på hwilken spön sönderslitas),</text:span> Pt.; u-is adjungere vites; fecundæ frondibus u-i, Vg.; piscium genus hæsit u-o, nota quæ sedes fuerat columbis; amicta vitibus u., Hor.; marita, Qu.; stratus humi palmes viduas desiderat u-os, Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ulmārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Almskog:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ulmeus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alm-, af alm:</text:span></text:span> virga; virgidemia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr detta ord);</text:span> vide modo, u-æ catapultæ tuum ne transfigant latus, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ulmĭtrĭba</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alm-spöslitare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ulna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gr.</text:span> ὠλένη):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arm; armbåge:</text:span></text:span> terrestrium solus homo bipes. Uni juguli, humeri: ceteris armi, uni u-æ, Pn. XI. 43. 98; puer patris tremula dormiens in u-a, Catl.; Tithonum Aurora suis decedens fovit in u-is, Ppt.; mollibus u-is tollere alqm, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom mått:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. dic, quibus in terris, et eris mihi magnus Apollo, tres pateat cæli spatium non amplius u-as, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Famn:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">U</text:span>lpiānus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: Domitius U., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berömd jurist på Alexander Severi tid.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">U</text:span>lpius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn för en rom. slägt, till hwilken kejsar Trajanus hörde.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uls</text:span> <text:line-break/>(ouls), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På andra sidan om; hinsidan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots. till</text:span> cis; = ultrā): u. Cato pro ultra posuit, Fs.; u. Tiberim, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T3">Ulter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obrukligt</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwaraf förekomma casus:)</text:span><text:line-break/>I.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultrā</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl. sing.;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> contrā, extrā, quā):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På andra sidan, hinsides:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. (i rummet):</text:span> procedere, Cs.; quo tenditis, inquit, quos alios muros, quæ jam u. moenia habetis?, Vg.; dextera deriguit nec citra mota nec u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(der man skulle wäntat</text:span> ultro = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åt andra sidan),</text:span> Ov. Met. V. 186.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. om tid l. sak: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derutöfwer; ytterligare, längre, widare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mera): -</text:span> ne quid u. requiratis; u. quo progrediar, quam ut verisimilia videam, non habeo; u. quam satis est, oportet, C.; u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= på andra sidan om grafwen)</text:span> nec gaudio neque curæ locus est, Sa.: non u. dilatum bellum gliscens; Aequi Tullium haud u. tulere ducem, L.; est quadam prodire tenus, si non datur u.; quid u. tendis? æqua tellus pauperi recluditur regumque pueris; insani sapiens nomen ferat, æquus iniqui, u., quam satis est, virtutem si petit ipsam, Hor.; non sustinet u.; quid u. exspectare potes?, Ov.; melius u. quam citra stet oratio, Qu.; suspectum jam nimiæ spei u. extulit Tiberius, T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. (i rummet): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På andra sidan om; hinsidan, utöfwer:</text:span></text:span> u. fossam, Enn.; u. eum castra posuit, Cs.; u. villam est vilula sordida, C.; u. Padum, L.; meam canto Lalagen et u. terminum curis vagor expeditus, Hor.; Euphraten u.; u. agros decumates Chatti initium <text:soft-page-break/>silvæ Hercyniæ incohant, T.; dextram proferre u. sinum, Qu.; u. Sauromatas fugere hinc libet et glacialem Oceanum, Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tid l. sak: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På andra sidan, utöfwer, öfwer:</text:span></text:span> u. modum progredi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerskrida),</text:span> C.; est modus in rebus, sunt certi denique fines, u. quos citraque nequit consistere rectum; sunt, quibus in satira videar nimis aeer et u. legem tendere opus, Hor.; omnes pelagi minas cælique ferebat invalidus u. vires sortemque senectæ, Vg.: hæc u. quid erit?, Juv.; hoc u. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efter)</text:span> Socratem duravit; cacozelon est, quidquid est u. virtutem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerdrifwet),</text:span> quum quis specie boni fallitur; paulum u. primas literas progressus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i studier),</text:span> Qu.; potestas non u. biennium valuit, T.<text:line-break/>II.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultrō</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> citro, retro, contro, quo, eo, huc), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åt andra sidan:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillsammans med</text:span> citro: ultro citroque = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åt begge sidor) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fram och tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> u. citroque commeare, Varr.: cursare, C.; legatos mittere, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bort:</text:span></text:span> u. istum (ɔ: abducite) a me, Pt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. ultro citroque = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ömsesidigt, å</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (åt, från) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">båda sidor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ömse sidor:</text:span></text:span> beneficia, officia u. citroque data et accepta, C. <text:line-break/>b. ultro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(syn.</text:span> sponte): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åt andra sidan, från sin sida, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af sig sjelf; sjelf, utan skäl,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> utan anledning från andra sidan (objectets sida); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">friwilligt, ej utmanad; onödd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w., </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">först:</text:span></text:span> impetum occupemus facere u. in regem; u. se ostentum obtulit, Acc.; arcessor, Ter.; Pyrrhus Romanis bellum u. intulit (de Off. I. §. 40), C.; Sa.; id, quod ante petenti denegarat, u. pollicebantur; magna pars Aquitaniæ sese dedidit obsidesque u. misit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> b. G. IV. 27), Cs.; hic stilus haud petet u. quenquam animantem; quod petet, u. defer, Hor.; u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af sig sjelf)</text:span> se offerre, occurrere; u. donare, exhortari, Qu.; rogare u. et ambire, T. (Dial. 9); regi minatur u. Quis exulem credat?, Sen.; u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(först)</text:span> compellare virum, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Å sin sida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">twärtom, å andra sidan, i stället</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (syn.</text:span> vicissim; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Aubert i Tidskrift for Philologi og Pædagogik</text:span> I. 112 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.):</text:span> ubi disputata est ratio cum argentario, plus ipsus u. debet argentario, Pt.; novi ingenium mulierum: nolunt, ubi velis: ubi nolis, cupiunt u., Ter.; Cicero ne nocturnum quidem sibi tempus ad quietem sumpsit, ut u. militum vocibus sibi parcere cogeretur, Cs.; latrones Remum captum Amulio tradunt u. accusantes; Galli vim facere conati u. pellebantur, L.; difficilem et morosum offendet garrulus: u. non etiam sileas, Hor. Sat. II. 5. 90. 91; a legatis bellum suadentibus, postquam impellere nequiverunt, crimen ac dolus u. compositus, T. Hist. I. 7; non interrogantes u. percontari, Qu.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deßutom, till på köpet, än widare:</text:span></text:span> quoniam, erus quod imperavit, neglexisti persequi, nunc venis etiam u. irrisum erum, Pt.; multis u. vulneribus illatis impetum hostium fortissime sustinuerant, Cs.; his lacrimis vitam damus et miserescimus u., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultrōneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Friwillig:</text:span></text:span> jussi an u-i?, Sen.; Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultrōtrĭbūtum</text:span> (ultro tributum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Friwillig gåfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">afgift:</text:span></text:span> virtus est in u-is, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultĕrior</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. Comp.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På andra sidan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> warande l. befintlig; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">längre borta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> warande, boende, stående, befintlig; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">aflägsnare:</text:span></text:span> Gallia u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på andra sidan Alperna),</text:span> Cs. (b. G. I. 7), C., Sa.; quum a proximis impetrare non possent, u-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(aflägsnare)</text:span> temptant; portus u., Cs.; tendebantque manus ripæ u-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(andra)</text:span> amore, Vg.; inter Hercyniam silvam Rhenumque et Moenum amnes Helvetii, u-ra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det som ligger på andra sidan derom)</text:span> Boji, Gallica utraque gens, tenuere, T.; spatium u-ius medio, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tal, tid, grad, sak: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ytterligare, (mera), fjermare, aflägsnare;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt om tid i motsats till närwarande så wäl </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förfluten,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillkommande:</text:span></text:span> set eccum ipsum. Quis ille u. est?, Ter.; pudor est u-ra loqui, Ov.; spes nulla u-ior, didicit jam dives avarus tantum admirari, tantum laudare disertos, ut pueri Junonis avem, Juv.; præteritum perfectum et u-ius (h. e. plusquamperfectum) non invenitur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af stammen</text:span> fero); opus est naturali quadam mobilitate animi, ut, dum proxima dicimus, u-ra struere possimus, Qu.; u-ra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(andra tider)</text:span> mirari, præsentia sequi: bonos imperatores voto expetere, qualescunque tolerare, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultĕrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Längre (bort), ytterligare, widare:</text:span></text:span> quoties - rogabat u. justo, Prognen ita velle ferebat; non tulit u., Ov.; si me u. provexerit ira, ostendes matri brachia læsa tuæ, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultĭmus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Ultumus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. Superl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ytterst, fjermast, aflägsnast, längst borta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rummet:</text:span> in terras solus orasque u-as sum circumvectus, Pt.; u-æ gentes, Enn.; in u-a platea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= ändan af -),</text:span> Ter.; in infinito inani nec summum nec infimum nec medium nec u-um nec citimum est; u-æ terræ; u-a Gallia, C.; Augustus ex u-is terris, quid ageret, certiorem fecit Atticum, N.; nationes; fines, Cs.; tibi serviat u-a Thule; locus, Vg.; u. circulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(polarcirkeln);</text:span> u-a tellus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jordens ändar);</text:span> ardua prima - u-a prona <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(början - slutet)</text:span> via est et eget moderamine certo, Ov.; u-a Hesperia, Africa; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bild:</text:span> moriar: mors u-a linea rerum, Hor.; syllaba, Qu.; veniet annis secula seris, quibus non sit terris u-a Thule, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aflägsnast</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i det förflutna l. i framtiden); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ytterst:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Först:</text:span></text:span> pueritiæ memoriam recordari u-am; principium; initium, C.; ab origine u-a stirpis Romanæ, N.; sanguinis u. auctor, Vg.; u-æ causæ, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sist:</text:span></text:span> u-a Cumææ venit jam carminis ætas, magnus ab integro seclorum vertitur ordo; arma, viri, ferte arma, vocat lux u-a victos, Vg.; hiems, Hor.; lapis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grafsten),</text:span> Ppt.; u-a semper exspectanda dies homini dicique beatus ante obitum nemo - debet; u-a cælestum terras Astræa reliquit; vox, Ov.; u-um operum mortalium; u-um illud visuri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för att kasta den - sorglige och oumbärlige - siste blicken på sitt hem),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ytterst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i grad l. sak, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">högst:</text:span></text:span> senatus consultum; supplicium, Cs.; u-a crudelitas; experiri u-a; u-um discrimen; poena, L.; ardor, Ov. (Met. IX. 562); scelus, Ct.; sicut vetus ætas vidit, quid u-um in libertate esset, ita nos, quid in servitute, T.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sämst, wärst, lägst:</text:span></text:span> miles, L.; principibus placuisse viris non u-a laus est, Hor.; pati u-a L.; infelix properas u-a nosse mala, Ppt.; <text:soft-page-break/>stirps, Vell.; plebs, Ct.; volgi pars u-a, Juv. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultĭmum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rum: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräns; mål:</text:span></text:span> u. mundi, C.; u-a stagni, Ov.; oculis u-a signant, Vg.; ad u-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= till slut),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slut;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> prægn. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">död, dödsfara:</text:span></text:span> u-a exspectato, C.; quando u-a cernunt, his se defendere certant, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräns</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i grad l. sak: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">det högsta, wärsta:</text:span></text:span> u. bonorum, C.: u. orationis, certaminis, L.; u-a passi, Ov.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mål:</text:span></text:span> C. de Fin. III. §. 25.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultĭme</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wärst, sämst, uslast:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ultĭmo</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sist, till slut:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pænultĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Näst-siste:</text:span></text:span> Aus. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pænultĭma</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">näst-sista stafwelsen, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Penultima:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ultio, Ultor, Ultrix <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ulciscor.<text:line-break/>Ultra, -tro, -tronens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ulter, Uls.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ulva,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waß, säf, rör</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i kärr, sjö, flod):</text:span> mollis; palustris, Ov.; delitui in u-a, Vg.; Hor., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ulvōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waßrik:</text:span></text:span> Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ŭ</text:span>lŭbræ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten stad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ŭlŭbrānus, <text:line-break/>Ŭlŭbrensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ŭlŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uggla, uf:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ŭlŭlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjuta, hyla, skria, wråla;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om döda subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skalla:</text:span></text:span> canere voce u-anti, C.; canes (per umbram), Enn., Vg., Ov.; Agāve (Baccha), Ov.; lupi; Nymphæ, Vg.; saga, Hor.; - cavæ ædes plangoribus femineis u-ant, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med skri åkalla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en person:</text:span> Hecate triviis u-ta per urbem, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med skri uppfylla</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genomwråla) ett ställe:</text:span> St., Cd. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ŭlŭlābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjutande, skrikande, skränande:</text:span></text:span> clamor, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ŭlŭlātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjutande, wrål, skrän, rop:</text:span></text:span> Galli suo more victoriam conclamant atque u-um tollunt; clamore et u-u suorum animos confirmant, Cs.; tripudia et u., L.; femineo u-u consonat omne nemus, Vg.; Bacchēi, festi u-us; longi, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Exŭlŭlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upphäfwa tjut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wrål:</text:span></text:span> Lycaon lupus factus, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med skri uppwäcka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anropa:</text:span></text:span> Thyas e-ta; dea e-ta, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ulysses <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ulixes.<text:line-break/>Umbella <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Umbra.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">U</text:span>mber, bra, brum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">italiskt folkslagsnamn, umbrisk;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Umbrer:</text:span> Plautus U. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> umbra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ordleken,</text:span> Pt. Most. 756). <text:line-break/>Umbria, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: U. Romani patria Callimachi (Propertii). <text:line-break/>Umbrĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">umbrisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Umbĭlīcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> umbo): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nafle:</text:span></text:span> L., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mußla:</text:span></text:span> conchas et u-os ad litus legere, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Staf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stock,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> omkring hwilken en bokrulle wecklades (rullades) och hwilken sålunda bildade centrum af den hoprullade volumen; enkannerligen äro</text:span> umbilici = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">knapparne, ändarne, bucklorna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af denne stock (Marquardt,</text:span> V. 2. 395): in fine libri u-i ex ligno aut osse solent esse, Porphyr. ad Hor. Ep. XIV. 8; iambos ad u-um adducere (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afsluta),</text:span> Catl.; picti u-i; jam pervenimus usque ad u-os, Mt. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wisare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på soluret:</text:span> Pn.; dies quidem jam ad <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter)</text:span> u-um est dimidiatus mortuus, Pt. Men. I. 2. 45.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Midt, medelpunkt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> centrum af ngt:</text:span> Henna u. Siciliæ, C.; Apollo, qui u-um certum terrarum obtines (i. e. Delphos), (Acc.?) ap. C. de Div. II. §. 115 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Varr.; Græciæ incolere u-um; in medio u-o Græciæ conspici, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utsprång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Umbĭlīcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nafleformig:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Umbo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> umbilicus):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Buckla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> utskjutande spets i midten af en sköld (jfr Rich, Dictionnaire etc.):</text:span> Cossus assurgentem regem u-e resupinat repetitumque sæpius cuspide ad terram affixit; u-bus incussaque ala sternuntur hostes, L.; telum imbelle sine ictu clipei - u-e pependit, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sköld:</text:span></text:span> texere salignas u-um crates, Vg.; u-e se protegere, Js.; bellum u-e propellit, Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Armbåge:</text:span></text:span> in turbam incideris: cuneos u-e repellet (libertus), Mt.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bröstflik,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> del af togan, hwilken drogs fram öfwer</text:span> sinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ofwanpå bröstet:</text:span> Tert. de pallio 5 ap. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Marquardt</text:span> V. 2. 165; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton.</text:span> = toga: jam candidus (ɔ: virilis) u., Ps.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utsprång,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> utskjutande del af ngt: af perla,</text:span> Pn.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af berg,</text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Umbra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skugga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: skugga, skuggbild:</text:span> mihi u. nusquamst, nisi si in puteo quæpiamst, Pt.; platani u-am secutus est Socrates; terræ u.; metuere suam u-am, C.; nolite, hospites, ad me adire: illico isti: ne contagio mea bonis u-ve obsit, Enn. ap. C.; spissis noctis se condidit u-is; majoresque cadunt de montibus u-æ, Vg.; u-as dare, præbere rei; sol exiguas fecerat u-as; amoena; æstiva; apta pastoribus, Ov.; arboris antiquæ quā levis u. cadit -, Tib.; u. corpore minor; u. cadit, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mörkret, afton, natt:</text:span></text:span> ad u-am lucis ab ortu, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skugga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i mots. till dager å målningar o. d.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ars invenit u-as et lumen, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bild:</text:span> habeat illa summa in dicendo admiratio u-am et recessum, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skuggrikt ställe</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. hwad som gifwer skugga:</text:span> ruris opaci u-as falce premere; spargite humum foliis, inducite fontibus umbras (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bekransen),</text:span> Vg.; vacua tonsoris in u-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tält?),</text:span> Hor.; spatiari in Pompeja u-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(park wid Pompeji theater),</text:span> Ppt.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skugga, skenbild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngn, enkannerligen af en afliden, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wålnad;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">de döde, underjordens inwånare, underjorden;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">en,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> liksom</text:span> manes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> cineres: ne reamur u-as inter vivos volitare, Lucr.; u-a Creūsæ; salvete recepti nequiquam cineres <text:soft-page-break/>animæque u-æque paternæ; crudelibus occubat u-is (= versatur apud infernos); tristes, Vg.; victor cum victis pariter misceberis u-is: consule cum Mario, capte Jugurtha, sedes, Ppt.; rex u-arum; senilis Anchisæ u.; exsangues sine corpore et ossibus; recentes; gelidæ; silentes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> silentum; maternæ (= matris) u-æ, Ov.; nos ubi decidimus, quo pater Aeneas, quo dives Tullus et Ancus, pulvis et u. sumus, Hor.; apertum Tænaron u-is, Luc.; di majorum u-is tenuem et sine pondere terram - qui præceptorem sancti voluere parentis esse loco, Juv.; audi, si quis remanet sensus in u-is; exstinctus u-as agitat infestus meas (Agrippinæ), Sen. Oct.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skugga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = client l. snyltgäst, som objuden följer med sin</text:span> dominus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> rex <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till gästabud:</text:span> Pt.; u-as adducere, Hor.<text:line-break/>7. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skugga = undangömd wistelseort, wrå; opractiskt, undangömdt eller obemärkt lif:</text:span> studia in u-a educata, Sen.; genus ignavum, quod lecto gaudet et u-a, Juv.<text:line-break/>8. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skugga = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skydd:</text:span></text:span> in u-a auxilii alicujus latere, L.<text:line-break/>9. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skugga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sken, liknelse,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> swag bild, qwarlefwa af, tillstymmelse till ngt:</text:span> nullam habemus solidam effigiem veri juris et germanæ justitiæ: u-is et imaginibus utimur; gloriæ u-as consectari; ne u-am quidem τοῦ καλοῦ vidit, C.; stat magni nominis u., Luc.; magni resto nominis u., Sen. tr.<text:line-break/>10. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en fisk:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Umbella</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Solskärm:</text:span></text:span> viridis, Juv. IX. 50; Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slag af blomsättning hos wäxter: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Umbella:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Umbrĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som skänker skugga; skugg-gifwande, skuggrik:</text:span></text:span> platanus; Academia, C.; nemus, Vg.; saltus, Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som bär</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">för skuggor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wålnader):</text:span> undæ (Stygis), St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Umbro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gifwa skugga; beskugga, skygga, öfwerskygga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (betäcka), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hölja:</text:span></text:span> virga u-at, Col.; terram floribus, Lucr.; tempora quercu u. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kransa),</text:span> Vg.; forum velis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerspänna med),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Umbrācŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. ngt, som skänker skugga, der man njuter skugga:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skuggig plats, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skjul, (tält), skygd:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> alnorum, C.; texunt u-a vites, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> ex eruditorum u-is (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skolor)</text:span> in solem productus (orator), C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Solskärm:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr Rich);</text:span> pellunt u-a soles aurea, Ov. Fast. II. 309; Mt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om en för tillfället tillwägabragt skärm:</text:span> operata deo pubes discumbit in herba, arboris antiquæ qua levis umbra cadit: aut e veste sua tendent u-a sertis vincta -, Tib. II. 5. 95 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.</text:span><text:line-break/>3. pilei u. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skyfwe:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Umbrātĭcŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: (colo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som söker eller ligger i skuggan: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wekling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> umbra 6): Pt. Truc. II. 7. 49 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Spengel).</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Umbrātĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som söker skuggan, trifwes i skuggan:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. homo u. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lätting, wekling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som skyr ansträngning, sol och swett l. dam,</text:span> ”impatiens pulveris atque solis”, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> Hor. Carm. I. 8), Pt. Curc. 556; Epicureorum turba u-a (quæ quiescit in hortulis, C. de Or. III. §. 63), Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wistas l. sker i hemmet l. i skolan, i motsats till det yttre l. </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offentliga lifwet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skol-, huslig:</text:span></text:span> doctor, Petr.; negotium, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Umbrātĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till det (undangömda) enskilda, theoretiska lifwet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skole-, skolmässig, opractisk:</text:span></text:span> vita u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åt studier egnadt lif);</text:span> exercitatio (dicendi) domestica et u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(opractisk);</text:span> mollis est et u. oratio philosophorum, C.; literæ, Pn.; vita, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ădumbro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerskygga, beskugga:</text:span></text:span> vineam tegetibus; uvas tegumentis, Col. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Teckna, afteckna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. ars pictoris aliquid, Val.; quis pictor omnia, quæ in rerum natura sunt, a-re didicit?, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. uttryck = i föreställningen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Teckna, göra sig en bild af, i tal framställa, teckna:</text:span></text:span> excellentis eloquentiæ speciem et formam a.; heroum veteres casus fictosque luctus imitari et a-re dicendo, C.; literas inani specie libertatis a., L.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Efterlikna:</text:span></text:span> Persis Macedonum morem a-re indecorum est, Ct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ădumbrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Diktad, låtsad, föreställd, skenbar, sken-:</text:span></text:span> in scena rebus fictis et a-is locus est; opinione a-a honestatis; suffragia, comitia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott skenbara);</text:span> vir a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(diktad),</text:span> C.; lætitia, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blott tecknad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">antydd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till en plastisk bild l. figur l. klar föreställning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skugg-:</text:span></text:span> cedo mihi istorum a-orum deorum lineamenta et formam; consectatur nullam eminentem effigiem virtutis, sed a-am imaginem gloriæ; a-æ intelligentiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dunkla, abstracta begrepp),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ădumbrātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I skuggritning:</text:span></text:span> Lucr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ădumbrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skuggritning, utkast:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utkast, antydning, tillstymmelse:</text:span></text:span> nulla est laus oratoris, cujus in nostris orationibus non sit aliqua, si non perfectio, at conatus tamen atque a., C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Låtsande, sken:</text:span></text:span> Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnumbro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kasta skugga öfwer, beskugga, öfwerskygga;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwerhölja, betäcka:</text:span></text:span> terra i-atur; ora coronis, Lucr.; toros obtentu frondis; palma vestibulum, Vg.; vespera i-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utbreder sina skuggor),</text:span> T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördunkla:</text:span></text:span> dignitatem alicujus, Pn. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra utkast till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> aliquid, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ŏbumbro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerskygga;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hölja, betäcka, fördunkla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> oleaster vestibulum; o-ant æthera telis, Vg.; lucus templum, Ov.; palmes vitis Asiam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i Astyagis dröm),</text:span> Js.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bemantla:</text:span></text:span> crimen sub re, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördunkla:</text:span></text:span> nomen alicujus, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förswara, skydda:</text:span></text:span> nomen reginæ alqm, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Præumbro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördunkla, undanskymma allt:</text:span></text:span> p-ante imperatoris fastigio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> præpotens), T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Umbrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skuggig, skuggrik</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (så wäl om det, som skänker skuggan, som om det beskuggade):</text:span> locus æstate u-ior, C.; vallis; caverna; cacumina fagi; arbos, Vg.; in u-is Heliconis oris; ripa; nunc et in u-is Fauno decet immolare lucis, Hor.; u-a tecta Priapi, Tib.; silva, Ppt.; nemus, Ov.; Dis, Sen. trag.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">U</text:span>mbrēnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Umbria, -bricus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Umber.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">U</text:span>mbricius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Umbrifer <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Umbra.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">U</text:span>mbro, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Etrurien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Umbro (-are), -brosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Umbra.<text:line-break/>Umeo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. m.,</text:span> Umerus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Humeo, Humerus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">U</text:span>mmĭdius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Umquam</text:span> <text:line-break/>(unquam), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">då</text:span> u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till betydelsen förhåller sig till</text:span> quisquam, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som</text:span> quum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(när) till</text:span> qui, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är det till formen förmodligen uppkommet af</text:span> quumquam, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med öfwergångsformen</text:span> vumquam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr umbr.</text:span> pum, pumpe = quum, quumque, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Fabretti,</text:span> Glossarium Italicum), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liksom</text:span> ubi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bewisligen är uppkommet af</text:span> quobi; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> ubi, unde; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> usquam]: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Någonsin:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i direct negativa satser:</text:span> utinam ne u., Enn.; nemo u. sine magna spe immortalitatis morti sese obtulit, C.; neque u. præripio pulpamentum, neque prævorto poculum, Pt.; nulla u. civitas bonis exemplis ditior, L.; - nec, si resurgat centimanus Gyas, divellet u. (me a te), Hor.; nulla u. tam exigua manus tantas opes prostravit, N.; non u., Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i frågor eller hypothetiska satser af nekande syftning:</text:span> en unquam fando auditum est?, L.; ulla si juris tibi pejerati poena, Barine, nocuisset u., crederem; caveant, ne - u. -; quæ poterunt u. satis expurgare cicutæ, ni melius dormire putem, quam scribere versus?, Hor.; egregius, si u. regnandam acceperit Albam, Vg.; si mihi filius u. erit -, Ter.; si u. in dicendo fuimus aliquid, -, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i affirmativa bisatser:</text:span> jussit Timarchidem æstimare argentum, quo modo qui u. tenuissime æstimavit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så lågt någonsin ngn gjort),</text:span> C.; portis alii bipatentibus astant, milia quot magnis u. venere Mycenis, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Numquam</text:span> <text:line-break/>(nunquam), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> ne = non <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> unquam; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> ne): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aldrig; aldrig någonsin;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> stundom i försäkringar blott = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">icke, bestämdt icke:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> philosophari n. didici neque scio; egone eam ducam domum, quæ mihi n. hoc dicat: eme, vir, lanam, unde pallium tibi conficiatur! Hoc n. verbum ex uxore audias; absque te esset, hodie n. ad solis occasum viverem, Pt.; n. se Scipio inferioris ordinis amicis anteposuit, C.; n. ante hoc tempus exercitus populi Rom. Galliæ provinciæ finibus egressus est, Cs.; fatis n. concessa moveri Camerina; n. omnes hodie moriemur inulti, Vg.; consilio patres firmabat auctor n. alias dato, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt märkas:</text:span><text:line-break/>a.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nonnumquam</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nonnumquam</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stundom, mången gång, wid åtskilliga tillfällen:</text:span></text:span> n. interdiu, sæpius noctu, Cs.; n. mortem sibi consciscere aliquis debet, alius in eadem causa non debet, C.<text:line-break/>b. nunquam - non = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alltid:</text:span></text:span> dicere n. est non ineptum, nisi quum est necessarium, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Unā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unus 6. c.<text:line-break/>Unanim . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Animus.<text:line-break/>Uncia, -cialis, -ciarius, -ciatim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unus.<text:line-break/>Uncin . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Uncus.<text:line-break/>Unciola <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Uncia, Unus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Unco,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ryta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om björnen:</text:span> Auct. carm. Philom.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Unct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ungo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uncus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krokig, krökt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som en klo l. hake), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">böjd:</text:span></text:span> vomis; u-o non alligat ancora morsu, Vg.; torquis, Ppt.; hamus, Ov.; vomer aratri, Lucr.; unguis, Lucr., Pn.; scrutatur u-is manibus oculos Oedipus, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uncus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hake; hulling; krampa:</text:span></text:span> infixus fugitivo u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stång med hake),</text:span> C.; u. ferreus, Cato; ferreis u-is naves subtrahebat Archimedes, L.; - fixus mento decussus u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en fisk, i bild),</text:span> Ppt.; clavi trabales, cunei, u., plumbum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom attribut för</text:span> Necessitas), Hor.; Sejanus (ɔ: cadaver) ducitur u-o, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uncīnus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hake:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uncīnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försedd med hakar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hullingar:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ăduncus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inåt böjd, krökt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> reduncus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bakåt l. uppåt böjd):</text:span> cornua aliis a-a, aliis redunca, Pn.; unguis; serrula, C.; nasus, Ter.; baculum, L.; aratrum, Ov.; rostrum, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ăduncĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krokighet:</text:span></text:span> rostri, C., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnunco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med hake gripa, sätta hake i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gripa, fasthålla:</text:span></text:span> lana rubis i-ta, Col.; unguibus aliquid, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ŏbuncus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjd åt, mot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">inåt:</text:span></text:span> rostrum, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕduncus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bakåt böjd, uppåt böjd:</text:span></text:span> rostrum, Ov.; cornua, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Unda,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Watten</text:span></text:span> (ὕδωρ); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wätska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> ter socios purā circumtulit u-ā, Vg.; u. nivalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(snöwatten),</text:span> Mt.; faciunt justos ignis et u. viros <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äkta män);</text:span> deus - cælo terras et terris abscidit u-as et liquidum spisso secrevit ab āere cælum; fluit u. capillis; cælestes u-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(regnwatten);</text:span> expers u-æque <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dryck)</text:span> cibique; vina fugit gaudetque meris abstemius u-is, Ov.; Tantalus hauriat u-as, Sen.; sanguinis, Sil.; croci, Mt. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåg, bölja,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> böljande watten l. wattenmassa:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> importunæ, Liv. Andr.; Europam Libyamve rapax ubi dividit u.; u-æ saxifragæ, Enn.; non vidisse u-as me majores censeo, Pt.; concursantes, Acc.; u-æ et litora, C.; u. dehiscens terram inter fluctus <text:soft-page-break/>aperit; Trinacria lentandus remus in u-a, Vg.; u. supervĕnit u-am, Hor.; u. impellitur u-ā; æquoreæ; rapaces; vaga u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(collectivt);</text:span> rauca; insonuit u. æquoris, Ov.; non vox et mutui hortatus juvabant adversante u-a, T.; haud ullas portabis opes Acheruntis ad u-as: nudus ad infernas, stulte, vehēre rates, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåg, bölja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af luft, rök, menniskoskaror o. s. w.:</text:span> āeriæ, Lucr.; comitiorum, C.; u-am fumus agit; salutantum, Vg.; magnis curarum fluctuat u-is, Catl.; adversis rerum immersabilis u-is (Ulixes), Hor.; nobis properantibus obstat u. prior, magno populus premit agmine lumbos, qui sequitur, Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">List</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en byggnad (jfr</text:span> cyma, cymatium): Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĭsŏnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I böljorna brusande; i brusande böljor boende:</text:span></text:span> u-os prece adire deos, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bölja; gå i wågor; häfwa wågor; swalla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg., om watten:</text:span> salum, Enn.; u-anti in freto, Acc.; cruor; aēna u-antia flammis, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om andra subject:</text:span> ruptis fornacibus Aetna; u-antes habenæ, lora, Vg.; regio equis, Vfl.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Komma att bölja, gå i wågor:</text:span></text:span> campos sanguine u-at, St.; conchæ u-tæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wattrade, wågformiga),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böljande, swallande:</text:span></text:span> mare, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I wågor, wågformigt:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böljande, swallande, brusande:</text:span></text:span> æquor; Plemmyrium, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böljande:</text:span></text:span> toga, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ăbundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerflödande; rikligt flödande:</text:span></text:span> lavacra, Gell. I. 2. 2 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Hertz).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ăbunde</text:span>,<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst. def.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">nom.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerflöd; rikligt förråd; öfwernog:</text:span></text:span> terrorum et fraudis a. est, Vg.; a. gloriæ adeptus, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till öfwerflöd; öfwernog, i rikt mått:</text:span></text:span> a. satisfactum est rei; a. potiri, C.; a. magna præsidia; nobis a. parentes sunt, Sa.; gratia, fama, valetudo contingit a., Hor.; a. favere alicui, Ov.; similis; disertus; bene; elatus spiritus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ăbundo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flöda rikligt, flöda öfwer, öfwerswämma:</text:span></text:span> flumen; fons, Lucr.; rursus a-bat aqua, Vg.; Nilus a-at aquā, Tib.; fons in omnem partem, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flöda af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hafwa öfwerflöd, wara rik på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (full af) ngt:</text:span> ripas superat atque a-at pectus lætitiā, Pt.; amore a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(”wara kär upp öfwer öronen”);</text:span> divitiis, Ter.; equitatu, Cs.; earum rerum, quibus a-amus, exportatio et earum, quibus egemus, invectio; semper boni assiduique domini - villa tota locuples est: a-at porco, hædo, agno, gallina, lacte, caseo, melle; te jam annum audientem Cratippum idque Athenis oportet a-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(flöda af</text:span> ɔ: imbutum esse) præceptis <text:soft-page-break/>institutisque philosophiæ, C.; exercitus omni genere copiarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förråd)</text:span> a-bat, N.; apibus fetis atque examine multo, Vg.; caligine, Ov.; Seneca dulcibus a-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(flödar af)</text:span> vitiis, Qu.; virtutibus, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara rik:</text:span></text:span> amici absentes adsunt et egentes a-ant; cum a-re debeam, cogor mutuari, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerskrida måttan; göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gå till öfwerdrift:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> neu desis operæ neve immoderatus a-es, Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flöda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">finnas i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till öfwerflöd:</text:span></text:span> opera et præmia vitæ, Pn. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara öfwerflödig:</text:span></text:span> Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ăbundans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerflödande, rikligt flödande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">strömmande, wattenrik:</text:span></text:span> amnis a-simus, C.; fluvius, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som flödar af ngt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rik på, rikt utrustad med</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliqua re</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sällan</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicujus rei</text:span>): fortunis, Acc.; vita bonis; homo a. bellicis laudibus (Pompejus); Græci non solum ingenio et doctrina, sed etiam otio a-es; consilio, doctrinā, sapientiā a-ior, C.; via copiosa omniumque rerum a., N.; quam dives pecoris, nivei quam lactis a., Vg.; opibus; amicis, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rik,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i fråga om förmögenhetswilkor:</text:span> supellex non illa quidem luxoriosi hominis, sed tamen a-is; hæc utrum a-is an egentis signa sunt?, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om talare l. framställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rik</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">syn.</text:span> copiosus); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">riklig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i mindre god mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">allt för rik, öfwerlastad:</text:span></text:span> non erat a., hon inops tamen, C.; a-ior atque ultra quam oportet fusa materia; supra necessitatem a. oratio; Asiane a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utswäfwande; öfwerlastad),</text:span> Attice pressus; ex a-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till öfwerlopps)</text:span> addere aliquid, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ăbundanter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikligt:</text:span></text:span> crescere, Pn.; alere, Col. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om talare och deras framställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikt, fylligt, omständligt, utförligt:</text:span></text:span> loqui, dicere copiose et a.; disputare a-ius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> angustius); id satis a. demonstratum est, C.; a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i ett öfwerlastadt språk; mots.</text:span> presse) dicere, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ăbundantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flödande, strömmande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikligt förråd, öfwerflöd på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> in omnium rerum a-a vivere; a. amoris, otii; omnium rerum, quas natura desiderat, a. et copia, C.; pecuniæ summa a., T.; salis, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikedom, öfwerflöd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i yttre och inre mening:</text:span> ex juvenili a-a coërcere (oratorem), Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ăbundātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flödande, öfwerflödande:</text:span></text:span> fossæ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Exundo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppwälla, framwälla; bölja, flöda, swalla upp, fram, öfwer:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg., om materiella subject i allm.:</text:span> vapor, Sen.; fons, Pn.; tura balsamaque - vicini solis radiis expressa atque liquentia - vi tempestatum in adversa litora e-ant, T. Germ. 45. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> dolor, Sen.; ex multa eruditione et rerum scientia e-at et exuberat illa admirabilis eloquentia, T.; ingenii fons, Juv.; Cicero non pluvias aquas colligit, sed vivo gurgite e-at, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Exundātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerswämning:</text:span></text:span> fluminum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnundo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerswämma, swalla öfwer,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> eg. och oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>: fluvius, L.; densi i-ant Trōes, Vg.; Nilus, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: aqua terras, C.; Tiberis agros i-vit; agri i-ti; vestro sanguine i-bitur Enna, L.; i-ant sanguine <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(komma att öfwerswämma af)</text:span> fossas, Vg.; invidiā, vino i-tus, Petr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnundātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerswämning:</text:span></text:span> anno permanserat i., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕdundo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bölja, flöda, swalla tillbaka, upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer sina bräddar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwerswämma:</text:span></text:span> lacus Albanus; mare æquabiliter undique conglobatur neque r-at unquam neque effunditur; pituita aut bilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i menniskokroppen);</text:span> sanguine locus, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass. part.</text:span>: aquæ r-tæ,, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälla, falla tillbaka på</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">in aliquem</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">härröra:</text:span></text:span> erumpunt sæpe vitia amicorum, quorum in amicos r-et infamia; invidia mihi in posterum r-bit; hinc illæ extraordinariæ pecuniæ r-arunt, C.; ad rem, Qu. XII. 2. 19. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gå till öfwerdrift, finnas till öfwermått; wara till öfwerlopps, wara öfwerflödig:</text:span></text:span> ornatus orationis neque defuit in Antonio neque in Crasso r-vit; in definitione neque abesse quidquam debet neque r-re, C.; r-ante multitudine (- <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkmängden war för stor),</text:span> T.; orator; epitheton; literæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bokstäfwer),</text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hafwa till öfwerlopps</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">för mycket:</text:span></text:span> digito uno, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara öfrig, blifwa öfwer:</text:span></text:span> ex meo tenui vectigali detractis sumptibus aliquid etiam r-bit, C.<text:line-break/>e. (= abundo) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flöda af, wara rik på, full af:</text:span></text:span> oratio r-vit hilaritate et joco; victoria luctu acerbissimo; ornamentis oratio, C.; clientelis, T.<text:line-break/>f. = exundo: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flöda upp, strömma fram:</text:span></text:span> ex rerum cognitione oratio, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕdundans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerswallande, öfwerflödande;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om talare och framställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwerlastad:</text:span></text:span> verba; oratores parum pressi et nimis r-es, C.; tumidior et r.; inane et r., Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕdundanter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Till öfwerflöd, öfwermått:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕdundantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerswallning, öfwerswämning:</text:span></text:span> aĕris, Vitr.; illa pro Roscio juvenilis r. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">allt för starkt ordflöde),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕdundātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppswallning, öfwerswämning:</text:span></text:span> stomachi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppstigning),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undĕ,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">partikel:</text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af pronominal rot, liksom</text:span> inde <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> is), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förmodligen, såsom</text:span> necunde <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> sicunde <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wisa, af</text:span> quonde <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med öfwergångsform</text:span> vonde, vunde; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> ubi, unquam): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwarifrån, hwadan; hwaraf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= från hwilket l. hwilken; af hwilken l. hwilket i ablativa och partitiva uttryck, men icke uttryckande agenten):</text:span> I. <text:span text:style-name="T2">interrogativ</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">partikel:</text:span> u. eam esse ajunt?; u. exit hæc? - u. nisi domo?, Pt.; u. hæc flamma oritur?, Enn.; u. is?; u. est puer?, Ter.; u. dejecti sunt Galli?; non recordor, u. ceciderim, C.; u. aut quo Catius?; u. quo veni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwadan och hwart har jag kommit?);</text:span> u. mihi lapidem?, Hor.; u. domo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwarifrån kommer du</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwar är ditt hem l. födelseort?),</text:span> Hor., Ppt., Vg.; hic canit errantem lunam solisque labores, u. hominum genus et pecudes, Vg.; u. quove sit armento, veri quasi nescia, quærit; neque erat cognoscere promptum, u. (audita sit vox), sed audita est, Ov.; qualis et u. genus, qui sint mihi, Tulle, penates, quæris pro nostra <text:soft-page-break/>semper amicitia, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">relativ</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">partikel l. conjunction:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwarifrån; hwaraf,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i uttryck så wäl för kommande l. afstånd från ett ställe, som för ursprung, härkomst l. för tagande, fående, hörande, lärande af ngn:</text:span> est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medel),</text:span> u. accipiam te apud me comiter; redigam te eodem, u. orta es, Pt.; - u. oritur imber sonitu sævo et spiritu; (Apollo) u. sibi populi et reges consilium expetunt, Enn.; eccos, u. certiscent!, Pac.; e prædonibus, u. emerat, audivit, eam civem esse, Ter.; restitui, u. dejectus est; orator melius dicet hæc, quam ipse ille, u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af hwilken)</text:span> ea cognovit; apud societates, u. erat attributa pecunia; is, u. petitur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= swaranden),</text:span> C.; naves revertebantur, u. profectæ erant; Latovicos in fines suos, u. erant profecti, reverti jussit, Cs.; non quæsivit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(något ställe),</text:span> ubi ipse tuto viveret, sed u. præsidio posset esse civibus suis; rex Themistocli dedit Myunta, u. haberet obsonium, N.; Hæmus, u. vocalem temere insecutæ Orphea silvæ; hic u. vitam sumeret nescius, pacem duello miscuit, Hor.; freta Sicaniæ petamus, u. huc advecti; Atys, genus u. Atii duxere Latini, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i orsaksförhållanden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwaraf, hwarpå, hwarför, i följd hwaraf:</text:span></text:span> est res quædam, u. tu pergrande lucrum facias, Pt.; u. quis non invidit florem liberûm meûm, Acc. ap. C. Tusc. Disp. III. 20; multos, qui, u. efferrentur, non reliquissent, suo sumptu extulit Cimon, N.; quærere, u. se tueri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(underhålla)</text:span> possit, L.; iambus pes citus, u. etiam trimetris accrescere jussit nomen iambeis, senos quum redderet ictus, Hor.; u. etiam (= itaque) templo Triviæ lucisque sacratis cornipedes arcentur equi, Vg.; guttas exceptas tellus animavit in angues: u. frequens illa est infestaque terra colubris, Ov.; u. illi ira violentior et materia criminandi, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På hwilken sida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> ab): eventus belli velut æquus judex, u. jus stabat, ei <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åt den, på hwilkens sida rätten war)</text:span> victoriam dedit, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĕcumque</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Undĕcunque) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undeunde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Conj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Från hwilket håll som helst som</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">än; från hwilket håll som helst:</text:span></text:span> fluctus u. moti sunt, verberant omnia, Sen.; numos u. u. extricare, Hor.; u. causa fluxit, ibi culpa est, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĕlĭbet</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwar som helst ifrån:</text:span></text:span> istud facile fuit u. invenire, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĕquāque</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerallt ifrån</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> usquequaque):. L. XXXVI. 44 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Mdvg:</text:span> classes quoque undique).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĭque</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Från alla håll, allestädes ifrån:</text:span></text:span> ad confligendum venientibus u. Poenis, Lucr.; u. consectari voluptates; colligentem u. repleri justa juris scientia, C.; coëmptis u. nobilis libris Panæti, Hor.; u. convenere, Vg.; circumveniri; impetus fit, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ălĭcunde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Någorstädes ifrån, från (af) någon</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">något:</text:span></text:span> a. exorare mutuum, Pt.: venire, Ter.; audire; procul a. quærere; præcipitare; quod motum affert alicui quodque ipsum agitatur a., quando finem habet motus, vivendi finem habeat, necesse est, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Undecentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och alla räkneord, som börja med</text:span> Unde . . ., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unus.<text:line-break/>Undique <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unde.<text:line-break/>Undisonus, Undo, -dosus, -dulatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unda.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ūnĕdo,</text:span> ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags buske och deß bär (mjölonris?):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">U</text:span>nelli, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folkslag.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Unetvices . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(unguo), unxi, unctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörja:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörja, bestryka:</text:span></text:span> labitur, natat u-ta carina, Enn., Vg.; globos melle, Varr.; tela <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> arma cruoribus, Vg., Hor.; axes, Ce. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörja, salfwa, olja, insmörja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en menniskas kropp för prydnads och wällukts skull l. för att göra den smidig wid kroppsrörelser:</text:span> servi, qui tergunt, u-unt, verrunt; unguento u-i; u-tus est, accubuit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till bords),</text:span> C.; capilli u-ti; u-i olivo; supra vires <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillgångar)</text:span> et vestiri et u-i; ter u-ti transnanto Tiberim, somno quibus est opus alto, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett lik före bränningen:</text:span> Tarquini corpus bona femina lavit et unxit, Enn. Ann. 156 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Vahl.);</text:span> Hectora Iliæ unxere matres, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mat: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörja, såsa:</text:span></text:span> caules oleo; oluscula lardo, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smord, fettig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (smutsig):</text:span> manibus u-is tractare calicem, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smord, oljad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för kroppsöfningar:</text:span> psallimus et luctamur Achivis doctior u-is, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om rätter; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">läcker, riklig:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något fett, läckert:</text:span></text:span> ponere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(servera)</text:span> u-um; ubi quid melius contingit et u-ius, (vos divites solos bene vivere ajo), Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälmående</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som har råd att lefwa godt och gör det); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rik:</text:span></text:span> ita defendebat palæstritas, ut ab iis ipse u-ior decederet <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smord</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mutad),</text:span> C.; accedes siccus ad u-um, Hor.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställning</text:span> (ɔ: copiosa et nitida; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mots.</text:span> exilis et horrida): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sirlig och bred; putsad och fyllig:</text:span></text:span> jam erat u-ior consuetudo loquendi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörjande, oljande, oljning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för palæstran):</text:span> simulac philosophus garrire coepit, omnes eum in media disputatione u-is causa relinquunt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ständigt salfwa; bruka att smörja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">olja sig:</text:span></text:span> unguento, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctiuscŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något fetare:</text:span></text:span> pulmentum, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insmörjare, salfware (parfyrmör)</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slaf, som insmorde hår l. kropp</text:span> (aliptes): ducitur familia tota, vestiplica, u., auri custos, flabelliferæ, sandaligerulæ (meretricis), Pt. Trin. 251 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ritschl;</text:span> bonus, C., Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctōrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rum i badhus, der man insmörjes och skrapas, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insmörjningsrum:</text:span></text:span> Pn. ep. V. 6. 25 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Marquardt</text:span> V. 1. 296).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något litet insmord:</text:span></text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">läcker rätt:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörjelse, inoljning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett lik:</text:span> C. de Legg. II. 60.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unctus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insmörjning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguēdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Salfwa:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörja, fett:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Vg., Ps.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fet, fettig:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wälluktande smörjelse, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Salfwa, wällukt, parfym</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (brukade af Romarne till att insmörja kropp, kläder, hår, i badet, wid likbegängelser m. m.; jfr Marquardt,</text:span> II. 2. 366): olere u-a; omnium u-ûm odos præ tuo nautea est, Pt.; u-is minus delectamur acerrima suavitate conditis, quam his moderatis; perfricare caput u-is; u-is nitere, affluere, oblĭtus, C.; huc vinum et u-a et nimium breves flores amoenæ ferre jube rosæ; funde capacibus u-a de conchis, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr de olika slagen af</text:span> u., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom</text:span> nardus, malobathron, costum Achæmenium (Persici apparatus), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och ordet</text:span> odores, Pn. XIII. 8-17; afferet hæc u-a mihi sertisque sepulcrum ornabit custos ad mea busta sedens, Ppt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguentārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörjelse-, parfym-,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till wällukter hörande:</text:span> taberna, Varr., Su.; vas, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguentārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Parfymhandlare, salfhandlare:</text:span></text:span> Ter., C., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguentāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Salfhandlerska:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Parfymerares konst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">yrke:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguentārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Salfpenningar,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> titel, hwarunder en romersk proconsul utpressat penningar af provincialer:</text:span> accepit sestertia X milia, nomine u-i, qui titulus a vita hominis compti semper et pumicati non abhorrebat, Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguento</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörja, insmörja, parfymera:</text:span></text:span> cincinni u-ti, Pt.: maritus u-tus, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Exungo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">smörja bort</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Anwända på smörjelser, parfymer:</text:span></text:span> quid factumst eo (ære)? - Comessum, e-tum, expotum, elutum in balineis, Pt. Trin. 406 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Rud. 580).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnungo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insmörja, smörja:</text:span></text:span> oculos, Varr.; non possis oculos quantum contendere Lynceus, non tamen idcirco contemnis lippus inungi, Hor.; conchis i-ta, Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnunctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insmörjning, besmörjning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnungĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insmörja:</text:span></text:span> capillum oleo, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĕrĭnungo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwersmörja:</text:span></text:span> aliquid re, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭpĕrĭnungo</text:span>, 3.: id.: Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĕrungo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörja helt öfwer, fullständigt:</text:span></text:span> corpora oleo, C.; Assyria nardo p-ti potamus; poēmata plaustris vexit Thespis, quæ canerent agerentque p-ti fæcibus ora, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĕrunctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smörjning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Præungo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förut smörja:</text:span></text:span> Cæl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕunctor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insmörjare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af sjuke:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭpĕrungo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwersmörja:</text:span></text:span> collyrio, Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Unguedo, Unguen, Unguent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ungo. <text:line-break/>Unguiculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unguis.<text:line-break/>Unguinosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unguen, Ungo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Unguis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nagel, klo, klöf, ram:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nagel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på menniskors fingrar och tår:</text:span> u-em latum ex loco discedere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en nagels bredd),</text:span> Pt.; ab imis u-bus ad summum verticem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från tårna</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fotabjellet till hjessan);</text:span> a recta conscientia u-em transversum non oportet discedere, C.; u-es exprimere (ære); u-es purgare cultello; sectis u-bus; in versu faciendo sæpe caput scabere - vivos et rodere u-es; vos carmen reprehendite, quod non multa et dies et multa litura coërcuit atque præsectum deciens non castigavit ad u-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter nageln - bild, hemtad från ett plastiskt konstwerk, som glattas och filas med nageln; jfr</text:span> Sat. I. 5. 32); a tenero u-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från späda åren, från barnsben),</text:span> Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf i allm.:</text:span> in u-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ad u-em = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">noggrannt, punktligt</text:span></text:span> (ad amussim): in u-em quadrare, Vg. G. II. 277; ad u-em dolare materiam, Col.; mordere u-es, Ppt.; u-bus ire in vultus alicujus, Ov., - carmina molli nunc demum numero fluere, ut per lēve severos effundat junctura u-es (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så att fogorna ej märkas; jfr</text:span> Hor.), Ps.; (per conventus et cuncta per oppida curvis u-bus ire parat numos raptura Celæno, Juv.); medium ostendere u-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= trotsa),</text:span> Juv. X. 153.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klo, klöf, ram</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos djur:</text:span> leonis, Hor., Vg.; corvi, Ov.; simiæ; canum; bovis, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hake, krampa:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mußla:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unguĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nagel:</text:span></text:span> usque ab u-is, Pt.; a teneris u-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från späda åren),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ungŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klo; hof; klöf:</text:span></text:span> injicere alicui u-as, Pt.; sol equis iter repressit u-is volantibus; summo sonitu quatit u. terram, Enn.; quadrupedante putrem sonitu quatit u. campum, Vg.; toto corpore atque omnibus u-is (ɔ: membris, viribus), C.; currum rapit u., Hor.; solida (equi), Pn.; suis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sexungŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sexnagladt</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">girigt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fruntimmer:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ring:</text:span></text:span> alicui detrahere u-um, Pac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Unguo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ungo.<text:line-break/>Unice <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unicus, Unus. <text:line-break/>Unicolor, Unicornis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Color, Cornu. <text:line-break/>Unicus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unus.<text:line-break/>Uniform . . ., Unigena, Unimanus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Forma, Geno, Mănus.<text:line-break/>Unio, Unitas, -ter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unus.<text:line-break/>Univers . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Verto.<text:line-break/>Univira <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vir.<text:line-break/>Uniusmodi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Unus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Modus.<text:line-break/>Unoculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Oculus. <text:line-break/>Unquam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Umquam.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ūnus,</text:span> a, um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.</text:span> <text:line-break/>oinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>oenus; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Curtius, Griech. Etymol.</text:span> 297-8), <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> unīus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(poet. </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stundom</text:span> unĭus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.</text:span> uni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> unæ): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i numerisk mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i motsats till flere, en af ett bestämdt l. obestämdt antal:</text:span> filiam unam habui, Pt.; universi in unum impetum fecerunt, N.; in amicitia u. efficitur e pluribus; parturire unum pro pluribus; unæ literæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett bref);</text:span> unis vestimentis lautus es, C.; u. et alter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en eller twå),</text:span> C., Hor.; tu præter omnes, une de capillatis, Catl. XXXVII. 17; Orgetorigis filia atque u. ex filiis captus est, Cs.; qui deperiit minor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(yngre)</text:span> uno mense vel anno, inter quos referendus erit? - caudæque pilos ut equinæ paulatim vello et demo unum demo et item unum; unĭus assis pretio, Hor.; uno plus Romanorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en Romare mera)</text:span> cecidit in proelio, L.; crimine ab uno disce omnes; satis ună superque vidimus excidia et captæ superavimus ubi, Vg.; tota domus redā componitur unā, Juv.; eam esse condicionem imperandi, ut non aliter ratio constet, nisi uni reddatur; dispersas per urbem cohortes una in castra conduxit (Sejanus); non alia est res Romana, quam si u. imperitet; tres legiones in unam miscere, T.; superesse videt de tot modo milibus unam; dolor unīus pervenit ad omnes; ex omnibus unum elige, dum ne sit in omnibus u. (Met. X. 317), Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (den ene) i motsats till den andre, den tredje o. s. w.:</text:span> rationem habetis, quo modo unum amiserit. Postquam belligerant autem Aetoli cum Aleis, ut fit in bello, capitur alter filius, Pt.; has causas inveniebam duas: unam, quod -. Altera est hæc - (de Or. I. §. 123); meæ totius orationis - tres sunt rationes, una conciliandorum hominum, altera docendorum, tertia concitandorum, C.; duo erant itinera, unum per Sequanos, alterum per provinciam, Cs.; est genus unum stultitiæ nihilum metuenda timentis, - alterum et huic varum et nihilo sapientius ignes per medios fluviosque ruentis, Hor.; unus - alter, Ov. Met. III. 165.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med starkare eftertryck: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En enda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blott en</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ensam; ofta, då det står såsom prædicat, att återgifwa med adverbia: endast, blott):</text:span> u. homo nobis cunctando restituit rem, Enn.; uni amatori morem gerere, Pt.; id unum defit, Acc.; possum ex hac una civitate pæne innumerabiles duces præstantissimos proferre; ex uno oppido sōlo; unam solam scitote esse civitatem Mamertinam, quæ publice legatos, qui Verrem laudarent, miserit, C.; quid olant, nescias, nisi id unum, male ut olere intelligas, Pt.; hoc unum vos oro, Ter.; una salus victis nullam sperare salutem; Pallasne exurere classem potuit unius ob noxam et furias Ajacis Oīlei?, Vg.; deprecor hoc unum, quod vero nomine poena, non honor est; Inachus u. abest, Ov.; in lapide hoc uni nupta fuisse legar; unĭus hic quondam servus amoris erat, Ppt.; una æstate duobus bellis confectis; dicit, unum se esse ex omni civitate Hæduorum, qui adduci non potuerit, ut juraret aut liberos suos obsides daret, Cs.; hæc sacra Romulus una peregrina suscepit; u. Appius legum expers, L.; id unum suffugium erat, T.; una de multis face nuptiali digna; nil admirari prope res est una, Numici, solaque, quæ possit facere et servare beatum, Hor.; - hoc unum (adjungam), quod nemo eat inficias, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(en) Enskild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofta tillsammans med pron. indefinita):</text:span> confugiebant ad unum alqm potentem virum; non una aliqua in re separatim elaboraverunt, sed omnia comprehenderunt; nulla una re magis commendatur orator; si tu solus aut unus quivis impetum <text:soft-page-break/>fecisset -; nemo de nobis unus excellat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(må utmärka sig framför andre),</text:span> C.; atque utinam primis animam me ponere cunis jussisset quævis de tribus una soror, Ppt.; populus superamur ab uno, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En, blott en,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> allt igenom utan mångfald l. afbrott:</text:span> nox est perpetua una dormienda, Catl.; una est eloquentia, quascunque in oras disputationis delata est; omnis doctrina artium ingenuarum uno societatis vinculo continetur, C.; unum erat omnia volnus, Ov.; unum est reip. corpus et unius animo regendum, T. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">en och samme</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för flere, i mångfald; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">samme,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i l. utan förening med</text:span> idem: ætas ambobus quasi una erat, Pt.; ager una <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enformigt)</text:span> specie, Sa.; leges una eademque voce cum omnibus loquuntur; unis moribus vivere; ne in uno quidem unus animus, C.; in unis ædibus vivere, Ter.; fronte non una minax, Sen.; uno tempore et ad silvas et in flumine hostes esse videbantur, Cs.; u. erat toto naturæ voltus in orbe; facies non omnibus una, non diversa tamen, quales decet esse sororum, Ov.; vox omnibus una, Vg.; sit quidvis, simplex duntaxat et unum; una salus ambobus erit; qui variare cupit rem prodigialiter unam, delphinum silvis appingit, fluctibus aprum; nec pes neque caput uni redditur formæ, Hor. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ofta anwändes</text:span> unus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> a.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom en förstärkning till superlativer l. superlativiska uttryck = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">framför andra; utmärkt:</text:span></text:span> te unum ad dicendum ex omnibus maxime natum cognoveram; illo uno equite Romano utor familiarissime, C.; omnes mortales sciunt, te unum in terra vivere virtute et forma et factis invictissimum; quod genus illist unum pollens atque honoratissimum?; hero multimodis fidus u., Pt.; Miltiades u. omnium maxime florebat, N.; o felix una ante alias Priamēia virgo, Vg.; potes comis garrire libellos unus vivorum, Fundani; hortos egregiasque domos mercarier unus cum lucro noram, Hor.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bland många, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">en</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som andra, i l. utan förening med ett partitivt uttryck</text:span> (de multis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. d.):</text:span> in sermonibus, quamvis præpotens sit, efficit, ut u. de multis esse videatur; ut homunculus u. de multis probabilia conjecturā sequens; moderabor, ne ut quidam magister, sed quasi u. de togatorum numero - videar fortuito in sermonem vestrum incidisse; tanquam u. paterfamilias de his rebus disputo, C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> pro Roscio com. cap. 5); Aemilium circa ludum faber u. et ungues exprimet et molles imitabitur ære capillos, Hor.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med förswagad betydelse, närmande sig till en s. k. obestämd artikel: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En, någon:</text:span></text:span> Lacedæmonia mulier, Furiarum una; unus erit, quem tu tolles in cærula cæli (ap. Ov.), Enn.; video unam adulescentulam, Ter.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i serskilda uttryck, substantiviskt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. in unum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ett</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ställe):</text:span> comportare in unum, Hor.; in unum confundere, Ov.; fluvius rapide dilapsus in unum confluit, C.; in unum convocare, Sa.; urgentur in unum, Enn.<text:line-break/>b. ad unum omnes = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">alla utan undantag, till siste man:</text:span></text:span> cæsi ad unum omnes, L.; senatus surrexit ad unum, C.; Juppiter omnipotens, si nondum exosus ad unum omnes Trojanos, da flammam evadere classi, Vg.; noctu ad unum omnes, desperata salute, sese interficiunt, Cs.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnā</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På ett ställe, på samma ställe; på en gång; </text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillsammans; i sällskap, i sällskapet:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">abstract om rum = på </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ett</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ställe:</text:span> u. tres aquilas et signa cohortium locant, T.<text:line-break/>β. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På en gång, samtidigt:</text:span></text:span> sunt, qui censeant u. corpus et animam occidere, C. Tusc. I. §. 18; u. Eurusque Notusque ruunt -; omnis et u. dilapsus calor, Vg.; carpitque et carpitur u., Ov. <text:line-break/>γ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillsammans, på en gång, i sällskap, i sällskapet, tillika:</text:span></text:span> u. hic et Palæstrio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i complott)</text:span> me habent venalem, Pt.; memini eum in hemicyclio sedentem, quum et ego essem u. et pauci admodum familiarium, C.; u. in convivio erat adolescentulus Rhodius, Ter.; u. nobis occidendum est; u. nobiscum, Sa.; flumen stirpes raptas et pecus et domos volvit u. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med sig);</text:span> ludos spectavit u. (cum Horatio Mæcenas); u. coenare; u. cum scriptore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besjungare)</text:span> meo capsa porrectus apertā, Hor.; cum quibus erat quomque una, iis se dedere, eorum studiis obsequi, Ter.; genitor lugubris et u. mater adest; puer Icarus u. stabat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sin faders sällskap),</text:span> Ov.; u. undique circum fundimur; venatum Aeneas unaque miserrima Dido in nemus ire parant; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>: Pallas huic filius u.; u. omnis - senatus tura dabant, Vg.<text:line-break/>δ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillika,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> der blott om twenne subject samma handling utsäges l. twärtom:</text:span> grandes rhombi patinæque grande ferunt u. cum damno dedecus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ullus</text:span> (= un-lus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Demin.</text:span>), a, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen., dat.</text:span>: ullīus, ulli (<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> ulli, Pt. Truc. II. 2. 38 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Sp.;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span> ullæ, Lucr.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om betydelsen jfr Ingstad,</text:span> de vi et usu pronominum quisquam et ullus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Någon</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> enda, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">någon,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwem det wara må, i samma anwändningar som</text:span> quisquam, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwilket</text:span> ullus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">motswarar såsom adjectivum och tillika isynnerhet i de former, i hwilka</text:span> q. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ej brukas, ersätter, således:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efter negation</text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dock ej efter enkel negation i samma sats</text:span> (non, haud), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utom der större eftertryck det föranleder; serdeles ofta så hos</text:span> Ppt.]:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom hufwudord l. attribut:</text:span> ego filiolam unam habui, eam unam perdidi: virile secus nunquam u-um habui, Pt.; neque u-a officii præcepta firma tradi possunt, nisi ab iis, qui maxime honestatem propter se expetendam dicunt, C.; negat, se u-i iter per provinciam dare posse, Cs.; talibus viris non locus u. asper aut arduus erat; nobis familiaris nusquam ullus est, Sa.; homo sine u-a religione ac fide; sine u-a impensa publica, N.; nec deinde - aut Etrusci aut u-i alii accolæ ausi sunt arma movere, L.; in me tardus amor non u-as cogitat artes; haud u-as portabis opes Acheruntis ad undas, Ppt.; nec harum, quas colis, arborum te præter invisas cupressus u-a brevem dominum sequetur; domus hac nec purior u-a est nec magis his aliena malis, Hor.; serpens frigore pigra prius nec formidabilis u-i; domus est imis in vallibus antri abdita, sole carens, non u-i pervia vento, Ov.; infert se sæptus nebula - mirabile dictu - per medios miscetque viris neque cernitur u-i, Vg.; non illo melior quisquam nec amantior æqui vir fuit aut illa reverentior u-a deorum, Ov.; neque corpus u-um reperiri neque illi fuisse un - quam fratrem pernotuit, T.; nec amet quenquam nec ametur ab u-o, Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom prædicatsnomen (jfr</text:span> nullus 3.): neque valetudinis curatio neque navigatio sine hominum opera u-a esse potuisset, C.; sunt philosophi, qui negant Fortunam esse u-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(finnas),</text:span> sed temeritate <text:soft-page-break/>res omnis fieri autumant, Pacuv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i frågor och hypothetiska satser af nekande l. twiflande innehåll:</text:span> u-a si juris tibi pejerati poena, Barine, nocuisset unquam, crederem, Hor.; cur u-a foret me fortior? ire per ignes et gladios ausim; si pietas u-a est, ad me, Philomela, redito, Ov.; an sit mihi gratior u-a - tellus, quam hæc?: u-a putatis dona carere dolis Danaûm? sic notus Ulixes?, Vg.; est ergo res u-a tanti, ut viri boni et nomen et splendorem amittas?; si tempus est u-um hominis necandi -, C.; nescis, quem tua simplicitas risum vulgo moveat, quum - putet u-is esse aliquod numen templis aræque rubenti, Juv.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efter</text:span> quam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(än):</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> ultra quam u. spiritus durare possit -, Qu.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i affirmativa bisatser:</text:span> iniqui sunt decumanis omnes, qui u-am glebam agri habent, C.; anguis - dum amnes u-i rumpuntur fontibus, stagna colit, Vg. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> quisquam 2.); scelus intra se tacitum qui cogitat ullum, facti crimen habet, Juv.; quidquid bene dictum est ab u-o, meum est, Sen. de Ben.; tecumque nunc evolve femineos dolos, quod u-a conjux perfida atque impos sui amore cæco, quod novercales manus ausæ, Sen. Agam. 116.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nullus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> ne, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">icke, och</text:span> ullus), a, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> nullīus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(poet.</text:span> nullĭus; nulli, nullæ, Pt., Ter.; Ppt. I. 20. 35), <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span> nulli (nullæ, Cs. b. C. II. 7; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Neue, Lat. Form.</text:span> 1.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det sednare serskildt i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl. sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samt i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur. masc.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deremot sällan och poet. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">neutr.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">cas. obl. sing.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">aldrig i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">nom. sing. neutr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingen:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> scin tu n-um commeatum huc hinc esse a nobis?; ecqui tu potis reperire mulierem formā lepidā, cui pectus sapiat: nam cor non potest, quod n-a habet; nullan mulier istic habitat?; n. hoc puero pejor est; nullust, quando occepit, blandior, Pt.; n-o loco excluditur amicitia; n-a pars vitæ neque publicis neque privatis in rebus vacare potest officio; n-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ingen)</text:span> eget; huic rei qui studeant, n-i sunt; n-a beluarum, C.; n-o præsente; nullius stipendii homo, Sa.; n-a civitas fuit non (ɔ: omnis c.) suspecta nobis, Cs.; n. unquam; n-ius condicionis non habuit potestatem; n-i fides ejus defuit, N.; n. in orbe sinus Bajis prælucet amoenis; Græci præter laudem n-ius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter intet)</text:span> avari, Hor.; n-o veniente, vidente, cogente; n-aque mortales præter sua litora norant; vitium n-i per secula longa notatum; tibi nubere n-a nolet, Ov.; n-os fugere labores, Ppt.; jam jam n-a mora est, Vg.; hoc n-us nisi arte consequi potest; n-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genom ingenting)</text:span> magis deus separavit hominem a ceteris, quam dicendi facultate, Qu.; Augustus in n-ius suorum necem duravit, T.; n-um numen habes, si sit prudentia, (Fortuna), Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = af intet wärde, som ej gör skäl för sitt namn:</text:span> n-a est excusatio peccati, si <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det att man kanhända)</text:span> amici causa peccaveris; sine his studiis vitam n-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(icke för att wara lif)</text:span> putamus; eas leges n-as puto; hoc argumentum n-um est, C.; veniam dapibus n-isque paratibus orant, Ov.; Juppiter hoc non n-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(icke ouppmärksamma)</text:span> oculis observat, Vg.; avi n-i, Hor. (Sat. I. 6. 10).<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i stället för en adverbial negation</text:span> (non) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom prædicatsnomen (icke såsom attribut till annat prædicatsnomen):</text:span> ille, qui vocavit, n. venit, Pt.; n. sum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jag är förlorad),</text:span> Pt. Merc. 164; Ter., Ov.; resp. nulla est omnino; mortui n-i sunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äro ej till);</text:span> nolite arbitrari, me, quum a vobis discessero, nullum fore; Philotimus n. venit, C.; ea nobis n-a sunt (ɔ: desunt), Sa.; sum toto corpore n. ego <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= aftärd),</text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>Ppt. (I. 5. 28); testare, n-os esse, qua veheris, deos (Medea), Sen.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">analogt härmed är bruket af</text:span> n. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom attribut till isynnerhet modala abl., der wi i sw. bruka præp. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utan:</text:span></text:span> n-o negotio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swårighet, beswär),</text:span> C.; n-o periculo, ordine, Cs., Sa.; ex n-a conscientia culpæ, Sa.; volucres n-a dulcius arte canunt, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nullĭbi</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingenstädes:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nullusdum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ännu ingen:</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nonnullus</text:span> (non nullus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Någon</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (icke ringa); isynnerhet i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">någre, åtskillige;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">neutr.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">åtskilligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> nullus - non = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hwarje</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofwan under</text:span> nullus 1., Cs., N.): n-a injuria, Ter.; n-um solatium; sunt n-æ disciplinæ, quæ officium omne pervertant; n-i omissa imitatione majorum suum institutum sequuntur; complectar n-a, quæ minus fortasse videantur necessaria (Brut. §. 313), C.; ea res afferebat n-am etiam deformitatem; n-i ita interpretantur, amitti civitatem Romanam aliā ascitā, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uncia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Uns,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> 1/12 af ett aß</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af ett helt i allmänhet l. af en mark (koppar, jfr</text:span> as), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom wigt l. mynt; äfwen hyperboliskt = småsak, bagatell:</text:span> auri pondo u.; non u-am piscium cepi, Pt.; mortuus est Babullius. Cæsar, opinor, ex u-a (heres), C.; si de quincunce (5 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uns)</text:span> remota est u., quid superest? - Triens (1/3 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">as, 4 uns). -</text:span> Eu. - redit u. quid fit? Semis (½ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">as, 6 uns),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unciālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som utgör ett uns, en tolftedel; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tolftedels:</text:span></text:span> as; uva, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unciārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som utgör l. får </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">en tolftedel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af det hela:</text:span> fenus u-um = 1/12 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af capitalet l. 8 1/3 procent årligen,</text:span> L. VII. 16; XII tabulis sanctum, ne quis u-o fenore amplius exerceret, T. Ann. VI. 16 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Marquardt</text:span> III. 2. 49). <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unciātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Unswis, styfwerswis:</text:span></text:span> Ter. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Unciŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ett litet uns; blott ett uns:</text:span></text:span> u-am Proculejus habet, sed Gillo deuncem, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕunx</text:span>, cis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett aß minskadt med ett uns (ordet bildadt såsom</text:span> depilis, depygis) i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Elfwa uns, elfwa tolftedelar:</text:span></text:span> heres ex d-e, C.; d. jugeri, Col. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> unciola).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quincunx</text:span>, cis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fem uns, fem tolftedelar:</text:span></text:span> jugeri, Ps.; si de q-e remota est uncia, quid superest?, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Quincunx,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">femma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = figuren</text:span> V: in q-em directi ordines, C.; cippi obliquis ordinibus in q-em dispositi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(l.</text:span> -tis), Cs. b. G. VII. 73; sata in q-em, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quincunciālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som håller fem uns l. fem tolftedelar:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bildar en</text:span> quincunx: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Septunx</text:span>, cis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sju tolftedelar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett helt:</text:span> Col. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om win, som är blott till 5/12 blandadt med watten,</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tĕruncius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tre tolftedelar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett helt i allm.:</text:span> facere heredem ex t-o, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett litet mynt,</text:span> ¼ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">aß (öre):</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēcentum</text:span> (unus de centum), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: 100 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ett när, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nittionio.</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēcentēsĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nittionionde.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĕcim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Elfwa.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĕcies</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Elfwa gånger.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĕcĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. Num. Ord.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Elfte.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĕcĭmānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till elfte legionen:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēni</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. Num. Distr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Elfwa åt gången, elfwa på hwarje:</text:span></text:span> u-i decies anni, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēnōnāginta</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åttationio.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēnōnāgēsĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åttionionde.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undĕoctōginta</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjuttionio.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēquădrāginta</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trettionio.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēquădrāgēsĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trettionionde.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēquădrāgies</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trettionionde gången.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēquinquāginta</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fyrationio.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēquinquāgēsĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fyrationionde.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēsexāginta</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Femtionio.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēsexāgēsĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Femtionionde.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undētrīginta</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugunio.</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undētrīcēni</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. Num. Distr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugunio på hwarje.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undētrīcēsĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjugunionde.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēvīginti</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Num. Card.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nitton.</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēvīcēni</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. Num. Distr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nitton på hwarje.</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēvīcēsĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nittonde.</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undēvīcēsĭmānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till nittonde legionen:</text:span> Cs. (Al.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnetvīcēsĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. Num. Ord.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjuguförste:</text:span></text:span> T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnetvīcēsĭmānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till 21:sta legionen:</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(factiskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ende; en enda; blott en:</text:span></text:span> gnatus, Pt., Ter.; flet u-um mater, Catl.; hujus miseri senectus hoc u-o filio nititur; habebat filiam u-am; quæ tanta vitia fuerunt in u-o filio, cur is patri displiceret?, C.; satis beatus u-is Sabinis; marito u-o contenta, Hor.; fuit u-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enda barnet)</text:span> matri; u. anser erat (Philemoni et Baucidi), Ov.; u-a nata meo pulcerrima cura dolori, Ppt. II. 25. 1 (III. 20); Augustus nepotem u-um in insulam Planasiam projecit, T.; nobilitas sola est atque u-a virtus, Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sitt slag och till sin art </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Den ende, ensam; utomordentlig, owanlig, utmärkt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (syn.</text:span> singularis): ille est mihi u-o magis u-us (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mera dyrbar än en ende son),</text:span> Pt.; aut summa negligentia, aut u-a liberalitas; in Calatinum est illud elogium u-um; malitia, C.; Camillus fuit vir vere u. in utraque fortuna; dux; imperator, L.; volucris; puer, Ov.; spes, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utomordentligt, synnerligen, owanligt, utmärkt:</text:span></text:span> unum u., Pt.; diligere alqm, C.; deditus alicui, L.; securus, Hor.; u. amator fuit ejus rei, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förena:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ensam stor </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Perla (solitär):</text:span></text:span> in conchis invenitur, Pn.; Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enhet; öfwerensstämmelse:</text:span></text:span> Varr. l. l. VIII. 1; alvei; coloris; generis humani, Pn.; consensus et u., Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I förening, till ett:</text:span></text:span> conjugio - corporis atque animæ consistimus u. apti, Lucr. III. 844.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnīusmŏdi</text:span> = unius modi = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af enahanda art</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">slag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (se</text:span> modus): C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ū</text:span>nŏmammia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (mamma): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Amazonlandet (de enbröstades land), comisk ordbildning hos</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnusquisque</text:span> (unus quisque), unaquæque, unumquidque (<text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> unumquodque <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. indef.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> quisque): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwar och en, hwarje serskildt, hwar och en för sig:</text:span></text:span> neque omnia dicam et leviter unumquidque tangam, C.; decem elegit in unaquaque civitate (i. e. denos in singulis), quibus summum imperium potestatemque omnium rerum committeret, N.; suorum unumquemque nominans laudat, Sa. Cat. 21; plures sententiæ, quarum unaquæque desiderat probationem, Qu.; hæc disciplina eo pertinebat, ut sincera et integra uniuscujusque natura toto statim pectore arriperet artes honestas, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnusquisquis</text:span>, unumquidquid, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. indef.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> quisquis): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwar och en för sig:</text:span></text:span> u-d paulatim protrahit ætas in medium, Lucr. V. 1452 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Bernays);</text:span> u-d singillatim et placide percontari, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ūnusquīvis</text:span>, unaquævis, unumquidvis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. indef.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwar och en, hwem som helst:</text:span></text:span> Varro l. l. X. §. 15.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vocab . . ., Vocal . . ., Vocamen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vox.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ocātes, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folkslag</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vocat . . ., Vocif . . ., Vocito, Voco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vox.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏcōnius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏcontii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">alpfolk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vocula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vox.<text:line-break/>Vogesus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vosegus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vŏla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flata handen,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> det inre af handen; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fotblad:</text:span></text:span> nec v. nec vestigium exstat, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlæmum</text:span> pirum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som fyller en hand,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> enligt</text:span> Serv. ad Vg. Georg. II. 88; Mcb. II. 15.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏlaminia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gudomlighet:</text:span> Lucia V. Saliorum carminibus appellatur, Varro l. l. IX. 61.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏlăterræ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Etrurien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Vŏlăterrānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Volat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Volo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olcæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag mellan Pyrenæerne och Rhone.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olcălo, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Volcernes land.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olcānus <text:line-break/>(Vulcanus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Volcanus,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> eldens gud, identificerad med</text:span> Ἥφαιστος, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gudakonstnären, Aphrodites (Veneris) man: (enl. Varros sätt att etymologisera:</text:span> ab ignis vi ac violentia dictus V.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Tatius aras vovit - Soli, Lunæ, V-o et cet., Varr.; C. de Nat. Deorum III. §. 55; spolia hostium V-o vovere, L.; graves Cyclopum V. ardens urit officinas, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> Vg. Aen. VIII. 370 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff. (om förfärdigandet af Aeneae sköld).</text:span> <text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eld:</text:span></text:span> V-um in cornu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hornlykta)</text:span> inclusum gerere, Varr.; V-um ventus vegebat, Enn.; furit V. ad auras, Vg.; V-um pro igne volgo audimus, Qu. <text:line-break/>Volcānālis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Volcani:</text:span> flamen, Enn., Varr. <text:line-break/>Volcānal, ālis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Volcani tempel wid forum i Rom.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Volcānālia, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Volcani festdag:</text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/>Volcānius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Volcani, volcansk:</text:span> arma <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af V. förfärdigad),</text:span> C. poēt.; V-a munera (Solis), Ov.; V-a tellus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om Sicilien och de Lipariska öarne),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olcātius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Volemum = Volæmum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vola. <text:line-break/>Volens, Volent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Volo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏlĕro, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen i</text:span> gens Publilia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏlĕsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn:</text:span> L., Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Volgiŏlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wält, sladd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att jemna jord med:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Volg . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för ö:rigt</text:span> Volgus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Volgus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulgus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">masc.</text:span> i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> us [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Neue,</text:span> I. p. 679, 548; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">d. w. s. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc. sing.</text:span> vulgum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> vulgu (Varr.); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i annan form, än dessa twå, kan skilnad i genus ej betecknas, då ordet är</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span> tantum]: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allmänheten, hopen, massan,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i motsats till framstående klasser l. individer, så wäl i allmänhet utan bibetydelse: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">folket, mängden, menige man, menigheten,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som med föraktlig bibetydelse: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">pöbeln, pöbel:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> nonne Argivos fremere bellum et velle vim v-um vides?, Acc. ap. Non.; v. abhorret ab hac (ratione Epicuri), Lucr.; v-us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">nom. masc.,</text:span> Varro ap. Non.; ea, quæ scripserunt, a v-o intelligi voluerunt; non est consilium in v-o, non ratio, non discrimen, non intelligentia; voluntas v-i, C.; mercatores circumsistit v.; inscientia levitasque v-i; misericordia v-i, Cs.; rumores v-i; res in paucorum - dicionem concessit: ceteri omnes - v-us fuimus sine gratia, sine auctoritate, Sa.; gratiam ad v-um quæsierat, L. VI. 34; v. liberius loquebatur et tyrannum non ferendum dictitabat; mutata est v-i voluntas, N.; v. cunctum, malignum, infidum; odi profanum v. et arceo, Hor.; scinditur incertum studia in contraria v., Vg.; mihi vita foret v-i nec tristia nossem bella!, Tib.; medium sanos v. affectus tenet; omnem v-um, Sen.; Tiberius primo prudentes, dein v-um, diutissime provincias fefellit; v. cupiens voluptatum et, si eodem princeps trahat, lætum; sic conquisitum collectumque v-us Moyses monuit, ne <text:soft-page-break/>- hominum opem exspectaret, T.; effigies Poppaeæ afflictæ v-i manibus, Sen. trag.: imperitum, Pn.; v-i pars ultima nostri, Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt märkes uttrycket: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">in vulgus</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">in vulgum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i betydelsen af så wäl </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(ut) ibland allmänheten,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">för allmänheten; ibland folket:</text:span></text:span> res exit et emanat in v-us; alter religiosus etiam nunc dies, alter in v-us ignotus; fit, ut multi per me tibi velint commendari. Ego autem tribuo nonnunquam in v-us (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan åtskilnad),</text:span> sed plerumque necessariis (Ep. ad Fam. XIII. 70), C.; in v-um disciplinam efferri volunt (Druides), Cs.; librum in v-us edere, N.; spargere voces in v-um ambiguas, Vg.; gratæ in v-us leges, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Massan, gemenskapen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en här:</text:span> in v-us militum efferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utsprida),</text:span> Cs.: comperit Lysander, v-um Atheniensium in terram prædatum exisse, N.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mängden, massan, hopen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en klaß:</text:span> avium, Enn.; servorum, Ter.; patronorum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volgō</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulgo), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allmänt, öfwerallt, wanligen:</text:span></text:span> v. dici solet, Ter.; facit ille, quod v. hau solent, Pt.; v. homines occidebantur; hae literæ, quas v. ad te mitto; v. auditur, C.; v. totis castris testamenta obsignabantur; v. milites a signis discedebant, Cs.; incedit veles v-o sicilibus latis, Enn. Ann. 499; coronis - v. donabatur Alcibiades, N.; v. jam homines eum statum rerum, qui sub Numa rege fuerat, requirebant, L.; v. nascetur amomum; habitant ad litora v. Cyclopes, Vg.; Volcanum pro igne v. audimus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volgāris</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulgaris), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tillhör allmänheten, som brukas af hopen l. allmänt</text:span> (volgo); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allmän, wanlig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med l. utan den bibetydelse, som ligger i: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hwardaglig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (olärd), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">alldaglig, trivial</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (banal):</text:span> singularia an v-ia?; ejus artis usus v. communisque est; in communi vita et v-i hominum consuetudine non esse rudem; oratio ad v-em popularemque sensum accommodata; v. opinio; v-e exordium est, quod in plures causas potest accommodari; v-e genus dicendi; v-i sermone de re disputare; v-e scortum; v. et obsoletus; commendatio non v.; v. et pervagatus, C.; virtus recludens immeritis mori cælum negata tentat iter via coetusque v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hopens)</text:span> et udam spernit humum fugiente penna; jejunus raro stomachus v-ia temnit, Hor.; puella, Ov.; gestus v., non ex arte; verba; vocabula, Qu.; oratio Senecæ v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(alldagligt)</text:span> et protrita, Gell. XII. 2. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volgārĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På hopens sätt, i wanligt språk:</text:span></text:span> scribere, C.; dari; electa, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volgārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allmän, hwardaglig, trivial, olärd:</text:span></text:span> Afr.; incompertam et v-am traditionem rei non exploratæ sequi, Gell. XVI. 5. 1.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volgĭvăgus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulgĭvăgus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bland hopen ströfwande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lös, oregelbunden, obunden:</text:span></text:span> Venus; mos, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulgo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra allmän, göra gemensam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillgänglig för allmänheten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. för hwem som helst; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">göra wanlig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> contagia v-bant (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spredo bland hela folket)</text:span> morbos; <text:soft-page-break/>ferarum prope ritu v-antur concubitus patrum et plebis; laudem; v-re corpus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla sig fal);</text:span> munus v-tum isse a civibus in socios, L. (II. 41); librum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(offentliggöra),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ställa på lika fot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med hwem som helst (”göra gemen”):</text:span> in ordinem se ipsum cogere et v-ri cum privatis (decemvirum), L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sprida, bekantgöra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett rykte, en mening:</text:span> facinus; famam, L.; bellaque jam totum famā v-ta per orbem; dolorem, Vg.; falsa; opinionem, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volgātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allmän, wanlig; allmänt bekant, spridd, känd:</text:span></text:span> navis, C.: v-ior fama est -, L.; non ante v-as per artes verba loquor socianda chordis, Hor.; sensus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(betydelser)</text:span> verborum v-simi, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utspridare:</text:span></text:span> taciti, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīvolgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Dīvulgo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bland allmänheten utsprida, sprida, bekantgöra, offentliggöra:</text:span></text:span> rem sermonibus; librum, C.: consilium, Cs.; opinionem, Js.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīvolgātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allmänt spridd, allmänt känd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">omtalad, beryktad:</text:span></text:span> Afer primoribus oratorum additus, d-o ingenio, T.; gloria, Luc.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wanlig, simpel:</text:span></text:span> C. Fam. X. 16. 2.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvolgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(evulgo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bringa ut bland allmänheten, göra allmänt bekant, offentliggöra, utbreda kännedom om</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sprida:</text:span></text:span> jus civile e-vit Flavius, L.; e-tus pudor (Neroni) non satietatem, sed incitamentum addidit; e-to arcano, posse alibi, quam Romæ, principes fieri; Octaviæ injurias e-re, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Involgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Invulgo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bekantgöra, upptäcka, angifwa:</text:span></text:span> Allobroges, C.; disciplinam, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervolgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Pervulgo), 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sprida till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bland, göra tillgänglig för allmänheten, göra allmän, offentliggöra:</text:span></text:span> juris consulti artem suam p-ri nolebant; operam suam; tabulas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(offentliga handlingar);</text:span> se omnibus mulier; tota Sicilia, C.; deûm numina, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomfara, -ströfwa:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> quæ p-ant nemora avia pervolitantes; lumina cælum, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervolgātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allmän; wanlig; allmänt känd:</text:span></text:span> consolatio; res p-a in vulgus, in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> apud omnes; dignitas p-sima, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervolgāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwardagligt:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvolgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Prōvulgo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Offentliggöra, bekantgöra:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Volito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Volo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Volnus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulnus; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäl af</text:span> vello, vulsum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom</text:span> facinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> facio), ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sår:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sår, blodvite</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en mennisko- l. djurkropp:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> v. infligere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slå)</text:span> alicui; facere; v. excipere, accipere; v. <text:soft-page-break/>alligare, obligare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förbinda),</text:span> sanare, refricare; v. acu punctum; v. recrudescit; ex v-e recreari; v-i mederi, C.; multis et illatis et acceptis v-bus, Cs.; curare, L.; erat æger v bus, quæ acceperat; v. mortiferum, N.; v. grave, lĕve, acerbum, foedum; v. pati, ferre; v. adigere, dare alicui, Ov.; facere, Qu.; recens, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngn</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicujus</text:span>) ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hugg, slag, skott</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.:</text:span> cadunt viri v-e virorum, Pt. Amph. 234; v-bus confodi, ici, confici, L.; v-e tardus Ulixi; v-a jactare; inter se miscere, dirigere; hæsit sub gutture v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hugget = wapnet),</text:span> Vg.; elusa v-a; se subducere a v-e; v-e consequi alqm, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett träd l. dödt föremål, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hål, hugg:</text:span></text:span> v-bus evicta ornus, Vg.; falcis; aratri, Ov.; calcei <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hål på skon),</text:span> Juv. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sorg, qwal</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skada, förtret:</text:span></text:span> nullum Fortunæ v. accepit; Fortunæ v-e percussus; reip. imponere v.; v. in re et fortuna, in moribus naturaque <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oeconomiskt mißöde, medfödd brist l. moraliskt lyte);</text:span> v-bus suis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oeconomiska förluster)</text:span> mederi; v. conscientiæ, C.; v. super v-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mißöde, nederlag),</text:span> L.; æterno v-e amoris, Lucr.; regina gravi jam dudum saucia cura v. alit venis et cæco carpitur igni (ɔ: amore); Juno æternum servans sub pectore v. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">harmen);</text:span> mentis, Vg.; gravissimum v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sorg)</text:span> accepit morte filii, N.; dicat, quo beatus v-e, qua pereat sagitta, Hor.; immedicabile v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skada);</text:span> inconsolabile v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sorg);</text:span> amor utrique æquum dedit v.; mutua sensit v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genkärlek);</text:span> in pectore, in animo grave v. habebam, Ov.; domesticum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volnĕrārius</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulnĕrārius), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sår-:</text:span></text:span> emplastrum, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volnĕrārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sårläkare:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volnĕro</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulnero), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Såra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> acie ipsa et ferri viribus v-ri; corpus ferro, C.; in adversum os fundā v-ri, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skada:</text:span></text:span> naves v-tæ, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personliga object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Såra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = skada, förnärma, förtreta:</text:span> voce alqm, C.; animum alicujus, L.; nuntius aures, Vg.; reum, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volnĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sårande, sår:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> vis sine cæde, sine v-e, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> vitæ, famæ, salutis v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wåld, skada till -),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convolnĕro</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Convulnero), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Såra:</text:span></text:span> alqm, Sen.; frontem, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Involnĕrābĭlis</text:span> <text:line-break/>(invulnĕrābĭlis), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Osårbar:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Involnĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sårfri, ej sårad:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volnĭfĭcus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulnĭfĭcus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sårande; som gifwer sår:</text:span></text:span> chalybs, Vg.; sus; telum, Ov.; deus, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Vŏlo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lefwande warelser, med wingar:</text:span> aves, C., Lucr.; v-at ille per āera magnum remigio alarum, Vg.; alte; demissius; Dædalus; circum <text:soft-page-break/>freta Alcyone, Ov.; graculi gregatim v-ant, Qu.; perniciter: catervatim, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om concreta, lefwande l. liflösa subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga, swäfwa, ila, fara:</text:span></text:span> curriculo, Pt.: literæ; v-re, non iter facere, C.; tela, L., Sa.; jamque faces et saxa v-ant; curru v-re; navis v-at; v-at ignis; vapor; ventus; stipulæ; ille v-at campis, Vg.; Etrusca præter et v-ate (navi) litora; ab Italia, Hor.; favilla; plumbum; pocula missa; passu alite homo; equus, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om abstracta subject, såsom tid, tankar (ord): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga:</text:span></text:span> veniet tempus (mortis), sive properabis sive retractabis: v-at enim ætas, C.; curæ laqueata circum tecta v-ntes; verba, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlantes</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fåglar:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlātĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygande, wingad:</text:span></text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygtig, ostadig:</text:span></text:span> Academia v-a et sui similis, C.; homo, C., Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlātĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. bemärkelse, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wingad:</text:span></text:span> bestiæ, C.; pecus, Col.; puer (Amor), Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygande, ilande, snabb:</text:span></text:span> telum, Lucr., Ov.; ferrum, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygtig, förgänglig:</text:span></text:span> ætas, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygande:</text:span></text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fåglar:</text:span></text:span> avidior, Col. VIII. 10. 5. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygt, sätt att flyga, flygande:</text:span></text:span> declarantur futura alitum v-bus; aquilæ admoneri v-u; v-us (<text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ideligen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga; swäfwa hit och dit:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om wingade wäsenden:</text:span> volucres levandi laboris causa passim ac libere solutæ opere v-ant, C.; aquila super carpentum cum magno clangore v-ans, L.; perdix - propter humum v-at ponitque in sepibus ova, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga, fara, swäfwa, ila hit och dit</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i rummet); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ströfwa, stryka, swärma omkring, utbreda sig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofta med bibetydelse af öfwermod l. skryt:</text:span> in foro; per totum forum florens ac popularis v-at; per gentes; conjuratio; vis latrocinii v-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utbreder sig),</text:span> C.; per Italiam Hannibal, L.; favilla, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ströfwa omkring, utbreda sig, swäfwa omkring</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i högre regioner):</text:span> nostri animi v-re cupiunt, vacui cura ac labore; Clodius v-at, furit: multis denuntiat, nihil certi habet; homo v-ans <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hufwudyr)</text:span> gloriæ cupiditate, C.<text:line-break/>c. nemo me lacrimis decoret neque funera fletu faxit. Cur? v-o vivus per ora virûm (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mina sånger flyga från mun till mun),</text:span> elogium Ennii ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlŭcer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlŭcris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">comm. A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med flygförmåga begåfwad (om fåglar och flygfän m. m.), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wingad:</text:span></text:span> natura alias bestias nantes aquarum incolas esse voluit, alias v-es cælo frui libero; angues v-es, C.; v. columba, Vg.; penna, Tib.; mater equi v-is (Pegasi); deum v-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om Amor);</text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>ætherium v-i carpit iter pede (Mercurius); v-er cum matre Cupido (Met. lX. 482); v-er serpens, Luc. VI. 677; Cupido puer et v-er, Qu. II. 4. 26; id., Sen. Hipp. 187. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlŭcris</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fågel:</text:span></text:span> āeriæ v-es, Lucr.; quædam v-es longius mille et octingenta stadia vident; v-es volitant solutæ opere; teneros v-es matremque peremit anguis, C.; tua nunc v-es astant super ossa marinæ, nunc tibi pro tumulo Carpathium omne mare est, Ppt.; obscænas pelagi ferro foedare volūcres, Vg.; turba volŭcrum, ritu volūcrum; diro facta volūcris crimine Nyctēis, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygande, flygtig; ilande, wingad, snabb,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om rörelser l. i rörelser i rummet:</text:span> o nuntium v-em!; astrorum v-es motus, C.; sagitta; classis; nebulæ; aura, Ov.; fumus; currus; navis; sagitta; aura; fluvius, Vg.; te v-em sequor, te per gramina Martii campi, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snabb, rask:</text:span></text:span> genus dicendi v-e atque incitatum, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om osinliga subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snabb, flygtig, lätt, ostadig, förgänglig:</text:span></text:span> nihil est tam v-e, quam maledictum; Fortuna; spes, C.; fatum; veluti stet v-is dies, cessas deripere horreo - amphoram, Hor.; par levibus ventis volucrique simillima somno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sömnen personificeras såsom ett bewingadt wäsende),</text:span> Vg.; anima, Ov.; gaudium, T.; v-er somnus, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlŭcrĭpes</text:span>, pĕdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snabbfotad:</text:span></text:span> Aus.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlŭcrĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snabbt, raskt:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invŏlŭcris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ej kan flyga:</text:span> pulli, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Advŏlo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(arvolo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga till, i flygt närma sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">komma till:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> avis ad avem, C.; examen vesparum in forum, L.; ales, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga, skynda, ila till:</text:span></text:span> si stas, ingredere: si ingredere, curre: si curris, a-a; Romam; res in pectus alicui, C.; hostes repente undique ad pabulatores a-runt, Cs.; ad equites a-at dictator, obtestans, ut descendant ab equis et pugnam capessant; Latini equites cum tumultuoso a-ant nuntio, Volscos ad urbem oppugnandam venire, L.; imago ad aliquem, Lucr.; fama alicui, Vg.; in auxilium, Pn.; a-at Hector, poēt. ap. Prisc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Advŏlo vŏlātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygande till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn (anflygande):</text:span> C. poēt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Advŏlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga, fladdra till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någon:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Altĭvŏlans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Högt flygande:</text:span></text:span> genus a-tum, Enn., Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Antĕvŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga före, framför:</text:span></text:span> Vg.; St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Āvŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:line-break/>(abvolo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">afvolo</text:span>, Paul. Diac. p. 26 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">M.):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga bort:</text:span></text:span> C. poēt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ila, fara, skynda bort,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om concreta och abstracta subject:</text:span> hinc; voluptas, C.; a-at ad equites, L. (III. 61; advolat, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Mdvg).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Circumvŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swäfwa omkring,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. och oeg. mening:</text:span> nox alta cava c-at umbra; nox atra caput c-at umbra, Vg.; Erycina ridens, quem Jocus c-at et Cupido, Hor.; alqm, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Circumvŏlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga, flaxa, fladdra omkring,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> eg. och oeg.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: arguta lacūs c-vit hirundo, Vg.; equites, Lucr.; quæ c-as agilis thyma?, Hor.; coetu c-antium alitum territa aquila, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga, ila, skynda tillsammans:</text:span></text:span> rumor venit, datum iri gladiatores, populus c-at, Ter.; cuncta ex Italia ad me revocandum c-rant; ad rostra c., C.; ad sellas consulum c-vere Patres, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga ned, flyga bort,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. mening och oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swäfwa, störta, rusa, ila ned</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bort:</text:span></text:span> angues jubati d-ant deorsum in impluvium, Pt.; ab afflicta amicitia transfugere, ad florentem d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom fågeln till rof),</text:span> C.; qui fortunis alicujus inducti sunt secuti ejus amicitiam, hi, simul ac fortuna dilapsa est, d-ant (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äro såsom blåsta bort)</text:span> omnes, C. (Her.); mobilis ille d-at in terram liquidi color aureus ignis, Lucr.; ales in tabernam; nihil agenti sibi de cælo d-turam in sinum victoriam censet; d-ant de tribunali consules; in forum, L.; Jovis in multas d-at ales aves, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga ut, flyga upp, flyga fram:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> apes quum jam e-turæ sunt, susurrant vehementer, Varr.; ex quercu e-vit nuntia fulva Jovis mirandā visa figurā; e-re, non excurrere videbatur, C.; domesticæ aves, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fri), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">åstad; ila fram, bort:</text:span></text:span> rus ex urbe; sic e-vit oratio; ex corporum vinculis tanquam ex carcere animus, C.; e-at ignis, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rusa ut, störta ut:</text:span></text:span> exanimatus e senatu, C.; hostes e silva e-runt, Cs.; per medias furibunda vias, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = stiga till höghet och wärdighet:</text:span> quem illi in principibus esse facile sunt passi, altius e-re certe noluerunt, C.; ex humili sede sublima e-at, Acc.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga undan, undkomma, undgå:</text:span></text:span> ex poena; ex vestra severitate, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvŏlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pläga att flyga ut:</text:span></text:span> patentibus fenestris ad requirendos cibus e-ant aves, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭpĕrēvŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga öfwer:</text:span></text:span> Alpes, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intervŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga, swäfwa, ila emellan:</text:span></text:span> Col., St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intervŏlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga emellan:</text:span></text:span> carne pluit, quam - ingens numerus avium i-do rapuisse fertur, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invŏlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga in:</text:span></text:span> in villam columbæ, Varr.; nidis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rusa på, störta sig öfwer, bemäktiga sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett förstärkt</text:span> invado):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">in alqm</text:span>): in capillum, in oculos alicui, Ter.; jamne in hominem i-em?; equites i-ant impetu alacri, Pt.; in nostram possessionem, quasi caducam atque vacuam, nobis occupatis, i-runt (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slagit under sig, inkräktat),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerfalla; stjäla:</text:span></text:span> castra, T.; pallium, Catl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invŏlātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygt mot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> avis, C. (Fam. VI. 6).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invŏlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fladdra, bölja öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på:</text:span></text:span> comæ humeris, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga igenom</text:span></text:span> (locum); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">flyga fram</text:span></text:span> (in locum):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> avis ædes, Vg.; in sedem suam, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerfara, genomfara:</text:span></text:span> crassa pulvis oritur: omnem p-at cæli fretum, Enn.; LVI milia passuum, C.; axe citato Flaminiam, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervŏlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ideligen genomflyga, -fara, -swäfwa:</text:span></text:span> per dissæpta domorum voces p-ant, Lucr.; lumen sole repercusso aut radiantis imagine lunæ omnia p-at late loca, Vg. (Aen. VIII. 22 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.).</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervŏlĭtantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ideligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swäfwande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swängning:</text:span></text:span> mundi circa terram, Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prætervŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga förbi,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. och oeg. mening:</text:span> ales alqm; sententiæ acutæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sinnrika, spetsiga)</text:span> sensūs hominum non acutorum p-ant; numerus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rhythm),</text:span> C.; occasionis opportunitas, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prævŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga före, förut, i spetsen:</text:span></text:span> grues p-antes, C.; aquila velut dux p-vit, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga fram; ila, störta, skynda fram:</text:span></text:span> apes, Pn. - hostes subito omnibus copiis p-runt, Cs.; Romulus ad primores p-at; desiliunt ex equis, p-ant in primum equites, L.; p-at armatus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> grus, C.; mergi, Vg.; telum; Dædalus alis, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subtervŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga inunder:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subvŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swäfwa uppåt:</text:span></text:span> āer et ignis in cælestem locum, C.; avis ut novas assumpserat humeris alas, s-at, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭpervŏlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ofwanför:</text:span></text:span> hasta alqm, Vg.; Perseus totum - s-at orbem, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭpervŏlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ständigt flyga, flaxa öfwer:</text:span></text:span> Tereus infelix sua tecta s-vit alis, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Transvŏlo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(trāvolo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga hän öfwer, till annan sida:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> grues Pontum, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ila</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fara, skynda öfwer, förbi:</text:span></text:span> vox aures, Lucr.; arma ad hostes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwergå),</text:span> Pt.; Alpes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerfara),</text:span> C.; eques <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rytteriet)</text:span> in alteram partem (pugnæ), L.; amor t-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förbi)</text:span> in medio posita, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Transvŏlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyga öfwer, igenom:</text:span></text:span> voces claustra, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Vŏlo,</text:span> vŏlui, velle, <text:span text:style-name="T2">V. anom.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">præs. ind.</text:span> vis, vult, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.</text:span> volt; <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> volŭmus, vultis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> voltis, volunt; sis, sultis = si vis, si vultis, Pt.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">præs. conj.</text:span> vĕlim, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.</text:span> vŏlim, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Prisc.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm., construeradt med ensam</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf. præs.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc. c. inf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen med samma subject som det styrande verbet), med ensam</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">conj.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sällan med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">ut, ne</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">conj.</text:span>: uti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så wißt)</text:span> bonis vos vostrosque omnes nuntiis me (Mercurium) adficere voltis, ea adferam, ea uti nuntiem, quæ maxume in rem vostram communem sient, ita huic facietis fabulæ silentium; v-o esse liber: nequiquam v-o; facile meus pater, quod volt, facit; nunc si voltis deprecari huic seni, ne vapulet, remur impetrari posse, plausum si clarum datis; vin (= visne) experiamur?; hæc commeminisse ego volam te, Pt.; Persium non curo legere (libros meos): Lælium Decimum v., Lucil.; velit, nolit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(han må wilja </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. icke wilja);</text:span> velim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jag skulle wilja - ett höfligt sätt att uttrycka en önskan om ngt, som förutsättes såsom möjligt)</text:span> animum a me parumper avertas et Lælium ipsum putes loqui; vellem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jag wille - en önskan om ngt omöjligt)</text:span> adesse posset Panætius; quam vellem ad Stoicos te applicavisses!; oratio Scipionis non est antiquior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mera gammaldags),</text:span> quam de multis, quam voles, Lælii; id spectant leges, id v-unt, ut suæ cuique rei custodia libera sit; v-o vos bene sperare; malitia vult se videri prudentiam, sed ab ea abest distatque plurimum; si legere aut audire voletis externa, respublicas a senibus sustentatas reperietis; monet proverbium mature fieri senem, si velis diu esse senex, C.; senex diu vivendo multa, quæ non volt, videt, Cæcil. ap. C.; quæsivit a me pater, vellemne secum in castra proficisci, N.; nihil frustra v.; si viri esse voltis, me sequimini; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med ensam</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">conj.,</text:span> Jug. 24), Sa.; jussit eos captivos tradere, si sibi purgati esse vellent; quid fieri velit, edicit, Cs.; velitis, jubeatis, Quirites, bellum cum Philippo rege fieri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(formel för</text:span> rogatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. hemställan af den föredragande embetsmannen till folkförsamlingen);</text:span> abi, nuntia Romanis, cælestes ita velle, ut mea Roma caput orbis terrarum sit, L.; multa v-tem dicere deseruit; quam vellent æthere in alto nunc et pauperiem et duros perferre labores!, Vg.; quantum vis, tolle!; scire v-im, libro pretium quotus arroget annus; quid faciam vis!; sic di voluere; ita majores v-runt; vellem in amicitia sic erraremus, Hor.; hoc v-o, sic jubeo, sit pro ratione voluntas; majores - præceptorem cari voluere parentis esse loco; convenerat olim, ut faceres tu, quod velles, Juv.; interrogo, Cæsar, quam partem rei publicæ tibi mandari velis, T.; in magnis et v-isse sat est, Ppt.; velle parum est, Ov.; Nero (in judicio capitali sanciendo): vellem, inquit, nescire literas, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskilda betydelser l. constructioner:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc. c. inf.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Påstå; uppställa en sats:</text:span></text:span> amicitiam ex inopia et indigentia natam v-unt; virtutem duram et ferream esse v-unt, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakliga subject = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fordra, kräfwa; medgifwa:</text:span></text:span> multa renascentur, quæ jam cecidere, cadentque, quæ nunc sunt in honore vocabula, si volet usus; versibus exponi tragicis res comica non vult, Hor. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med participium l. subst. l. adj. såsom prædicatsnomen till objectet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja, önska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn (i ett tillstånd, till ngt):</text:span> salvam velle rempublicam; hac cura te liberatum volo; defensum velle alqm, C.; non uxor te salvom volt, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i analogi härmed äfwen af impersonelt passivum:</text:span> omnibus consultum vult, C.<text:line-break/>d. velle <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquid</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hafwa ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">önska sig, söka, begära, fordra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> ab aliquo; gratiam alicujus; si quid vellent, ad Idus Apriles reverterentur, Cs.; nec si plura velim, tu dare deneges, Hor.; quid inde æquomst dare mihi? dimidium v-o dicas, Pt.; quam joco rem v-isti a me tandem, quin perfeceris?, Ter. Eun. 180. <text:line-break/>e. velle <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquem,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja träffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wilja tala med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn;</text:span> velle aliquem aliquid = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wilja hafwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, wilja hafwa ngt af ngn:</text:span> paucis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med ett par ord)</text:span> te v-o; te v-o, Pt., Ter.; Cs. b. G. I. 34 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Kraner);</text:span> numquid nunc aliut me vis?, Pt. Mil. 575.<text:line-break/>f. velle <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui bene</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicujus causa</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="T2">male</text:span> v. <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wäl, illa:</text:span></text:span> plane v-o his magistratibus, quorum voluntatem in supplicatione sum expertus; videor intellexisse, te Anneji causa omnia velle, C.; male v. alicui, Pt., Ter.; bene volt tibi. - Nequam <text:soft-page-break/>illud verbumst bene volt, nisi qui bene facit, Pt.<text:line-break/>g. velle <text:span text:style-name="T2">sibi aliquid,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer och deras handlingar l. ord = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja, åsyfta, betyda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> quid sibi vellet <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fråga i or. obl.),</text:span> quid in suas possessiones veniret?, Cs.; non satis intellexi, quid sibi verba ista vellent; quid istæ numorum accessiones sibi v-unt?; quid statuæ inauratæ sibi v-unt?, C.; quid sibi vult hæc oratio; audite, quid sibi iste Eunuchus velit, Ter.; quid tibi vis, mulier?, Hor.; quid vult sibi noctis imago?, Ov.<text:line-break/>h. res est alicui volenti = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">är i enlighet med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wilje</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">önskan, önskas af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> militia plebi v-enti non esse putabatur, Sa. (Jug. 84. 3. 100; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Heinichens lat. deutsches Wörterbuch p.</text:span> 794); mea cymba v-nti solvitur, aucturis tot mea fata meis, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Willig, friwillig, hågad:</text:span></text:span> tenuant armenta v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(friwilligt, med afsigt),</text:span> Vg.; sponte sua properant: labor est inhibere v-es, Ov.; a v-bus accipere, Vell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälwillig, bewågen, nådig:</text:span></text:span> quorum virtuti belli fortuna pepercit, eorundem me libertati parcere certum est: dono, ducite, doque v-bus cum magnis dis, Enn. ap. C.; v-i animo agere; dis v-bus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genom gudarnes nåd)</text:span> magni estis, Sa.; deum deo natum regem parentemque urbis Romanæ salvere universi Romulum jubent: pacem exposcunt, uti volens propitius suam sospitet progeniem, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäl behaglig; angenäm,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> blott i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">neutr. pl.</text:span> volentia: plebi v-ia, Sa. ap. Non., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gerna:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilje, håg:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlōnes</text:span>, num, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Friwillige soldater,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om slafwar, som inträdde i romerska hären efter slaget wid Cannæ:</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏluntārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Friwillig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om personer och deras handlingar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">godwillig:</text:span></text:span> motus animi; auxilia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hjelptrupper);</text:span> amicus; id ipsum, quod recte fit, ita est justum, si est v-um; virtutes; mors v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sjelfmord),</text:span> C.; milites v-i, Cs., L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Godtycklig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> naturalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> necessarius), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ords härledning i mots. till böjning:</text:span> Varr. l. l. VIII. 21 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏluntas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wilje):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja, önskan, håg, lust, behag:</text:span></text:span> ad <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter)</text:span> alicujus v-em loqui, se conformare; res ad v-em fluunt; facere aliquid ex v-e alicujus; habere v-em ad opprimendum, nocendi; id tua fert v.; res accidit ex v-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(önskan);</text:span> Cæsar cedit justis et officio incensis, non inanibus aut ambitiosis v-bus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(önskningar);</text:span> abjeci v-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lust)</text:span> discendi; tua v. est, ut simul simus, C.; dixit, quid suæ v-is esset, Cs.; non est tua tuta v., Ov.; cognita eorum v-e; alicujus v-i morem gerere, N.; adero, tua si mihi certa v., Vg.; sperabat, se ex v-e Antonio usurum, Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fri wilja,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynnerhet i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>: æquius erat, id v-e fieri, C.; sua v-e diem prodixerunt, L.; nonnulli sua v-e apud eum remanserunt, Cs.; urbes partim vi, partim v-e imperio suo adjungit, Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bestämmande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">medgifwande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (befallning l. </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föranledande):</text:span> si hoc mea v-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med min wilja)</text:span> factum est, est quod mihi succenseas, Pt.; hæc non sunt in nostra v-e, C.; non minus eorum v-e imperium obtinuit, qui miserant, quam illorum, cum quibus erat profectus, N.; rogare, ut ejus v-e id sibi facere liceat, Cs.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afsigt, uppsåt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> prægnant: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (god wilja, i mots. till förmåga):</text:span> suscepi v-em faciendi; fui ego in ea v-e, ut -, C.; v-em occultare; a v-e (libertatis populo reddendæ) deterritus tyrannus crudelior esse coepit, N.; Massiliensium v. (urbis dedendæ), Cs.; hæc et meam æquitatem indicabunt et vestram v-em, N. (Thrasyb. IV. 2); temerata, Ov.; immutata, Sa.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sinnelag, tänkesätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot ngn:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i indifferent mening, bestämdt medelst adjectiva:</text:span> legati venerunt Romani, qui de regis v-e explorarent; vulgi offensa v.; propria v-e esse in alqm, N.; v. aliena ab aliquo; copulare v-es, C.; omnium v-es abalienare ab aliquo; non se ignorare, quæ vires suæ, quæ v. erga Cæsarem esset totius provinciæ, Cs.; v-e alienari ab aliquo, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absolut = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälwilja (wälmening):</text:span></text:span> mutua; summa, singularis v. in alqm, C.; Divitiaci summam in se v-em cognoverat; egregia in se v.; super omnia voltus accessere boni nec iners pauperque v., Ov.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tycke, smak, åsigt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynnerhet uti æsthetiska ting:</text:span> in alia v-e esse; naturis differunt (illi scriptores), v-e similes sunt; ex eorum scriptis, cujusque ætatis quæ dicendi ratio v-que fuerit, intelligi potest, C.<text:line-break/>7. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Betydelse, syftning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ord:</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>8. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en persons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sista wilja:</text:span></text:span> mortuorum, defunctorum v-es defendere, C., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bĕnĕvŏlens</text:span>, tis (Pt.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bĕnĕvŏlus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(benĭvolens, <text:line-break/>benĭvolus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: C<text:span text:style-name="T2">omp.</text:span> benevolentior, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Superl.</text:span> -lentissimus: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälwillig, wänlig, wälwilligt sinnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stämd:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> formen</text:span> benevolens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förekommer äfwen såsom</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wän:</text:span></text:span> Pseudolus mi ita imperavit, ut alqm hominem strenuom b-tem adducerem ad se; quoja hic prope me vox sonat? Tui b-tis, si ita es, ut ego te volo: sin aliter es, inimici atque irati tibi; Megaronides communis meus et tuus b-ens; b-lus erga alqm, Pt.; b-lus alicui, Ter., C.; animus, auditor b.; b-um mihi judicem facilius facere (reddere) possum in cursu orationis, quam quum omnia sunt inaudita; b-ior, quam fui, esse non possum; fungi officio b-simi, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bĕnĕvŏle</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälwilligt, wänligt:</text:span></text:span> amice et b. erga alqm facere aliquid; et monendi amici sunt sæpe et objurgandi et hæc accipienda amice, quum b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i wälwillig afsigt, i wälmening)</text:span> fiunt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bĕnĕvŏlentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälwilja, bewågenhet, wänlighet; tillgifwenhet; wälwilligt tänkesätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wänskap, kärlek):</text:span> Ter.; b-am hominum movere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäcka),</text:span> conciliare, adjungere sibi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fästa wid sin person);</text:span> animos hominum allicere ad b-am; capere, captare, colligere, consectari, comparare, conservare hominum b-am; b-ā complecti alqm; præstare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wisa)</text:span> alicui b-am; alicujus erga se b-am experiri, perspicere; habere b-am, esse singulari b-a in alqm; conferre b-am in alqm, C.; magnam regis b-am consequi; lacrimans accepit civium b-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wälwilja, om ynnestbetygelser);</text:span> b-ā munitum <text:soft-page-break/>imperium; quod ceteri reges imperio potuerunt, hic b-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kärlek)</text:span> tenuit; b-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wänskap)</text:span> usumque alicujus retinere, N.; b. in alqm, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mălĕvŏlens</text:span>, tis (Pt.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mălĕvŏlus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(malĭvolens, <text:line-break/>malĭvolus), -entior, -entissimus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illwillig, elak; illa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">owänligt, afwogt sinnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot ngn</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui, in aliquem</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">owän, fiende:</text:span></text:span> est miserorum, ut m-tes sint atque invideant bonis; ingenium, Pt.; homo naturā maledicus et m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(elak);</text:span> in me in senatu fuit turpiter m.; sermo; obtrectatio; omnibus est m.; omnium m-orum, iniquorum, invidorum animos frangere, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mălĕvŏlentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illwilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (att wilja l. unna ngn illa l. ondt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">elakhet, owilja, ogunst, afund, skadeglädje:</text:span></text:span> m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skadeglädje)</text:span> est voluptas ex malo alterius sine emolumento suo; animus nullā in quemquam m-ā suffusus; posterorum erit verius judicium obtrectatione et m-ā liberatum, C.; m. et invidia, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mālo</text:span> [i. e. magis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> mage volo; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.</text:span> <text:line-break/>māvŏlo, māvellem, māvĕlim, mallim (Pt. Trin. 762) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w</text:span>.], mālui, malle: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hellre wilja, hellre önska sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wilja hafwa), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">föredraga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt l. att göra, få ngt (om constructionen se</text:span> volo):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> nunc fuisse me quam esse māvelim; ostium lenonis crepuit. Crura mavellem; mallim, ut verum dicant, Pt.; m-o errare cum Platone, quam cum istis vera dicere; mallem Cerberum metueres, quam ista tam inconsiderate diceres; Homerus ad deos humana transferebat: divina mallem ad nos; quævis mallem fuisset causa, quam ista, quam dicis; ego vero m-o virum, qui pecunia egeat, quam pecuniam, quæ viro, C.; ignoscere quam persequi malle; sua ab aliis bene facta laudari, quam (scribere res gestas) m-bat; bellum quam pacem m-bat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(föredrog kriget framför freden);</text:span> sanguinem quam omnia malle, Sa.; m-uit se diligi, quam metui, oblivisci, quam ulcisci, N.; se victoriæ Pompeji comitem esse m-bat, quam socium Cæsaris in rebus adversis, Cs.; cur nescire pudens stulte, quam discere, m-o?, Hor.; precibus mavult quam viribus uti; Byblida jam mavult, quam se vocet ille sororem, Ov.; malŏ pater tibi sit Thersites -, Juv.; tuta et præsentia, quam vetera et periculosa malle, T. (Ann. I. 2). <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskilda betydelser l. constructioner:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. malle <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui,</text:span> malle <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui omnia</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bättre:</text:span></text:span> ego illi omnia m-o, quam mihi; in hac re m-o universæ Græciæ, quam negotiatoribus, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pleonastiskt:</text:span> malo potius, quam -: an ille si potuisset evadere, Uticæ potius, quam Romæ, esse m-isset?, C.; potius patriæ opes augeri quam regis m-uit, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nōlo</text:span> (ne-volo; <text:line-break/>nollo, Pt.; non vis, non vult et cet.; nēvis, nēvolt, Pt.; noltis, Lucil.), nōlui, nolle <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> ne = non <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> volo):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Icke wilja;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ensam</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wägra;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">imper.</text:span> nolī (-īte, -īto, -ītōte) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">låt wara, låt bli</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofta i sw. jemte sin inf. att öfwersätta med </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">icke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och imperat.):</text:span> noli minitari; hinc exemplum capere volt, nisi tu nēvis; tempestas venit, confringit tegulas: ibi dominus indiligens reddere alias nevolt, Pt. (Most. 748. 105; non vis, non velint, ibdm. 323, 666; <text:soft-page-break/>nevis, Men. V. 2. 35, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lorenz);</text:span> se non nolle (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hafwa lust)</text:span> dixit; emori n-o (poēt.); nolite arbitrari, me, quum a vobis discessero, nusquam aut nullum fore; nollem Corinthum (excidissent majores), C.; Accius Hectōrem nolet facere, Hectora malet, Valer. Cato; hæc nolite pati, Sa.; nolis longa feræ bella Numantiæ - aptari citharæ modis; sunt, qui nolint tetigisse -; alicui procedere recte nolle, Hor.; Spartam redire n-uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wägrade);</text:span> non parere n-uit, N.; nolim rata sit (res): nollem tibi visa fuissem, Ov.; me n-ente <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot min wilja),</text:span> Qu.; ego n-o Florus esse, amblare per tabernas, Hadr. imp.<text:line-break/>2. nolle <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Icke wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wäl:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervĕlim</text:span>, pervelle, -vellem: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gerna wilja:</text:span></text:span> illum videre p-lem; scire p-lim, C.; p-le videre, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ologēsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">parthiskt namn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ologēsocerta, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i inre Asien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Volones <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Volo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Volpes</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulpes), is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enligt Varros etymologi</text:span> Qu. I. 6 = voli-pes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> I. volo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Räf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofta nämnd såsom det slugaste bland djur l. såsom repræsentant för denna egenskap):</text:span> pirum comest v., Pt.; cauta, C.; feta v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett dåligt omen för den mötande);</text:span> nunquam te fallant animi sub v-e latentes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwad der är under räffällen</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">räfwen bakom smickrarens öra),</text:span> Hor.; mulgere hircum, jungere v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spänna räfwar för wagn, om något omöjligt),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volpēcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.: Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Räf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (räfracka):</text:span> vis leonis, fraus v-æ esse videtur, utrumque homine alienissimum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volpīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Räf-:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volpīnor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begå räfstreck:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Volpio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gammal räf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bildl.):</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olscens, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. namn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olscius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olscus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">volskisk, Volsker, folkslag i södra Latium wid Liris (Ciceros födelsestad Arpinum låg i Volskernes land):</text:span> gens V-a, C.; Tarquinius Superbus primus V-is bellum in ducentos amplius post suam ætatem annos movit, Suessamque Pometiam ex his vi cepit; bellum V-um imminebat; in V-um agrum legiones duxere consules, L.; V-a de gente Camilla, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olsce, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på volskiskt språk:</text:span> fabulari, Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Volsella <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vello.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olsĭnii <text:line-break/>(Vulsĭnii), ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Etrurien (Bolsena).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Volsĭniensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Volsura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vello.<text:line-break/>Volticulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Voltus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>oltinia tribus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en af Roms 35 tribus.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Voltiniensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>oltumna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">etruscisk förbundsgudinna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Voltuosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Voltus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>oltur <text:line-break/>(Vultur), ŭris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Apulien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Voltur</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vultur), ŭris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Voltŭrus</text:span>, i (Enn.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Voltŭrius</text:span> (vultŭrius), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gam:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> v-rus in silvis miserum comedebat hemonem, Enn.; priori Remo augurium venisse fertur, sex v-res, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. om en girig, roflysten, sniken menniska: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rofdjur, -fågel:</text:span></text:span> Pt. Trin. 101; v. paludatus, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Voltŭrīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gam-:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subvoltŭrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nästan en liten gam:</text:span> Pt. Rud. 423.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olturnum <text:line-break/>(Vulturnum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Campanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olturnus <text:line-break/>(Vulturnus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod på gränsen mellan Latium och Campanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Volturnus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulturnus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sydostwind:</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">III. <text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>olturnus <text:line-break/>(Vulturnus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en gudomlighet.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Volturnālis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: flamen V. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">guden Volturni prest:</text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/>Volturnālia, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Volturni fest.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Voltus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vultus), us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Voltum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: Enn.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppsyn, min, ansigtsuttryck</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (det ständiga och det wexlande); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ansigte</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med afseende på uttrycket:</text:span> v. est imago animi; is, qui v. appellatur, qui in nullo animante præter hominem esse potest, quomodo animis affecti simus, indicat; severus, gravis, tristis; v-us ficti et simulati; ad v-um alicujus se accommodare; mobilitas linguæ, celeritas verborum, ea denique, quæ nobis non possumus fingere, facies, v., sonus; v-u terrere alqm, C.; avorsabuntur semper vos vostraque volta, Enn.; constantia vocis et v-ūs; e v-u ephori, qui eum moneri cupiebat, insidias sibi fieri intellexit, N.; v-um fingere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förställa);</text:span> ne v-um quidem alicujus ferre posse, Cs.; v-u varius; v. bonus, demissus; ferociam in v-u retinens, Sa.; justum et tenacem propositi virum - non v. instantis tyranni mente quatit solida; ut ridentibus arrident, ita flentibus assunt v-us (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ansigte)</text:span> humani; v-u mutabilis; ridere invito v-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med twungen min),</text:span> Hor.; breviter Dido v-um demissa profatur; spem v-u simulat, premit alto corde dolorem; consilium v-u tegit et spem fronte serenat, Vg.; os homini sublime dedit cælumque tueri jussit et erectos ad sidera tollere v-us (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blickar),</text:span> Ov.; Gallus v-u (Tiberii) offensionem conjectaverat, T.; hilaris, turbatus, Pn.; mæstus, Sen.; v-um submittere, Su.; torvus, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. (<text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ansigte</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i och för sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ansigtsbild:</text:span></text:span> largoque umectat flumine v-um, Vg.; v-us velamine celat amatos; cadit in v-us; contraherere, Ov.; Epicuri v., Pn.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Min</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utseende</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (physiognomi):</text:span> unus erat toto naturæ v. in orbe, Ov.; salis placidi v., Vg.; dum licet et servat v-um fortuna benignum, adducta solvatur fronte senectus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Voltĭcŭlus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vultĭcŭlus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blott en min</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blick:</text:span></text:span> deterret, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Voltuōsus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vultuōsus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Full af miner, grimaserande; affecterande:</text:span></text:span> C., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Volva</text:span> <text:line-break/>(vulva), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> volvo?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hylsa, hölje:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lifmoder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af djur l. menniskor:</text:span> Varr.; scrophæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en läcker rätt hos Romarne),</text:span> Hor.; v-æ procidentia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(moderfall);</text:span> v-æ dolores; v. præclusa, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Volub . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Volvo.<text:line-break/>Volucer, -lucripes, -lŭcris, -lucriter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Volo. <text:line-break/>Volūcra, -lūcris, Volumen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Volvo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏlumnius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Voluntarius, Voluntas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Volo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Volvo,</text:span> volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla, wältra, (weckla, swepa, hwälfwa);</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">intr.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pr.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tumla sig, tillra, hwirfla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwälfwa), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kretsa, slingra sig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. och i allm.:</text:span> cylindrus v-itur; sol circum terram v-itur, C.; navis præ se undas v-it, Acc.; saxa v-re; cadavera v-ntes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wältrande, wändande)</text:span> amicum alii, pars cognatum reperiebant, Sa.; sues v-untur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wältra sig)</text:span> ibidem; v-da <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kretsande)</text:span> sidera; glans v-da calescit, Lucr.; oculos huc et illuc v.; serpens v-itur; ignis vento v-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwirflar);</text:span> lacrimæ per ora v-untur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillra);</text:span> tacito v-untur sidera lapsu; excutitur pronusque magister v-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(styrmannen wräkes)</text:span> in caput; v-entia (<text:span text:style-name="T2">intr.</text:span>) plaustra, Vg.; flumen v-it saxa, v-it minores vertices, Hor.; undæ v-unt saxa, arenas; Ixion rotā v-itur; v-itur in præceps; amnes defrenato cursu in æquora v-untur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rulla),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt l. oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om Parcerna = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spinna;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> häraf i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bestämma:</text:span></text:span> sic v-re Parcas; sic fata deûm rex sortitur v-itque vices, Vg.; natura vices lucis et anni, Juv. XIII. 88; inexorabile Clotho v-it opus, St.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprulla, wända, bläddra i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (uppslå) en bok:</text:span> librum, C.; commentarios Numæ, L.; - fabor enim, quando hæc te cura remordet, longius et v-ens fatorum arcana movebo, Vg. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ljud l. ord: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framrulla, uttala</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> fundo, jacto); <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rulla:</text:span></text:span> clamor ad cælum v-dus ad æthera mugit, Enn. Ann. 520 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Vahl.;</text:span> celeriter verba; sententias verbis, C. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwälfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tankar, bekymmer i sitt sinne, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwerwäga, betänka, besinna, tänka på:</text:span></text:span> multa secum, Sa.; ingentes iras in pectore; cum animo aliquid, L.; curarum fluctus in pectore, Lucr.; bellum, T.; <text:soft-page-break/>varias pectore curas, Luc.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid och öden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomgå, genomlefwa;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tiden sjelf: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">löpa, ila, förgå:</text:span></text:span> ætas v-da <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ilande),</text:span> Lucr.; tot v-re casus insignem pietate virum; v-dis mensibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under månaders lopp);</text:span> v-da dies <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tidens lopp)</text:span> en attulit ultro (quod optabas), Vg.; v-ens annus, Vg., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rullande, kretsande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> cælum, C.; aquæ, Hor.; aurum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om ett gulläple);</text:span> nexus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en orm),</text:span> Ov.; buxum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(snurra),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snabb, rask, liflig:</text:span></text:span> vis orationis; oratio, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hastigt förgår l. wexlar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flygtig, ostadig:</text:span></text:span> tempus; fortuna, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūbĭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snabbt rullande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kretsande rörelse:</text:span></text:span> mundi, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om föredrag l. talare: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Raskhet, wighet, rörlighet:</text:span></text:span> linguæ; verborum, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ostadighet, osäkerhet:</text:span></text:span> fortunæ, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūbĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Raskt, flytande:</text:span></text:span> funditur numerose et v. oratio, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūcra</text:span>, ae <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūcris</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mask på winträd</text:span> (= convolvulus): Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulle, rullning:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm., i concret och i abstract betyd.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulle, lynga, hwirfwel, ring, krets, krökning:</text:span></text:span> anguis - septem ingens gyros, septena v-a traxit; vinclorum (cæstuum) immensa v-a; anguis - sinuat immensa v-e (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bugtar i ringform)</text:span> terga; equus sinuat alterna v-a crurum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om de upplyftade frambenens krökning under språnget),</text:span> Vg.; nigra v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwirflar, ringar)</text:span> fumi; per magna v-a labens (anguis); celeri, juncto v-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slingrande)</text:span> serpunt angues; siderum v. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kretslopp),</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: skrift</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rulle</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bokrulle), papyrus- l. pergamentsblad, fästadt wid en stock (jfr</text:span> umbilicus), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omkring hwilken det rullades, då man ej läste derpå (och från hwilken det upprullades -</text:span> evolvebatur -, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">då man wille läsa); då de serskilde delarne af större werk plägade skrifwas hwar på sin</text:span> v., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är en </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rulle</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en skrift = del</text:span> (tomus ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">band):</text:span> v. amplius; primum, secundum v., Varr.; evolvi, explicui v. epistolarum tuarum; referre epistolas in v-a; quoniam satis hujus v-is magnitudo crevit, in altero v-e illa exponemus; implere v-a rebus; v-a conficere, C.; XVI v-a epistolarum a Cicerone ad Atticum missarum edita sunt; (uno) v-e vitam excellentium virorum concludere; plura persequi magnitudo v-is prohibet, N.; annosa v-a vatum, Hor.; mutatæ ter quinque v-a formæ (ɔ: 15 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">böcker metamorphoser),</text:span> Ov.; v-e complecti aliquid, Pn.; liber grandi v-e, Gell.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wexling:</text:span></text:span> sortis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snäcka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">voluta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> architecturstycke i fronten af ett ioniskt och corinthiskt capitäl:</text:span> Vitr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Rich).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūtim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hastigt, raskt:</text:span></text:span> Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wältra, rulla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">refl. och act. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. præs.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wältra, rulla, kasta sig:</text:span></text:span> ad <text:soft-page-break/>pedes alicujus; verres in luto v-atur, C.; vocem per ampla v-ant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låta rulla</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skalla)</text:span> atria; littora vocem; genibus v-ans hærebat, Vg.; gallina in pulvere; sus cænoso lacu v-atur, Varr., Col.; glans in jactu v-atur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kastas hit och dit),</text:span> L. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. v-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> v-ri, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sysselsätta;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sysselsätta sig med</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">in</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en sak (ett starkare synonym till</text:span> versor): in veteribus scriptis multum v-tus; in his scriptoribus te video v-tum, C.<text:line-break/>b. v-ri = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wältra sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i brott l. laster):</text:span> in stupris; cum scortis; in sceleribus; inter mala, C.<text:line-break/>c. v-re = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerwäga; hwälfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tankar l. bekymmer i sitt sinne:</text:span> aliquid in pectore, animo, in animo, Pt., C., L.; talia flammato secum dea corde v-ans, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūtābrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ställe, der swin wältra sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swinläger, pöl:</text:span></text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūtābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wältrande sig:</text:span></text:span> in voluptatibus, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūtātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wältrande, wältring:</text:span></text:span> scelera tua non vestigiis odorantes ingressus tuos, sed totis v-nibus corporis et cubilibus persecuti sumus, C.; in lutu v-tus, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ostadighet, obeständighet:</text:span></text:span> animi; rerum, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏlūtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slingrande:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Advolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla, wältra, kasta till, fram till;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">refl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kasta, wältra sig till, för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (isynnerhet</text:span> ad pedes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> pedibus (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), pedes, ad genua, genibus, genua alicujus): a-unt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rulla fram till bålet)</text:span> ingentes montibus ornos; a-vēre focis ulmos ignique dedere, Vg.; genibus se a-ens, a-tus, L.; o Bacche, tuis humiles a-imur aris, Ppt.; ad ignem aliquid, Pn.; - ambulantis Tiberii genua a-batur Haterius, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Circumvolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kringrulla, kring-, omswepa;</text:span></text:span> se c-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> c-i = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rulla, wältra, swepa sig omkring:</text:span></text:span> interea magnum sol c-itur annum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kringrullar ett år</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fullbordar kretsloppet af ett år),</text:span> Vg.; herba arboribus (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>) se c-it, Pn.; lanā multā c-tus, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Circumvŏlūtor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wältra sig omkring:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla tillsammans, weckla ihop; hoprulla, -weckla:</text:span></text:span> se c-ens sol abit, C.; coluber - lubrica c-it sublato pectore terga, Vg.; volumen (ɔ: librum), Sen.; herbam; ignis c-tus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convŏlūtor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tumla om med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convolvŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mask i winträd:</text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en slingerwäxt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åkerbinda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blomman för dagen):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla ned, wältra ned, kasta ned; nedrulla, -wältra, -kasta;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">refl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rulla, rinna, falla, sjunka ned:</text:span></text:span> saxa in musculum, C.; jumenta cum oneribus d-ta sunt, L.; auratas trabes d-unt (in oppugnatores); pensa fusis d. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spinna),</text:span> Vg.; fluvius inter saxa, Ct.; a sublimi d-i, Pn.; aqua d-itur e montibus per saxa, Col. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> vitā d-re (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">beröfwa)</text:span> alqm, Pt. Men. V. 5. 5. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">refl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sjunka ned, förfalla:</text:span></text:span> ad spem inanem, C.; res eo d-itur, ut -; d-ĕre (<text:span text:style-name="T2">imper. pass.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sjunk ned)</text:span> ad stirpem (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till din låga härkomst, ståndpunkt),</text:span> fratris similior quam patris, L.; ad otium et inertiam, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvolvo</text:span>, volvi (evŏluo, evŏlui, poēt.), vŏlūtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bort; wältra, wräka, kasta, weckla, draga ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bort:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. och i allm.:</text:span> id argentum tibi aut terra aut mari e-dum (ɔ: eruendum) est, Pt.; ex turba se, Ter.; Xanthus se e-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rullar)</text:span> in mare, Vg.; se super āera frustra tollere conatur jactasque e-re (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kasta af sig)</text:span> silvas, Ov.; serpens antro e-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slingrar sig fram),</text:span> Sil. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om spånad: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Weckla, draga ut; spinna</text:span></text:span> (deduco): Ov., Ppt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drifwa från</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beröfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt (ett starkare synon. till</text:span> exuo): ex præda, L.; bonis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>), Sen.; sede patriā regem, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla upp, weckla upp, upprulla, uppslå, utweckla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynnerhet om skriftrullar</text:span> (volumina); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">läsa, studera:</text:span></text:span> volumen, C., Qu.; poētas, C., T.; librum, C.; fastos, Hor.; antiquitatem, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprulla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwerwäga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">framställa, utreda, förklara, uppenbara:</text:span></text:span> quis potis ingentes oras e-re belli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upprulla krigets - rymder, taflor - bilden af en</text:span> volumen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ännu klar),</text:span> Enn. (Ann. 178, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Vahl.);</text:span> Vg. (IX. 528); exitum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerwäga);</text:span> naturam rerum; notionem animi, C.; seriem fati vates, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvŏlūtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprullande, uppslående</text:span></text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">studerande, läsande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en bok l. en författare:</text:span> poētarum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Involvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlutum, 3.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(inrulla), Inswepa, inweckla, inhölja:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> caput, C.; i-ta manu sacrum facere, L.; libellum membranā, Tib.; fertur in abruptum mons - silvas, armenta virosque i-ens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dragande in i hwirfweln)</text:span> secum; i-ēre diem nimbi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inswepte, höljde)</text:span> et nox humida cælum abstulit; nemus fumus, Vg.; nube alqm, Sen.; ventus nubibus se i-it, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> se literis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fördjupa sig, gräfwa sig ned i studier);</text:span> res ab ipsa natura i-tæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i mörker höljda);</text:span> causa obscuritate i-ta, C.; obscuris vera i-ens (Sibylla), Vg.; si celeres alas quatit Fortuna, virtute me i-o, Hor. (Od. III. 29. 55).<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla, wältra till, öfwer, på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> Ossæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på Ossa,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>) Olympum, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invŏlūcrum</text:span>, i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invŏlūcre</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omslag, hölje, omhölje, swepduk; foderal:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> <text:line-break/>1. eg.:</text:span> i-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om handduk, som begagnas wid rakning),</text:span> Pt.; clipei, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> ingenii tui ornamenta per quædam i-a atque integumenta perspexi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Involvŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bladmask:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obvolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hölja för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till; hölja, öfwerhölja:</text:span></text:span> caput; os folliculo, C.; capitibus o-tis se in Tiberim præcipitaverunt, L.; caput togā o-it Cæsar moriens, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bemantla:</text:span></text:span> vitium verbis, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wältra, rulla fram, bort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (widare), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">omkring:</text:span></text:span> in luto p-i, Ter.; pondere suo p-i, L.; torrens saxa, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genombläddra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en bok:</text:span> Catl. <text:line-break/>3. p-i in re = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flitigt sysselsätta sig med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">studera,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sätta sig in i:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pervŏlūto</text:span>, 1.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genombläddra, flitigt genomgå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">studera:</text:span></text:span> libros; scriptores, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla fram; wältra (kasta) fram, framåt, hän, bort:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> alqm in mediam viam, Ter.; saxa in alqm, Ct.; cupas ardentes in opera, Cs.; hunc (curru effusum) lora et juga subter p-ēre rotæ, Vg.; molares (in subeuntes hostes) p., T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hänföra, hänrycka:</text:span></text:span> in iram, Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wräka, kasta framstupa, omkull, ned:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> se ad pedes alicujus p-re; ad genua alicujus p-i, L.; genibus alicujus p-tus, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. uttryck:</text:span> sperne fidem, p-ve (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kasta, trampa i stoftet)</text:span> deos, mendacia vincant, Ppt.; multi fortunis p-bantur (ɔ: exuebantur; cedebant bonis, Ann. VI. 17; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> prolabi, III. 55); ad libita alicujus p-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förnedra sig</text:span> ɔ: prolabi), T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla, wältra tillbaka; rulla, weckla upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> igen;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rulla tillbaka, falla baklänges:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> draco serpit subter supraque r-ens se, C. (N. D. II. 42); excussi manibus radii r-taque pensa; saxa r-ta; æquora r-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillbakaswallande);</text:span> r-tus equo; ter sese attollens cubitoque annixa levavit, ter r-ta torost (moriens Dido), Vg.; fluctum, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprulla, uppslå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en</text:span> (volumen) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bok l. ställe deri:</text:span> tuas adversus te (Cato) Origines r-am, L.; loca jam recitata r-imus irrevocati, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kastas, falla tillbaka, återgå, återkomma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ett ställe, ett ämne l. påstående, ett tillstånd o. s. w.:</text:span> in eandem vitam, Ter.; r-or identidem ad Tusculanum; neque diutius, quam satis sit, in iisdem locis commoremur neque eodem identidem r-amur; non, quoties causa dicenda est, toties ad ejus causæ seposita argumenta r-i nos oportet; r-eris eodem (Tusc. I. 5), C.; juvenis quondam, nunc femina Cænis rursus et in veterem fato r-ta figuram, Vg.; ad dispensationem annonæ, L.; Tiberius (in laudatione filii) ad vana et totiens irrisa r-tus de reddenda re publica et cet., T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">act.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter genomgå, upplefwa:</text:span></text:span> casus, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">act.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprepa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tanke l. ord; ånyo </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwerwäga:</text:span></text:span> quid ego hæc nequiquam ingrata r-o?, Vg.; animus r-ens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(”idislande”)</text:span> iras (Tiberii); dicta factaque alicujus, T. <text:line-break/>d. ut longe repetas longeque r-as nomen, ab infami deducis nomen asylo, Juv. VIII. 272-3.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvŏlūbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbakarullande:</text:span></text:span> pondus saxi, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subvolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprulla, -wälta:</text:span></text:span> saxa, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭpervolvo</text:span>, volvi, vŏlūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wältra ofwanpå:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vŏlup</text:span> (vŏlŭpe; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den sednare formen är wäl den ursprungliga, dock lära codd. uteslutande hafwa den förra; beslägtadt med</text:span> vŏlo?), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott brukadt såsom prædicat) och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljuft, angenämt, wälkommet, kärkommet, glädjande:</text:span></text:span> vocat -, quocum multa vŏlūp (ɔ: habuisset) et gaudia clamque palamque, Enn. (Ann. 247, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Vahl.);</text:span> venis, ut tibi sit ex me v.; volŭp est, quod agas, si id procedit lepide atque ex sententia; bene factum et volŭp est, hodie me his mulierculis tetulisse auxilium; facere animo suo v. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">göra sig en glad dag);</text:span> victitare v., Pt.; venire (te) salvum, v. est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en glädje),</text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏlŭpia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nöjets gudinna:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏluptas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nöje, njutning, wälbehag; lust, wällust:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nöje</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillfredsställelse, fröjd, glädje:</text:span></text:span> quot ego v-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fröjder)</text:span> fero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bådar)?;</text:span> v-em creare alicui, Pt.; v-em capio maximam, Afr.; v-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(glädje)</text:span> magnam nuntio, Ter.; dulcis tua amicitia et sperata v., Lucr.; omne, quo gaudemus, v. est; id est mihi v-i; v-em cepi, tantum virum fuisse in republica, C.; ea (ɔ: oves) v. solamenque mali; trahit sua quemque v., Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sinligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nöje,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> kroppslig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">njutning, lust</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lustar), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wällust:</text:span></text:span> nunquam in aqua sensi inesse tantam v-em, Pt.; v-e capiuntur homines, ut hamo pisces; expetuntur divitiæ ad v-es perfruendas; nulla capitalior pestis homini data est, quam corporis v., cujus avidæ libidines ad potiundum rapiuntur; v-e perfundi; nova, m ediocris, perpetua v.; v-em capere, percipere, captare, accipere, habere ex re; v-bus deditum esse; in (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ett tillstånd af)</text:span> v-e esse; titillatio v-is; v. in motu, in statu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(positiv, privativ),</text:span> C.; his profecto contra naturam corpus v-i, anima oneri est; animus captus pravis cupidinibus ad inertiam et v-es corporis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kroppsliga njutningar)</text:span> pessumdatus, Sa.; vini, L.; rara et interrupta doloribus contingit v., Hor.; Tiberius vitare coetus, recondere v-es insueverat, T.; pravā duci, deliniri v-e, Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer, wanl. såsom smekord:</text:span> v. mea = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">min lust, fröjd, min glädje:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Lucr., Vg.; Aeneadum genetrix, hominum divomque v., alma Venus, Lucr.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offentliga </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förlustelser, lustbarheter, nöjen:</text:span></text:span> C. Mur. cap. 55; Vop., Treb.; volgus avidum v-um et, si principes eodem trahant, lætum; Augustus civile rebatur misceri v-bus vulgi, T. (Ann. I. 54).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏluptābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljuf, glädjande:</text:span></text:span> nuntius, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏluptārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljuflig; sinlig, wällustig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som erbjuder nöjen l. njutningar i rikt mått:</text:span> is casus nobis miserabilis videtur, ipsi (Regulo) propter fidem et constantiam - v. erat; sensus; disputationes; possessiones; philosophus, C.; loca amonea et v-a exercitum corruperant, Sa.; homo; res amoenæ et v-æ, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏluptārie</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wällustigt:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏluptĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bringar njutning:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏluptuōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljuflig:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏlūsiēnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏlūsius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. personnamn</text:span> (Catl. 36).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Volut . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Volvo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vōmer</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vōmis,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Plogbill:</text:span></text:span> v-e perstringere, C.; aduncus, Ov.; vomis (Georg. I. 162); sulco attritus splendescere vomer (ibid. I. 65), Vg.; incultæ pacantur v-e silvæ, Hor.; vomer, Juv. III. 311.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vŏmĭca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böld, warböld, pestböld:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> v-am aperire, C.; putres, Juv. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. om skadlig och widrig person l. sak:</text:span> duæ v-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Augustus om sin sedeslösa dotter och dotterdotter),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏmĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förpestad:</text:span></text:span> mores, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vomificus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vomo.<text:line-break/>Vomis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vomer. <text:line-break/>Vomit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vomo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vŏmo,</text:span> ui, ĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräka, uppkräka, spy, utspruta, ut-, uppspy, uppkasta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> v-tum, Pt.; in mensam; post coenam, C.; atros ore v-ens ignes (Cacus), Vg.; edunt, ut v-ant, v-unt, ut edant, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utkasta, gifwa ifrån sig, uppkasta:</text:span></text:span> Charybdis v-it fluctus totidem totidemque resorbet, Ov.; animam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppgifwa);</text:span> stuppa fumum; domus undam salutantum, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏmĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förorsakar kräkning:</text:span> Cæl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏmĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppkastning, kräkning:</text:span></text:span> curari v-e, C.; v-em ciere, concitare; v-e reddere aliquid, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏmĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräkas:</text:span></text:span> pecudes, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏmĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som brukar att kräkas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för att få bättre matlust):</text:span> jejuni v-es Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏmĭtōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förorsakar kräkning:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏmĭtōrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mellan bänkraderna på en theater:</text:span> Mcb. Saturn. VI. 4.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏmĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräkning, kräkande:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convŏmo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräka allt öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvŏmo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kasta upp, kräkas:</text:span></text:span> Cæcil. ap. Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēvŏmo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utspy, kräka upp:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> avis conchas, C.; venenum Britannicus, Su.; nisus e-entis adjuvat medicus, T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> iram in alqm, Ter.; virus acerbitatis in alqm; urbs improbum e-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wräker ut</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">frigör sig ifrån);</text:span> pecuniam devoratam e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa igen);</text:span> orationem in aliquem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intervŏmo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spruta, utgjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">emellan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> fons dulces inter salsas i-it undas, Lucr. VI. 894.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōvŏmo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framspruta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utblåsa):</text:span> ventus - turbinis immanem vim p-it atque procellæ, Lucr. VI. 447.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕvŏmo</text:span>, ui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräka upp igen, uppkasta, gifwa ifrån sig igen:</text:span></text:span> salsos fluctus pectore, Vg.; Charybdis vorat r-itque carinas, Ov.; aqua - sursum r-it atque remittit ligna trabesque, Lucr. II. 199.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>onōnes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">parthiskt namn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏpiscus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen (om ordets ursprungliga betydelse se</text:span> Pn. VII. 8).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vopte = vos ipsi, Cato ap. Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vŏro,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sluka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> piscis hamum, Pt.; animalia v-ant, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> literas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sluka = med otålig ifwer läsa),</text:span> C.; naves rapidus v-at æquore vortex, Vg.; Charybdis carinas, Ov.; viam v-bit (= corripiet), Catl.; amor v-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förtär)</text:span> medullas, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏrāgo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afgrund, bråddjup,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> gapande </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">djup, håla, remna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i jorden:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> summersus equus v-bus, C.; in foro, L.; vasta v., Vg.; ingens, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> gurges et v. patrimonii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en slösare);</text:span> v. reipublicæ, C.; ventris (Erysichthonis), Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏrāgĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af hålor l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bråddjup:</text:span></text:span> solum, Cs. (Ht.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏrax</text:span>, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slukande, glupsk, glupande:</text:span></text:span> Charybdis, C.; venter; ignis v-ior, Ov.; usura, Luc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏrācĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glupskhet:</text:span></text:span> asini, Ap.; ignis, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vŏrācĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glupskt:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvŏro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sluka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ned, bort):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ovum, Cato.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förslösa:</text:span></text:span> patrimonium; bona, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">girigt höra l. läsa:</text:span> libros; orationem, C.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">få swälja ngt förtretligt:</text:span> molestiam, C.<text:line-break/>d. nomen d-vi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(glömt),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vors . . ., Vort . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vers . . ., Vert . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under</text:span> Verto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vōs,</text:span> vostri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> vostrum (vostrorum, Pt., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">t. ex.</text:span> Amph. prol. 4), vestri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> vestrum; vōbīs: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. pers.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I; eder:</text:span></text:span> vos a vostris abduxi negotiis neque id processit, qua vos duxi gratia; abi intro ad vos domum; nunc ne quis erret vostrum, paucis in viam deducam, Pt.; ne cui vestrum -, Ter.; minus habeo virium, quam vestrum utervis, C.; vos, quibus est virtus, muliebrem tollite luctum, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vosmet</text:span>, vōbismet: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I; eder:</text:span></text:span> ut vosmet alias pariter nunc Mars adjuvet, Pt.; vosmetipsi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Voster</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vester</text:span>, stra, strum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. poss.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eder:</text:span></text:span> vos in vostris mercimoniis emundis vendundisque; modo nescio quis inspectavit vostrum (i. e. vostrorum) familiarium per nostrum inpluvium, Pt.; vester, Camenæ, vester in arduos tollor Sabinos, Hor.; de v-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af edert eget, eder egendom)</text:span> impendite, L.; plaga v-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som träffar eder),</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vestras</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af edert folk:</text:span> Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">V</text:span>ŏsĕgus <text:line-break/>(Vogĕsus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Vogeserne i Elsas.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Vot . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Voveo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vŏveo,</text:span> vōvi, vōtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lofwa; göra löfte</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt en gud (med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc. c. inf. fut.</text:span>): vota v., Pt.; decimam deo: se daturum deo aliquid, C.; Galli aut homines pro victimis immolant aut se immolaturos v-ent, Cs.; Tullus in re trepida duodecim vovit Salios fanaque Pallori ac Pavori; votum, L.; votum (equum Danai) pro reditu simulant, Vg.; dona; victimam; taurorum corpora centum, Ov.; v-ram dulces epulas et album Libero caprum prope funeratus arboris ictu, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppoffra:</text:span></text:span> capita sua pro salute patriæ, Sa. fr.; tyranno, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Önska:</text:span></text:span> quid v-eat dulci nutricula majus alumno, qui sapere et fari possit, quæ sentiat et cui gratia, fama, valetudo contingat abunde, Hor.; quæ v-rat, odit; v., ut - (Met. IX. 675), Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vōtum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Löfte</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till en gud), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">löftesskänk:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> v. vovere, Pt.; victoriæ suæ deo v-um facere, C.; v-a nuncupare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(högtidligen göra l. afgifwa),</text:span> suscipere, pro aliqua re, Cs., C.; v-o obligari, teneri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara förpligtad till uppfyllelse af -</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hafwa wunnit sin önskan);</text:span> v-i religione obstrictum esse, C.; v. solvere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppfylla, fullgöra),</text:span> reddere, Catl., C.; non v-is neque suppliciis muliebribus auxilia deorum parantur, Sa.; dixit, se v-a suscepisse, quæ Jovi Ammoni solveret; dixit, nunc demum se v-i esse damnatum (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hafwa fått sin bön uppfylld),</text:span> N.; v-i damnari; hoc deos immortales inter nuncupanda, concipienda v-a expoposci, L.; v-i reus (= v-i damnatus); cessas in v-a precesque; aras v-is incendere, Vg.; v. persolvere, Ct.; ex v-o facere templum, Ov.; ad miseras preces decurrere et v-is pacisci, ne Cypriæ Tyriæque merces addant avaro divitias mari; vitulus largis juvenescit herbis in mea v-a; donare ex v-o laribus catenam, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Äktenskapslöfte, äktenskap:</text:span></text:span> secunda, Jct., Ap.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bön, önskan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. deß föremål; äfwen någon gång i ond mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förbannelse:</text:span></text:span> si virtus famula fortunæ est, vereor, ne non tam virtutis fiduciā nitendum nobis ad spem beate vivendi, quam v-a facienda, C.; ejus me v-i compotem vos facere potestis, L.; hoc erat in v-is, modus agri non ita magnus; versibus impariter junctis querimonia primum, post etiam inclusa est v-i sententia compos; v-is obligasti perfidum caput, Hor.; v-a movent superos: ubi portitor æra recepit, obserat umbrosos lurida porta rogos, Ppt.; pia, timida v-a; v-a tangunt deos; v-a suos (ɔ: propitios) habuere deos; tua corrige v-a; v-a fovere; v-o majora munera; v-i potens; v-is potiri; concipere pia v-a; pro v-o; ex v-o, Ov.; ad v-um, Qu.; effundi in v-a, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vōtĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Löften bärande:</text:span></text:span> arbor, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Vōtīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lofwad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt en gud, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">löftes-:</text:span></text:span> ludi; legatio, C.; pascitur in reditum vestrum v-a juvenca; me tabula sacer v-a paries indicat uvida suspendisse potenti vestimenta maris deo, Hor.; v-as noctes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för tillfrisknande)</text:span> et mihi solve decem, Ppt.; tura, Ov.; v-us oris habitus Chattorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oklippt hår),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Önskad:</text:span></text:span> Treb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvŏveo</text:span>, vōvi, vōtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bortlofwa, lofwa till offer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt en gud l. högre makt </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerhufwud:</text:span> Agamemnon Dianæ d-rat, quod in regno suo pulcherrimum natum esset illo anno; sica sacris initiata et d-ta, C.; Galli Marti ea, quæ bello ceperunt, d-ent, Cs.; victima d-ta, Hor.; ara, Ppt. <text:line-break/>2. se militem d-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> hostes d-re = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gifwa sig till offer, inwiga till offer,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sades om romerske fältherrar, som medelst högtidliga ord och bruk inwigde sig l. ngn annan af hären till offer för hele hären och folket och på samme gång åt döden och förderfwet inwigde fienderne</text:span> (L. VIII. 9. §. 4 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.,</text:span> 10. §. 11 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.):</text:span> quidam imperatores etiam se ipsos diis immortalibus, capite velato, verbis certis pro republica d-runt, C.; in trepidatione (proelii) P. Decius: agedum, inquit, pontifex, præi verba, quibus me pro legionibus d-eam: - sicut verbis nuncupavi, ita pro rep. pop. Romani, exercitu, legionibus, auxiliis pop. Romani Quiritum legiones auxiliaque hostium mecum diis manibus Tellurique d-o -; licet consuli dictatorique et prætori, quum legiones hostium d-eat, non utique se, sed, quem velit ex legione Romana scripta civem, d-re, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbanna; förtrolla:</text:span></text:span> Alcibiades capitis damnatum se audivit et sacerdotes coactos a populo, ut se d-ren<text:bookmark text:name="_GoBack"/>t, N.; num te carminibus, num te pollentibus herbis d-vit tacito tempore noctis anus?, Tib.; Battiades inimicum d-et Ibin, Ov.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerhufwud: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Offra, uppoffra, hängifwa, egna, bestämma:</text:span></text:span> me fortunasque meas pro vestra incolumitate d-vi, C.; infelix (Dido) pesti d-ta futuræ, Vg.; se gloriæ, Ov.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om fostbrödralag l. följesförhållande bland Celter och Germaner:</text:span> se d-re amicitiæ alicujus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hängifwa sig åt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swärja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn trohet:</text:span> d-torum hæc est condicio, uti omnibus in vita commodis una cum iis fruantur, quorum se amicitiæ dediderint: si quid his per vim accidat, aut eundem casum una ferant aut sibi mortem consciscant, Cs. b. G. III. 22.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvōtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbannad, åt förderfwet wigd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bestämd:</text:span></text:span> arbor; Romam, quam non finitimi valuerunt perdere Marsi, impia perdemus d-i sanguinis ætas, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hängifwen, tillgifwen:</text:span></text:span> alicui d-simus, Sen.; animus alicui d., Su. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvōti</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">krigare, som swurit att följa sin anförare i lif och död: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fosterbröder:</text:span></text:span> Galli appellant soldurios, Cs. b. G. III. 22 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> devoveo 5).<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begifwen på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> scenæ, Su.; d-a vino mulier, Phdr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvōtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppoffrande, -offring, hängifwande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom offer:</text:span> Deciorum (devoveo, 2); capitis sui; vitæ suæ, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbannelse, bannlysning; förtrollning:</text:span></text:span> d. in pilis scripta (Alcibiadis), N.; veneficiis et d-bus impugnari se comperit Germanicus; petere conjugium principis d-bus, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillgifwenhet, hängifwenhet:</text:span></text:span> erga alqm; pro aliquo, Treb., Cp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēvōto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gifwa till offer, uppoffra:</text:span></text:span> animam hostibus, Acc. Aen. 15 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Ribbeck);</text:span> C. Parad. 1. (inc. l.).<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbanna; förhexa:</text:span></text:span> Ap.; Pt. Cas. II. 6. 36.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vox,</text:span> vōcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Röst; ton; ord; yttrande:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Röst, stämma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (organ):</text:span> quoja prope me hic v. sonat?; corvi; v-em exercere, Pt., C.; orationis indicem v-em habemus: in v-e autem duo sequimur, ut clara sit, ut suavis; sine contentione v. nec languens nec canora; v. subrauca; et v-is contentione majore et verborum gravitate uti; flebilis; dulcis; plena; altior; hæc sic ab illo esse acta constabat oculis, v-e, gestu, inimici ut lacrimas tenere vix possent; histriones omnes in oris et v-is et motus moderatione elaborant; v-is conformatio et varietas; v-em attollere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(höja),</text:span> intendere, ponere; aliud v-is genus iracundia sibi sumat, aliud metus, C.; audita est in foro v. præconis patres in curiam vocantis, L.; v-e magna <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hög)</text:span> hortari; v-e supplici uti, Sa.; et v-e et manibus significare aliquid; v. clarior, magna, Cs.; talia v-e refert, Vg.; summa suavitas oris et v-is; constantia v-is et vultūs, N.; quiritantium, L.; interdum comoedia v-em tollit; minax; liquida; acuta, Hor.; si v-em haberes, nulla prior ales foret, Phdr.; candida <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(klar);</text:span> fusca; v-em submittere, Qu.; objiciunt ad os scuta, quo plenior et gravior v. repercussu intumescat, T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ton, ljud:</text:span></text:span> (v-es ut chordæ sunt intentæ, quæ ad quemque tactum respondeant); acuta gravis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hög, låg),</text:span> cita tarda, magna parva <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stark, swag);</text:span> v-em mittere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa ifrån sig),</text:span> C.; citabat ”io Bacche” modo summa v-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(högsta ton),</text:span> modo hac resonat quæ chordis quattuor ima; v-es fidibus crevere severis; sunt verba et v-es, quibus hunc lenire dolorem possis, Hor. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uttal:</text:span></text:span> quædam certa v. hujus Romani generis urbisque propria, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ord:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ett</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ord:</text:span> v. voluptatis, doloris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ordet</text:span> voluptas, dolor), C.; formæ v-is; in scrutando verbo adjiciunt aut demunt literas (etymologi), quo facilius, quid sub ea v-e subsit, videre possint, Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ord</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom innehållande en mening, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">röst, röster</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som utsäga l. fordra ngt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tal, yttrande:</text:span></text:span> leges una eademque v-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(röst, språk)</text:span> cum omnibus loquuntur; magnifica vero v. et magno viro ac sapiente digna; quæ v. potest esse contemptior, quam Milonis Crotoniatæ, qui - aspexisse lacertos suos dicitur illacrimansque dixisse: at hi quidem jam mortui sunt?; negabat Scipio, ullam v-em inimiciorem amicitiæ potuisse reperiri, quam ejus, qui dixisset, ita amare oportere, ut si quando es-</text:p>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>